UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='急救是一项很有用的技能。在战斗中，它常常能救人一命。如果你想要学习这项技能的话，就去灵魂高地的「精神治疗」小店里面找找潘德·缚石，他可是这方面最好的训练师。',Text0_1_loc4='急救是一项很有用的技能。在战斗中，它常常能救人一命。如果你想要学习这项技能的话，就去灵魂高地的「精神治疗」小店里面找找潘德·缚石，他可是这方面最好的训练师。',Text1_0_loc4='急救是一项很有用的技能。在战斗中，它常常能救人一命。如果你想要学习这项技能的话，就去灵魂高地的「精神治疗」小店里面找找潘德·缚石，他可是这方面最好的训练师。',Text1_1_loc4='急救是一项很有用的技能。在战斗中，它常常能救人一命。如果你想要学习这项技能的话，就去灵魂高地的「精神治疗」小店里面找找潘德·缚石，他可是这方面最好的训练师。' WHERE entry=1336; /* Text0_0: First Aid is always a nice skill to have.  Many a time during battle has it saved my hide.  Visit Spiritual Healing on the Spirit Rise.  Pand Stonebinder can teach you all you need to know to save your hide as well. */ /* Text0_1: First Aid is always a nice skill to have.  Many a time during battle has it saved my hide.  Visit Spiritual Healing on the Spirit Rise.  Pand Stonebinder can teach you all you need to know to save your hide as well. */ /* Text1_0: Life is a struggle, and the saying that which does not kill you makes you stronger is not always true.  Sometimes wounds act slowly, which is why we have bandages.  Pand Stonebinder of the Spirit Rise can teach you the art of First Aid. */ /* Text1_1: Life is a struggle, and the saying that which does not kill you makes you stronger is not always true.  Sometimes wounds act slowly, which is why we have bandages.  Pand Stonebinder of the Spirit Rise can teach you the art of First Aid. */
