UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经学会的任何知识我都可以教你, $N.  如果你想继续学习的话,在暴风城法师区的暗夜精灵莉萨谈谈 . 听说他是一个好老师' WHERE entry=5015; /* Text0_0: You\'ve already learned everything I can teach you, $N. Talk to the night elf Lilyssia Nightbreeze in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind if you want to continue your studies. I hear she\'s a good teacher. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然我被关在这间小屋里，但是我梦想着加入城墙外激烈的战斗。然而，职责迫使我为替我战斗的那些人传授知识...',Text0_1_loc4='虽然我被关在这间小屋里，但是我梦想着加入城墙外激烈的战斗。然而，职责迫使我为替我战斗的那些人传授知识...',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5016; /* Text0_0: Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now. */ /* Text0_1: Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='(达纳苏斯语)祝你好运，$g兄弟:姐妹;。你有外面的消息吗?我希望得到泰达希尔的消息。' WHERE entry=5019; /* Text0_0: Ishnu-alah, $gbrother:sister;. Have you any tidings from abroad? My heart yearns for news of Teldrassil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很荣幸能够传授给你知识，$N。看得出来你用得不错。' WHERE entry=5020; /* Text0_0: I am honored to share my knowledge with you, $N. See that you use it well. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须找一个更有经验的老师，因为你已经超越了我的能力了。我建议你找这里的莉琳希亚·夜风谈谈:她有更多知识可以传授给你。' WHERE entry=5021; /* Text0_0: You must choose a more experienced teacher, for you have surpassed my abilities. I advise you to speak with Lilyssia Nightbreeze here: she has much knowledge to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='德鲁伊们说大自然把部落从卡林多赶出去只是个时间问题。然而堕落继续在我们的大地上蔓延，甚至在泰达希尔这里也是。',Text0_1_loc4='德鲁伊们说大自然把部落从卡林多赶出去只是个时间问题。然而堕落继续在我们的大地上蔓延，甚至在泰达希尔这里也是。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5022; /* Text0_0: The druids say that it is only a matter of time until nature itself drives the Horde from Kalimdor. Yet corruption continues to spread throughout our lands, even here on Teldrassil. */ /* Text0_1: The druids say that it is only a matter of time until nature itself drives the Horde from Kalimdor. Yet corruption continues to spread throughout our lands, even here on Teldrassil. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好!你对药剂的理解进展不错。',Text0_1_loc4='干得好!你对药剂的理解进展不错。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5023; /* Text0_0: Well done! Your understanding of potions is coming along nicely. */ /* Text0_1: Well done! Your understanding of potions is coming along nicely. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不幸的是，对於拥有像你这样经历的人来说我没有什麽可教的，我的朋友。找到夜精灵希尔瓦娜·林月，她住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text0_1_loc4='不幸的是，对於拥有像你这样经历的人来说我没有什麽可教的，我的朋友。找到夜精灵希尔瓦娜·林月，她住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5024; /* Text0_0: Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='(达纳苏斯语)愿伊露恩与你同在，我的$g兄弟:姐妹;。我们这里欢迎你。',Text0_1_loc4='(达纳苏斯语)愿伊露恩与你同在，我的$g兄弟:姐妹;。我们这里欢迎你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5025; /* Text0_0: Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you. */ /* Text0_1: Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人们从森林植物中制造的东西难道不令人震惊吗?说真的，月神对我们已经很慷慨了。',Text0_1_loc4='人们从森林植物中制造的东西难道不令人震惊吗?说真的，月神对我们已经很慷慨了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5026; /* Text0_0: Is it not astonishing what one can create from the plants of the forest? Truly, Elune has blessed us with her bounty. */ /* Text0_1: Is it not astonishing what one can create from the plants of the forest? Truly, Elune has blessed us with her bounty. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不幸的是，对於拥有像你这样经历的人来说我没有什麽可教的，我的朋友。去找夜精灵希尔瓦娜·林月，她住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text0_1_loc4='不幸的是，对於拥有像你这样经历的人来说我没有什麽可教的，我的朋友。去找夜精灵希尔瓦娜·林月，她住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5027; /* Text0_0: You are kind to seek me out, but your skills are beyond my own. Have a word with Sylvanna Forestmoon, just over there. She\'s been looking for another student. */ /* Text0_1: You are kind to seek me out, but your skills are beyond my own. Have a word with Sylvanna Forestmoon, just over there. She\'s been looking for another student. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是我亲爱的恋人卡利派你来找我的?她可是我的宝贝。' WHERE entry=5028; /* Text0_0: Did my sweet lass Kali send you down to me? The apple of my eye, she is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没想到你会来这儿找我的可爱的卡利谈话。很好。这是药水。有没有人说过你是个头脑简单的家伙?' WHERE entry=5029; /* Text0_0: I don\'t suppose you\'re here to talk about my lovely Kali. Fine, then. Potions it is. Anyone ever tell ye you\'ve got a one-track mind? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我教不了你，$N。去找塔雷·浆泡;她是一个侏儒，住在铁炉堡的侏儒区。哦，既然你反正要去，请把我的爱带给卡利。' WHERE entry=5030; /* Text0_0: Ye\'re beyond my skill to teach, $N. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she\'s a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you\'re headed up anyway, give Kali my love. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别被那些天真的大眼睛欺骗了。塔雷是个专家，我每天都在学习新知识。你认为我为什麽会在侏儒区?你看我像个工程师吗?啊，我可不这麽想。' WHERE entry=5031; /* Text0_0: Don\'t let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally\'s an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d\'you think I\'m here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn\'t think so. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$g小夥子:小姑娘;，努力吧。苦干和决心 - 那才是成功之道!书本知识是远远不够的。' WHERE entry=5032; /* Text0_0: Put your back into it, $glad:lass;. Hard work and determination--that\'s the way! Don\'t let anyone tell you book learnin\' is all ye need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，我无法教你任何东西，$N。跟那边的塔利·浆泡谈谈。她几乎构不着桌子，但是当她在配制药水时，你得小心一点!' WHERE entry=5033; /* Text0_0: Och, there\'s nothing I can teach ye, $N. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来像是个喜欢冒险的人。而我，自从我们食人妖来到这里我就受够冒险了。现在我每天都是既来之则安之，而且我训练其他家伙替我冒险。' WHERE entry=5034; /* Text0_0: You got the look of someone wantin\' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an\' I train other folks to handle adventures for me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='准备好下一个训练了吗? 好, 他们. 第一个 放松. 你必须保持放松搅拌好药水.' WHERE entry=5035; /* Text0_0: Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对话' WHERE entry=5036; /* Text0_0: You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $N. You be needin\' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'ll help you out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='桌上的所有瓶子中都盛有今天配制好的药水。心急吃不到热豆腐。哈哈!' WHERE entry=5037; /* Text0_0: All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们说我愚蠢，我要证明自己的实力。我要关注所有的罐子，证明它们都能煮东西。我的好运就要来了!谁是愚蠢的人，嗯?嗯!?' WHERE entry=5038; /* Text0_0: They called me stupid, but I\'ll show them. I\'m going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I\'m on a roll! Who\'s stupid now, huh? Huh!? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不能帮你。你比我更懂药剂。还有，我还要看着罐子。去找那边的耶尔玛克谈谈。他懂得很多药剂的知识。' WHERE entry=5039; /* Text0_0: Can\'t help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='贝娜就像着魔一样工作。她日以继夜地调制这些药剂，不吃不睡。我知道我们的不死族盟友需要帮助，但是我担心她这样会伤身体的。' WHERE entry=5040; /* Text0_0: Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我首次开始配制药水时，我一定打碎过成百个瓶子。我笨手笨脚，瓶子在我手中极易破碎。希望你比我更为小心。' WHERE entry=5041; /* Text0_0: I must have broken hundreds of vials when I first began brewing potions. The glass was so fragile in my clumsy hands. I hope you are more cautious than I was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你学习的能力已经超过我了。你需要找那边的贝娜·冰蹄谈谈以获得更多指示。但请不要占用她太多时间。她需要休息。' WHERE entry=5042; /* Text0_0: Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don\'t take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能看到一张友善的脸真不错。我没有跟药剂师乔汉聊过很多，除非他想要什麽东西。他离开坟墓太久了。有一天我也会像他一样，我听说。真可怕。或许到那时我就不在乎了。',Text0_1_loc4='能看到一张友善的脸真不错。我没有跟药剂师乔汉聊过很多，除非他想要什麽东西。他离开坟墓太久了。有一天我也会像他一样，我听说。真可怕。或许到那时我就不在乎了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5043; /* Text0_0: Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care. */ /* Text0_1: Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来学习配制药水的?我能传授给你很多知识。虽然我已年老力衰，但脑子还是管用的。',Text0_1_loc4='你是来学习配制药水的?我能传授给你很多知识。虽然我已年老力衰，但脑子还是管用的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5044; /* Text0_0: Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet. */ /* Text0_1: Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很珍惜我们之间的友谊，但是让我们面对现实吧:你对药水的了解比我多。要是你想得到训练的话，就找亡灵马许医生谈谈。他居住在幽暗城的炼金房。',Text0_1_loc4='我很珍惜我们之间的友谊，但是让我们面对现实吧:你对药水的了解比我多。要是你想得到训练的话，就找亡灵马许医生谈谈。他居住在幽暗城的炼金房。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5045; /* Text0_0: I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */ /* Text0_1: I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是真的，我曾经是人类。缺点是可能转换为我们的优势的，$N，因为我对人类的劣势了若指掌。' WHERE entry=5046; /* Text0_0: Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $N, for I know human weaknesses intimately. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好。从这些标本上再切下一块肉来。让我们看看你学到了什麽，我们可以由此开始。' WHERE entry=5047; /* Text0_0: Very well. Cut another lump of flesh from one of these specimens. Let us test what you\'ve learned so far, and we can progress from there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对药剂的知识已经远胜於我，但你还有很多要学的。上楼去到东南面见见马许医生。他会交给你真正的苦痛─啊咳。他是一个被遗忘者，他能进一步训练你。' WHERE entry=5048; /* Text0_0: Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别那样看我。我也许跟你不同，我不是个冒险家，但是这并不意味着我的力量比你小。忙碌的生活会让你的手臂变得强壮的。' WHERE entry=5049; /* Text0_0: Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn\'t mean I can\'t have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有什麽可教你的了。但是，我听说有位名叫安尼希尔的夜精灵也许能教你。她居住在达纳苏斯的工匠区。' WHERE entry=5050; /* Text0_0: There\'s nothing more I can teach you. I\'ve heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对不起, $N, 但是我真的没有时间花费在新手身上了. 去找可以教你的训练师. 去找暗夜精灵 米拉 , 在达纳苏斯的工匠区的露台.' WHERE entry=5051; /* Text0_0: I\'m sorry, $N, but I have no time to spend on novices. You want someone closer to your own skill level. Try the night elf Milla Fairancora, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要我的帮助?可以。你需要什麽?' WHERE entry=5053; /* Text0_0: You want my help? You got it. What do you need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别被沃萨亮晶晶的眼睛和浓密的胡须愚弄了。他是个很有才能的学徒，也是个很好的朋友，即使我在跟他谈话时颈部有些痉挛。',Text0_1_loc4='别被沃萨亮晶晶的眼睛和浓密的胡须愚弄了。他是个很有才能的学徒，也是个很好的朋友，即使我在跟他谈话时颈部有些痉挛。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5054; /* Text0_0: Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him. */ /* Text0_1: Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，我能教的你已经都学会了。或许你该找其他人谈谈了。试一下达纳苏斯工匠区的夜精灵安尼希尔。她确实很有智慧!',Text0_1_loc4='嗯，我能教的你已经都学会了。或许你该找其他人谈谈了。试一下达纳苏斯工匠区的夜精灵安尼希尔。她确实很有智慧!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5055; /* Text0_0: Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent! */ /* Text0_1: Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那很好，$N。无论那是什麽，去拿给那边的沃萨看看。他会回答你的任何问题。',Text0_1_loc4='那很好，$N。无论那是什麽，去拿给那边的沃萨看看。他会回答你的任何问题。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5057; /* Text0_0: That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have. */ /* Text0_1: That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁?为什麽骚扰我?哦，是啦─你是学生吧。是的。我能为你做什麽吗?',Text0_1_loc4='你是谁?为什麽骚扰我?哦，是啦─你是学生吧。是的。我能为你做什麽吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5058; /* Text0_0: Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you? */ /* Text0_1: Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='(达纳苏斯语)祝你与家人好运, $N。你是来寻求知识的吗?',Text0_1_loc4='(达纳苏斯语)祝你与家人好运, $N。你是来寻求知识的吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5059; /* Text0_0: Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge? */ /* Text0_1: Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='教学不只是一项单边活动，$N。当我教你时，我自己也在学习，而我的理解也在加深。',Text0_1_loc4='教学不只是一项单边活动，$N。当我教你时，我自己也在学习，而我的理解也在加深。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5060; /* Text0_0: Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows. */ /* Text0_1: Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然我很高兴听到你对我的能力充满信心，但我真的没法再教你了。你必须到达纳苏斯的工匠区去找夜精灵安尼希尔谈谈。她可以帮助你。',Text0_1_loc4='虽然我很高兴听到你对我的能力充满信心，但我真的没法再教你了。你必须到达纳苏斯的工匠区去找夜精灵安尼希尔谈谈。她可以帮助你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5063; /* Text0_0: Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you. */ /* Text0_1: Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='即使轻微地改变药剂的成份也能使它发生根本的变化。耐心和精确，年轻人:他们会让你在所有行业都受益匪浅。',Text0_1_loc4='即使轻微地改变药剂的成份也能使它发生根本的变化。耐心和精确，年轻人:他们会让你在所有行业都受益匪浅。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5064; /* Text0_0: Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life. */ /* Text0_1: Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我制造药剂的技能在你之下。你应该与那边的安尼希尔谈谈。她会明白你需要进一步的培训。',Text0_1_loc4='我制造药剂的技能在你之下。你应该与那边的安尼希尔谈谈。她会明白你需要进一步的培训。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5065; /* Text0_0: My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction. */ /* Text0_1: My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，又回到年轻的时候了，还有第一次发现药剂的时候。谢谢你恢复我的记忆，$N。去跟那边的米拉·法拉科纳分享那份年轻的热情吧。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，又回到年轻的时候了，还有第一次发现药剂的时候。谢谢你恢复我的记忆，$N。去跟那边的米拉·法拉科纳分享那份年轻的热情吧。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5067; /* Text0_0: Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there. */ /* Text0_1: Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经用多年学会了很多药剂知识，$N，而那些知识都由你支配。你只需提要求就可以。',Text0_1_loc4='我已经用多年学会了很多药剂知识，$N，而那些知识都由你支配。你只需提要求就可以。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5068; /* Text0_0: I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask. */ /* Text0_1: I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很忙，$N。告诉伍特去处理一切。那个年轻人整天都焦虑不安的。他大部分时间都处於这种状态，像是要做些什麽。' WHERE entry=5069; /* Text0_0: I\'m busy, $N. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he\'s going to hurt something. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='见到你是我的荣幸，$N，但是你在配制药水方面比我厉害。去幽暗城 链金房找亡灵赫伯特·哈尔希医生。他能帮助你。' WHERE entry=5070; /* Text0_0: I\'m honored to meet you, $N, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你找错兽人了。我不训练新手。去问问那边的小伍特……谦虚一点。' WHERE entry=5072; /* Text0_0: You\'re talking to the wrong orc. I don\'t train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='另一名学生，是吗?好吧。我看看有什麽能帮助你的。' WHERE entry=5073; /* Text0_0: Another student, eh? All right. I\'ll see what I can do to help you out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='格里克斯和我达成一项共识:他给我供货，而我给他钱。这是很认真的!那个海贼为了一小袋皱皱巴巴的皇血草收我多少钱...足够把一个成年的地精弄哭了。' WHERE entry=5074; /* Text0_0: Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it\'s enough to make a grown goblin cry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我有许多处方可供选择，我还可以为你打折!' WHERE entry=5075; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got plenty of great recipes for you to take a look at, and at discounted prices, too! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做得比我要好!你需要一个经验比我还要多的人。那就是安尼希尔，一个在达纳苏斯工匠区生活的夜精灵女士。' WHERE entry=5078; /* Text0_0: You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一次看见亡灵时，我哭了，我无法想像他们的恐惧和孤寂。大地之母在我耳边吟唱，她告诉我:「拯救他们吧。」',Text0_1_loc4='第一次看见亡灵时，我哭了，我无法想像他们的恐惧和孤寂。大地之母在我耳边吟唱，她告诉我:「拯救他们吧。」',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5079; /* Text0_0: When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them." */ /* Text0_1: When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them." */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你难道感觉不到大地之母为了她所丢失的孩子，也就是亡灵们，而出现的苦恼吗?快些说，$N。每一秒对我都很珍贵。我们必须帮他们找到回归她身边的路!',Text0_1_loc4='你难道感觉不到大地之母为了她所丢失的孩子，也就是亡灵们，而出现的苦恼吗?快些说，$N。每一秒对我都很珍贵。我们必须帮他们找到回归她身边的路!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5080; /* Text0_0: Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her! */ /* Text0_1: Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我们的盟友，也就是亡灵们，在遭受可怕苦难时候，我如果还在这里训练新手，这会让我感到良心不安。请找那边的克瑞谈谈;他目前能够帮你。',Text0_1_loc4='当我们的盟友，也就是亡灵们，在遭受可怕苦难时候，我如果还在这里训练新手，这会让我感到良心不安。请找那边的克瑞谈谈;他目前能够帮你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5081; /* Text0_0: I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你制造药剂的技术已经在我之上。去幽暗城的链金房找亡灵赫伯特·哈尔希医生。他可以继续你的训练，而你也可以亲眼目睹他的人民所遭受的苦难。',Text0_1_loc4='你制造药剂的技术已经在我之上。去幽暗城的链金房找亡灵赫伯特·哈尔希医生。他可以继续你的训练，而你也可以亲眼目睹他的人民所遭受的苦难。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5083; /* Text0_0: Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight. */ /* Text0_1: Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='又来打扰我了。像这样我还能做什麽工作麽?不用回答，我看起来像是很在乎你的回答麽?如果我们要清理这个地方并且扩张我们帝国的话，我需要绝对的安静!' WHERE entry=5084; /* Text0_0: Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don\'t answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don\'t you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要我训练你?别开玩笑了─我们都知道这是不可能的。我可无法胜任。你要是想接受训练的话，就去幽暗城的链金房找被遗忘者赫伯特·哈尔希医生吧。' WHERE entry=5085; /* Text0_0: Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can\'t. It\'s this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别浪费我时间。我从事研究的时间比你的年纪还要大。去跟幽暗城炼金房的亡灵马丁·费尔本谈谈。他或许能传授给你一些基础知识。' WHERE entry=5087; /* Text0_0: Don\'t waste my time. I have research projects older than you. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He\'s a Forsaken who can probably manage to teach you the basics. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='另一名学生。棒极了。这就是林度恩跻身皇家学会从事研究工作的原因，也是我坚持成为一名导师的原因。只要我再获得一枚教学奖章，我的美名便不会被人所遗忘了。' WHERE entry=5088; /* Text0_0: Another student. Wonderful. This is why Lydon belongs to the Royal Society of Snobs and gets to do research, and I\'m stuck being an instructor. If I win another teaching award, I\'ll never live it down! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有奥格诺恩提供所需的供应，我可以不用寻找一株草药就能完成在这里的任务。如果我永远都不用再次看到自然的奇蹟，这就不会很快发生。' WHERE entry=5089; /* Text0_0: With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有可传授给你的知识了。穿过拱门走下斜坡到东南方，找赫伯特·哈尔希医生谈谈。他是个被遗忘者，他能教给你更加高级的技术。' WHERE entry=5090; /* Text0_0: I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你如此大胆地跑来找我，想要接受训练，我对此可不高兴。穿过拱道，沿着坡道向东南方走，跟被遗忘者马丁·费尔本谈谈。他能教你一些基础知识。' WHERE entry=5092; /* Text0_0: I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到这儿来学习的吗?很好。我想要是我教你的话，你不会对我们的联盟造成太多的伤害。只要你一心对付我们的敌人。' WHERE entry=5093; /* Text0_0: Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然每次我都使用了相同的成分，但配制出的药水似乎都达不到预期的治疗效果。这只能得出一个结论:植物发生了变化。我还不清楚具体原因。',Text0_1_loc4='虽然每次我都使用了相同的成分，但配制出的药水似乎都达不到预期的治疗效果。这只能得出一个结论:植物发生了变化。我还不清楚具体原因。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5094; /* Text0_0: This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what. */ /* Text0_1: This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在你该找一位更加渊博的老师了。在菲拉斯的羽月要塞居住着夜精灵凯兰娜·风语。她有聪明的头脑;毫无疑问她能继续教你。',Text0_1_loc4='现在你该找一位更加渊博的老师了。在菲拉斯的羽月要塞居住着夜精灵凯兰娜·风语。她有聪明的头脑;毫无疑问她能继续教你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5095; /* Text0_0: It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further. */ /* Text0_1: It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你制造药剂的技能需要再高超一些才能当我的学生。在此期间，在那边的希尔瓦娜·林月或米拉·法拉科纳可能会帮助你。',Text0_1_loc4='你制造药剂的技能需要再高超一些才能当我的学生。在此期间，在那边的希尔瓦娜·林月或米拉·法拉科纳可能会帮助你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5097; /* Text0_0: Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there. */ /* Text0_1: Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的培训进展很好。你该为你的成就感到自豪。',Text0_1_loc4='你的培训进展很好。你该为你的成就感到自豪。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5098; /* Text0_0: Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments. */ /* Text0_1: Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我和我的同伴正在收集我们所知的致命物质，并在敌人身上测试它们的效果。一旦我收集齐备，我将制造出这世界前所未有的瘟疫。' WHERE entry=5099; /* Text0_0: My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='难以置信。你配制药水的技能已经能跟我匹敌了。我不能再训练你了，去悲伤沼泽找斯通纳德的兽人罗格瓦尔谈谈。他以他的宝刀而闻名。' WHERE entry=5100; /* Text0_0: Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技术太差了，还不能跟我学习。去跟那边的马丁医生谈谈，或者爬上斜坡到东南方去看看马许医生。他们是被遗忘者，可以给你所需的训练。' WHERE entry=5102; /* Text0_0: You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='准备好接受训练了?保持速度，$N。我们要走的路还长着呢。' WHERE entry=5103; /* Text0_0: Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $N. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从前我欢迎过黑暗，因为它是夜晚的姐妹。现在总是漆黑一片，甚至在白天也是这样，而森林迫切需要给养。除非我们快些行动，否则这扩散的荒疫会遍布整个世界。',Text0_1_loc4='从前我欢迎过黑暗，因为它是夜晚的姐妹。现在总是漆黑一片，甚至在白天也是这样，而森林迫切需要给养。除非我们快些行动，否则这扩散的荒疫会遍布整个世界。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5104; /* Text0_0: Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world. */ /* Text0_1: Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来接受药水配制这一技能的训练的吗?要是你认为能从我这儿不费吹灰之力地学到东西的话，你就大错特错了。走吧，在你没有掌握更高技能之前别来找我。',Text0_1_loc4='你是来接受药水配制这一技能的训练的吗?要是你认为能从我这儿不费吹灰之力地学到东西的话，你就大错特错了。走吧，在你没有掌握更高技能之前别来找我。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5105; /* Text0_0: Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill. */ /* Text0_1: Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技能显示你一直喜爱我们的艺术，但是我想看到你所做承诺的进一步证据。我会分配给你一项任务。完成它就会令我满意。',Text0_1_loc4='你的技能显示你一直喜爱我们的艺术，但是我想看到你所做承诺的进一步证据。我会分配给你一项任务。完成它就会令我满意。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5106; /* Text0_0: Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content. */ /* Text0_1: Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大酋长萨尔亲自邀请我到这儿来。我感到非常荣幸，这并不困难。我不要求自己的职务高於斯通纳德。我只想找些生长在这儿的草药。' WHERE entry=5108; /* Text0_0: Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it\'s no hardship. I couldn\'t have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，好吧，我看到你还懂一点做药剂的方法。然而，你是否配做我的学生仍有待察看。我有一项任务交给你。争取给我一个好印象。' WHERE entry=5110; /* Text0_0: Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you\'re worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你胆敢让我培训你，你这可怜虫?你期望什麽，你这个呆头呆脑的乡巴佬，一场关於如何正确使用银叶的讲演?滚出去!你浪费我的时间没把你打个半死算你走运。' WHERE entry=5111; /* Text0_0: How dare you ask me for training, maggot? What were you hoping for, you slack-jawed yokel, a lecture on the proper uses of silverleaf? Out! You\'re lucky I don\'t thrash you senseless for wasting my time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只需做些小调整...我们出发吧!' WHERE entry=5112; /* Text0_0: Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是我能的话，我是会训练你的，但是你需要找个稍微……怎麽说，聪明点的人为你服务吧!去铁炉堡找崔克希·迅移吧。告诉他是布隆克派你去的!' WHERE entry=5113; /* Text0_0: I would train ye if I could, but ye need the services of someone a bit more... what\'s the word? Brainy! Look for Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge. Tell \'er Bronk sent ye! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想成为工程师，是吗?嗯，穆拉丁保佑你，你来对地方了!' WHERE entry=5114; /* Text0_0: Lookin\' to be an engineer, eh? Well, by Muradin, ye\'ve come to the right place! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的旋转诱饵在哪儿?我刚刚还把它放在这附近的……' WHERE entry=5115; /* Text0_0: Where\'s my spinner? I just had it here somewhere... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你目前的智慧超出了我的指导能力。你该找我在铁炉堡的侏儒同伴崔克希·迅移询问一下!' WHERE entry=5116; /* Text0_0: Your current aptitude exceeds my instructional capabilities. You should enquire further with my fellow Gnome Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很高兴能在你事业开始的时候帮上忙，!让我们抓紧纺纱机，开始吧……' WHERE entry=5117; /* Text0_0: I would be delighted to aid you in the commencement of your pursuit! Let me grab my spinner and we\'ll get started... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说新型的极速6000型很快就要开下生产线了。我几乎不能抑制激动的心情!',Text0_1_loc4='我听说新型的极速6000型很快就要开下生产线了。我几乎不能抑制激动的心情!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5118; /* Text0_0: I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement! */ /* Text0_1: I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呃……虽然我不愿承认，但是你要想继续训练的话就必须跟我的姐妹谈谈。目前来说……我知道的没她多!她乘坐火箭车四处巡查。',Text0_1_loc4='呃……虽然我不愿承认，但是你要想继续训练的话就必须跟我的姐妹谈谈。目前来说……我知道的没她多!她乘坐火箭车四处巡查。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5119; /* Text0_0: Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car. */ /* Text0_1: Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我愿意教你!要让我的姐姐看看她不是唯一了解工程学的人……',Text0_1_loc4='我愿意教你!要让我的姐姐看看她不是唯一了解工程学的人……',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5120; /* Text0_0: I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering... */ /* Text0_1: I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好!我的名字是洁娜!你呢?',Text0_1_loc4='你好!我的名字是洁娜!你呢?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5121; /* Text0_0: Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you? */ /* Text0_1: Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，你还有很多东西要学。我会教给你我所学的全部知识，但是我自己也在学习!你为什麽不找铁炉堡的特里克希谈谈，她会帮你进修的!',Text0_1_loc4='哦，你还有很多东西要学。我会教给你我所学的全部知识，但是我自己也在学习!你为什麽不找铁炉堡的特里克希谈谈，她会帮你进修的!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5122; /* Text0_0: Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education! */ /* Text0_1: Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想学习?跟着我?太棒了!唯一比装配子弹和爆裂物装置有趣的事情就是与别人分享那种知识!我们开始吧!',Text0_1_loc4='你想学习?跟着我?太棒了!唯一比装配子弹和爆裂物装置有趣的事情就是与别人分享那种知识!我们开始吧!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5123; /* Text0_0: You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started! */ /* Text0_1: You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，多麽美好的一天啊!真该炸点什麽东西。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，多麽美好的一天啊!真该炸点什麽东西。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5124; /* Text0_0: Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up! */ /* Text0_1: Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要开始学习一些我的专门技术之外的东西!跟那边帐篷前面的利廉姆·火轴谈谈。他会让你步入正轨的!',Text0_1_loc4='你需要开始学习一些我的专门技术之外的东西!跟那边帐篷前面的利廉姆·火轴谈谈。他会让你步入正轨的!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5125; /* Text0_0: You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course! */ /* Text0_1: You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这种工作胆小鬼做不了的。我有个叔叔丢了一只手!可怜的老胖子……无论如何，如果你还感兴趣我或许能给你看些东西?',Text0_1_loc4='这种工作胆小鬼做不了的。我有个叔叔丢了一只手!可怜的老胖子……无论如何，如果你还感兴趣我或许能给你看些东西?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5126; /* Text0_0: This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things. */ /* Text0_1: This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什麽?你要什麽东西?' WHERE entry=5127; /* Text0_0: What? You want something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能帮助你!你会遇到比我更精於此道的人!你是联盟的人，你得跟暴风城的利廉姆·火轴谈谈。' WHERE entry=5128; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help ya\'! You\'re ready to see someone who\'s been at it longer than I have! Let\'s see... you\'re an Alliance type, so you need to talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我有些东西要给你看看。我们来看一下你做得怎麽样，或许你会令我吃惊的!' WHERE entry=5129; /* Text0_0: Yeah, I\'ll show you a few things. We\'ll see how you do, maybe you\'ll surprise me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='(吸气声，吸气声)你闻到了吗?你难道不是只喜欢油脂的气味吗?' WHERE entry=5130; /* Text0_0: (Sniff, sniff) You smell that? Don\'t you just LOVE the smell of grease? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怕你已经超出我的范围了，朋友，你应该去拜访奥格瑞玛的诺格，他会教你达到下个级别的。' WHERE entry=5131; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid you\'re out of my league, friend! You should go see Nogg in Orgrimmar, he\'ll take you to the next level! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望组建队伍。当然，我更希望扩大队伍!' WHERE entry=5133; /* Text0_0: I like to build stuff. Of course, I like to blow stuff up even more! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道谁能真正让你开阔见识吗?诺格!去奥格玛可以找到他。' WHERE entry=5134; /* Text0_0: You know who can really show you some things? Nogg! You go find him in Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我知道一些。要我告诉你吗?' WHERE entry=5135; /* Text0_0: I know a few things. You want me to show you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谁说兽人不聪明?当工程师很费脑筋的!' WHERE entry=5136; /* Text0_0: Who says Orcs aren\'t smart? It takes a lot of brains to be an engineer! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道谁是真正聪明的人吗?诺格!甚至比我还要聪明。你去告诉诺格是桑德派你来的!你可以在那边的控制台那里找到他。' WHERE entry=5137; /* Text0_0: You know who\'s really smart? Nogg! Smarter than me, even. You go tell Nogg Thund sent you! You can find him by the control panel over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为你很聪明吗?你认为你得到了吗?让我们查明真相!' WHERE entry=5138; /* Text0_0: You think you\'re smart enough? You think you got what it takes? Let\'s find out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='黑暗女王说过，在这场战争中，知识是我们最强大的武器。' WHERE entry=5139; /* Text0_0: The Dark Lady has said that knowledge will be our greatest weapon in this war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好迎接更大的挑战了!见见我右边的弗兰克林·洛伊德。从现在开始他会指导你。' WHERE entry=5140; /* Text0_0: You are ready for greater things! See Franklin Lloyd, to my right. He will guide you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='工程学能赋予你击败敌人的技能和知识!让我看看你是如何做的?' WHERE entry=5141; /* Text0_0: Engineering will provide you with the skills and knowledge to dismantle your opponents! Let me show you how... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我忙死了，不会跟陌生人讲话的!几乎从来不...' WHERE entry=5142; /* Text0_0: I\'m never too busy to speak to a stranger! Almost never, anyway... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在努力上进?在这点上你已经超过我了!你应该与铁炉堡的宾斯匹德谈话!(他会?她会?)让你见识那些我所做不到的!' WHERE entry=5143; /* Text0_0: You\'re working your way up??? higher than me, at this point! You should talk to Springspindle Fizzlegear in Ironforge! He\'ll show you more than I ever could! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以教你一些诀窍……如果你不介意先帮我做些事情的话。' WHERE entry=5144; /* Text0_0: I can show you a few tricks... if you don\'t mind doing a little something first, that is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯??? 好吧，我不能帮助你! 你必须先学习。 为什么不去暴风城看看斯普莱特!' WHERE entry=5145; /* Text0_0: Hmm well, I can\'t help you quite yet! You have to learn the basics first. Why don\'t you go see Sprite Jumpsprocket in Stormwind! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太棒了!难道你不是一个勤奋的人吗?好的，让我们开始吧，行吗?' WHERE entry=5146; /* Text0_0: Fantastic! Aren\'t you the industrious one? Well, let\'s get started, shall we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我看看...14加7，得1进2...是吗?' WHERE entry=5147; /* Text0_0: Let\'s see... fourteen plus seven, carry the two... oh, yes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，你学习速度蛮快的!我没办法教你更多知识了，但是宾斯匹德可以!你可以在铁炉堡里找到他。祝你好运!' WHERE entry=5148; /* Text0_0: Well, you\'re just zooming right along! I can\'t teach you anything you don\'t already know, but Springspindle Fizzlegear sure can! You can find Sprinspindle in Ironforge. Good luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='成交!我会将我所知的传授给你，但是在那之前我要你替我执行一个小任务。' WHERE entry=5149; /* Text0_0: Quid pro quo! I\'ll teach you what I know, but first I want you to perform a small task? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以马上跟我学习?但时机不到!为什麽你不从跟我右边的斯普莱特谈话开始呢。你适应以后再来找我!' WHERE entry=5150; /* Text0_0: You can learn from me in time, but not yet! Why don\'t you start out by talking to Sprite Jumpsprocket to my right here. You can check in with me after you\'ve gotten your feet wet! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你当然不会失望!现在既然我们已经把那个清除掉,你可以下达指令了!' WHERE entry=5151; /* Text0_0: You certainly did not disappoint! Now that we\'ve gotten that out of the way, your instruction may begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的二十英尺高的火鸡烤肉架的计画快要完成了!现在我需要的就是一只二十英尺高的火鸡了……',Text0_1_loc4='我的二十英尺高的火鸡烤肉架的计画快要完成了!现在我需要的就是一只二十英尺高的火鸡了……',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5152; /* Text0_0: The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey... */ /* Text0_1: The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要告诉任何人我说过，就当我什麽都不知道!如果你还想学习，你应该与店主宾斯匹德谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='不要告诉任何人我说过，就当我什麽都不知道!如果你还想学习，你应该与店主宾斯匹德谈谈。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5153; /* Text0_0: Don\'t tell anyone else I said this, but even I don\'t know everything! If you want to keep learning, you should talk to the owner of the shop, Springspindle Fizzlegear. */ /* Text0_1: Don\'t tell anyone else I said this, but even I don\'t know everything! If you want to keep learning, you should talk to the owner of the shop, Springspindle Fizzlegear. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我袒露秘密之前，你得证明自己的价值!我会对你进行测试的。',Text0_1_loc4='在我袒露秘密之前，你得证明自己的价值!我会对你进行测试的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5154; /* Text0_0: You\'ll need to prove your worthiness before I go giving away my secrets! I\'ve got just the test for you... */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll need to prove your worthiness before I go giving away my secrets! I\'ve got just the test for you... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠近点，但是不要抽雪茄!我恐怕你必须得先跟我的妹妹洁娜谈谈。当她领你复习完基础知识再回来找我，我那时就会让你见识真正有趣的东西!',Text0_1_loc4='靠近点，但是不要抽雪茄!我恐怕你必须得先跟我的妹妹洁娜谈谈。当她领你复习完基础知识再回来找我，我那时就会让你见识真正有趣的东西!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5155; /* Text0_0: Close, but no cigar! I\'m afraid you\'ll have to talk to my sis, Jemma first. After she\'s gone over the basics with you, come see me and I\'ll show you the juicy stuff! */ /* Text0_1: Close, but no cigar! I\'m afraid you\'ll have to talk to my sis, Jemma first. After she\'s gone over the basics with you, come see me and I\'ll show you the juicy stuff! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对一个初学者来说还不坏!我猜给你看些东西也不会对我有什麽损失……',Text0_1_loc4='对一个初学者来说还不坏!我猜给你看些东西也不会对我有什麽损失……',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5156; /* Text0_0: Not bad, for a beginner! I guess it couldn\'t hurt for me to show you a few things... */ /* Text0_1: Not bad, for a beginner! I guess it couldn\'t hurt for me to show you a few things... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是离天黑还有些时间的话……' WHERE entry=5157; /* Text0_0: If there were just a few more hours in a day... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你赢得了到一个更高级的导师那里学习的权利。去见见我那边的朋友罗克希克。' WHERE entry=5158; /* Text0_0: You have earned the privilege of training with a higher instructor. Go see my pal Roxxik there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='每天都是考验，这天也不例外。如果你通过这次测试，我会教你一些知识……' WHERE entry=5159; /* Text0_0: Every day is a test, and this day is no different. If you pass this test, I will share some of my knowledge... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你还没有资格接受我的培训。先去见见桑德，就在那张桌子旁边。当他说你可以了再来找我!' WHERE entry=5160; /* Text0_0: You have not yet earned the right to train with me. See Thund first, over by the table. Come back when he says you\'re ready! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经通过测试了，干得好!对你的培训可以继续了。' WHERE entry=5161; /* Text0_0: You have passed your test, well done! Your training may now continue. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可没时间闲谈，我是个专业人士!' WHERE entry=5162; /* Text0_0: I don\'t have time for idle gossip, I\'m a professional! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为我能教给你什麽?罗克希克比我更适合做你的老师。你可以在奥格玛找到他。出发吧。' WHERE entry=5163; /* Text0_0: What do you think I could teach you? Roxxik would do a much better job. You can find him in Orgrimmar. Now be off! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们看看你的能力，好吗?要是你按要求完成任务，我会乐意教你的!' WHERE entry=5164; /* Text0_0: Let\'s see how competent you are, shall we? If you perform this task to my liking, I\'ll spend the time to teach you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们彼此都在浪费时间!如果你想接受训练的话，就去找格拉哈姆·范·塔伦吧!他就站在右边。' WHERE entry=5165; /* Text0_0: This is a waste of time, mine and yours! Go see Graham Van Talen if you want to begin your instruction! He\'s standing to my left over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是我计算正确的话，这车轮很快就会作废的!' WHERE entry=5167; /* Text0_0: If my calculations are correct, the wheel will soon be obsolete! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你确实投注了很多心力於你的训练当中。如果你想要得到更多的知识，你就必须前往沙漠。去找到加基森的巴兹克·布拉斯温!' WHERE entry=5168; /* Text0_0: You have certainly come a long way in your training. There is only one instructor who can train you further. Find Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我要教你的东西会让你头脑混乱的!当你学到足够的知识后再来找我吧!' WHERE entry=5170; /* Text0_0: The things I would teach you would turn your brain to jelly! Come back when you\'ve learned sufficiently! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好，你已经证明了你自己!现在进入下一阶段的授课……' WHERE entry=5171; /* Text0_0: Excellent, you have proven yourself worthy! Now for the next phase of your instruction... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有时，连我自己都感到惊讶!' WHERE entry=5172; /* Text0_0: Sometimes I surprise even myself! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有什麽可以教你的啦!如果有人比我知道得多……等等，有啦!去加基森找巴兹克·布拉斯温吧。' WHERE entry=5173; /* Text0_0: I can\'t teach what I don\'t know! If only there was someone else who knew more than I do... wait, there is! Go see Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好的尝试，但是在训练之前，你还需要进行更多的锻炼!回到战壕!' WHERE entry=5175; /* Text0_0: Nice try, but you\'ll need some more experience before training with me! Back to the trenches! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好!无论其他人怎麽说，我想我对你的看法是正确的。哈哈!我是开玩笑的!好吧，开始上课?' WHERE entry=5176; /* Text0_0: Nice going! I knew I was right about you, no matter what those other people said. Ha! I\'m kidding! Okay, on with your lessons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一直在研究在大城市间通过地下通道运送石油的方法，但是每个人都认为我是在做白日梦。' WHERE entry=5177; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been working on a way to transport oil underground between major cities, but everyone tells me it\'s a pipe dream. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='给你看看你得到了什麽!我承诺，你不会有遗憾的!' WHERE entry=5179; /* Text0_0: Show me what you got! You won\'t be sorry, I promise! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我从不拒绝那些已经准备好跟我一同训练的人。不幸的是，你不是!你还像个小孩!' WHERE entry=5180; /* Text0_0: I would never turn away someone who\'s ready to train with me. Unfortunately, you\'re not! You\'ve still got a ways to go kid! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，旅人!是什麽风把你吹来的?',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎，旅人!是什麽风把你吹来的?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5181; /* Text0_0: Hail, traveler! What brings you to my doorstep? */ /* Text0_1: Hail, traveler! What brings you to my doorstep? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我担心对有你这样经验的人没什麽可教的。但是你还有其他方法。去找那边柜台后面的鲁坎·考迪尔谈谈。他会指引你通过旅行的下一个阶段。',Text0_1_loc4='我担心对有你这样经验的人没什麽可教的。但是你还有其他方法。去找那边柜台后面的鲁坎·考迪尔谈谈。他会指引你通过旅行的下一个阶段。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5182; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid I have nothing to teach to someone with your experience. But you haven\'t reached the end of the road yet. Speak to Lucan Cordell, behind the counter there. He\'ll guide you through the next phase of your journey. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m afraid I have nothing to teach to someone with your experience. But you haven\'t reached the end of the road yet. Speak to Lucan Cordell, behind the counter there. He\'ll guide you through the next phase of your journey. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯……你看起来很有能耐。如果你真想学习的话，那麽没有什麽能阻挡你!我会指引你通过漫长而硕果丰盛的道路上的第一步。',Text0_1_loc4='嗯……你看起来很有能耐。如果你真想学习的话，那麽没有什麽能阻挡你!我会指引你通过漫长而硕果丰盛的道路上的第一步。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5183; /* Text0_0: Hmm... well you seem capable enough. If you truly desire to learn, then nothing will stand in your way! I will guide you through your first steps on what I hope will be a long and fulfilling path. */ /* Text0_1: Hmm... well you seem capable enough. If you truly desire to learn, then nothing will stand in your way! I will guide you through your first steps on what I hope will be a long and fulfilling path. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='除了铁锤和熔炉外还有许多方法能使钢铁更坚固，年轻的漫游者。' WHERE entry=5184; /* Text0_0: There are ways to strengthen steel beyond the hammer and forge, young wanderer. Care to learn more? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你确实是个不错的附魔师!现在你该继续了。我想让你与楼上的吉布·草须谈谈。他人有些古怪，但是他会继续指引你!' WHERE entry=5185; /* Text0_0: Ye\'re a fine enchanter indeed! Now it\'s time fer ye to move on. I want ye to talk to Gimble Thistlefuzz, upstairs. He\'s a bit of a character, but he\'ll steer ye in the right direction from here on out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你是个好奇的人，是吗?太好了!听仔细了，这也许能在恶劣的环境下保护好你的皮肤!' WHERE entry=5186; /* Text0_0: Ah, ye\'re an inquisitive one, are ye\'? Excellent! Pay close attention, this just might save yer skin when the goin\' gets rough! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='女神已经赐予我智慧，陌生人。如果那是她的意愿，我将会把它传给你。',Text0_1_loc4='女神已经赐予我智慧，陌生人。如果那是她的意愿，我将会把它传给你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5187; /* Text0_0: The Goddess has granted me wisdom, stranger. If it is her will, I shall pass it on to you. */ /* Text0_1: The Goddess has granted me wisdom, stranger. If it is her will, I shall pass it on to you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技能已经非我能及。现在你该接受新的挑战了。塔兰丹会帮你准备。他就站在那里的桌子旁边。',Text0_1_loc4='你的技能已经非我能及。现在你该接受新的挑战了。塔兰丹会帮你准备。他就站在那里的桌子旁边。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5188; /* Text0_0: Your skills are beyond my reach. It is time for you to face new challenges. Taladan will help you prepare. He is standing by the table there. */ /* Text0_1: Your skills are beyond my reach. It is time for you to face new challenges. Taladan will help you prepare. He is standing by the table there. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会尽我所能教你。每一节课都是女神亲自给你的礼物。正确使用她的礼物，你就会无往不胜。',Text0_1_loc4='我会尽我所能教你。每一节课都是女神亲自给你的礼物。正确使用她的礼物，你就会无往不胜。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5189; /* Text0_0: I will teach you what I can. Each lesson is a gift from the Goddess herself. Use her gifts wisely, and you shall not falter. */ /* Text0_1: I will teach you what I can. Each lesson is a gift from the Goddess herself. Use her gifts wisely, and you shall not falter. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='月神的秘密很多，但是它们不能让任何人知道。',Text0_1_loc4='月神的秘密很多，但是它们不能让任何人知道。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5190; /* Text0_0: Elune\'s secrets are many, but they are not to be shared with just anyone. */ /* Text0_1: Elune\'s secrets are many, but they are not to be shared with just anyone. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在附魔方面的知识真是很出色。如果你愿意的话，还有很多要学的。跟塔兰丹谈谈，他在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text0_1_loc4='你在附魔方面的知识真是很出色。如果你愿意的话，还有很多要学的。跟塔兰丹谈谈，他在达纳苏斯的工匠区。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5191; /* Text0_0: You have truly accelled in your knowledge of enchanting. There is much more to learn, if you are willing. Speak to Taladan, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: You have truly accelled in your knowledge of enchanting. There is much more to learn, if you are willing. Speak to Taladan, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='开阔你的视野，流浪者，我们马上开始。',Text0_1_loc4='开阔你的视野，流浪者，我们马上开始。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5192; /* Text0_0: Open your mind, wanderer, and we shall begin. */ /* Text0_1: Open your mind, wanderer, and we shall begin. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='陌生人，我没有时间浪费啦。说说你的事儿吧，要麽就离开!' WHERE entry=5193; /* Text0_0: I do not have time to waste, stranger. State your business or be off! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呃，你进展到这个程度了吗?去那边的书架找拉文尼亚·克洛文。要是你没把事情搞糟，或许你能学到更多知识。' WHERE entry=5194; /* Text0_0: Eh, well you\'ve made it this far... go see Lavinia Crowe by the other bookshelf there. If you don\'t mess things up with her, maybe you can learn some more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来不怎麽像我，但谁知道呢，可能有一个附魔师藏在那里的什麽地方!',Text0_1_loc4='你看起来不怎麽像我，但谁知道呢，可能有一个附魔师藏在那里的什麽地方!' WHERE entry=5195; /* Text0_0: You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere! */ /* Text0_1: You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我最不愿放弃的就是在这样的日子里到开阔的大草原上……但我的职责约束着我。' WHERE entry=5196; /* Text0_0: What I wouldn\'t give to be out on the open plains on a day like this... but my duty binds me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能再教你什麽啦。但是，我父亲的知识远胜於我。进去跟他谈谈。祝你好运!' WHERE entry=5197; /* Text0_0: I cannot teach you anything you don\'t already know. However, the knowledge of my father far surpasses my own. Go inside and speak to him. Good luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只要有耐心和决心，很多秘密都是有可能解开的。现在，让我们开始吧……' WHERE entry=5198; /* Text0_0: There are many secrets that may be unlocked with patience and determination. Now, let us begin... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好!陌生人，你在找什麽?' WHERE entry=5199; /* Text0_0: Throm-ka! What you looking for, stranger? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来错地方了。去找那边的专家古丹谈谈。你可以从他那儿学到更多东西。' WHERE entry=5200; /* Text0_0: You come to wrong place. Talk to the expert Godan over there. You learn more from him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战死沙场是件光荣的事儿!但是，若是你能利用我教你的东西，或许你不会死得那麽快，嗯?' WHERE entry=5201; /* Text0_0: To die in battle is glorious! But, with what I teach you, maybe you not die so quickly, hm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁?你想从我这儿得到什麽?' WHERE entry=5202; /* Text0_0: Who are you? What do you want from me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看起来像什麽，附魔师普巴尔?你的技能还需要附魔大师的指导!去阿祖拉之塔找基塔·费温德。' WHERE entry=5203; /* Text0_0: What do I look like, the Grand Poobah of enchanters? Your skills require the guidance of an Artisan! Go find Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太好了，我们开始吧……哈!你受骗了!你当然不会认为是那麽简单吧。你需要像其他人一样证明你的勇气!' WHERE entry=5204; /* Text0_0: Great, let\'s get started... ha! Fooled you! Surely you didn\'t think it would be that simple. You\'ll need to prove your mettle just like everyone else! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在开玩笑，是吗?我认为你在寻找那个矮家伙，索恩斯·火石。他就在楼下。现在快逃吧!' WHERE entry=5205; /* Text0_0: You\'re joking, right? I believe you\'re looking for the OTHER short fellow, Thonys Pillarstone. He\'s downstairs. Now skedaddle! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧，好吧？？不要骄傲自大！既然你已经证明自己的能力，那么现在我们可以开始了！' WHERE entry=5206; /* Text0_0: Okay, well??? don\'t get cocky! Since you have demonstrated  your competence though, we may now begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你带着那东西，我会很高兴地为你指路的。' WHERE entry=5207; /* Text0_0: If you have what it takes, I will be happy to show you the way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个真正的专家知道他的局限，而我并不羞於承认你的技能超越了我。我想让你到阿祖拉之塔拜访基塔·费温德。她很有声誉。' WHERE entry=5208; /* Text0_0: A true professional know his limitations, and I\'m not ashamed to admit that your skills exceed mine. I want you to pay a visit to Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. She is well-renowned, and with good reason. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来很自信。我想你不会介意测试一下你的技术吧?' WHERE entry=5209; /* Text0_0: You seem confident. Surely you wouldn\'t mind a test of your skills? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你还没有准备好。找贝蒂·奎恩谈谈，他就站在那边的楼梯旁边。当你提高以后再来找我。' WHERE entry=5210; /* Text0_0: You are not ready. Speak to Betty Quinn, she\'s standing by the stairs over there. Return to me when you have achieved a higher enlightenment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='旅人，你有充分的理由让自己充满信心。现在你真正的培训开始了!' WHERE entry=5211; /* Text0_0: Your confidence is well-founded, traveler. Now your true education may begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想猎杀纳迦，你需要所能获得的所有帮助。水底有裂缝，能产生足够的气泡供你在水下呼吸。向水面游动，就能利用这些气泡了。' WHERE entry=5212; /* Text0_0: If you seek to hunt naga, then you will need all the help you can get. Deep in the water you can find bubbly fissures that produce enough air bubbles that will allow you to breath underwater. Swim up close so that you can use the bubbles. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我确实有能力对那些有价值的人进行教学。你是这样的人吗?' WHERE entry=5213; /* Text0_0: It is true I have skills to teach to those who are worthy. Would that be you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是一个非常棒的附魔师。我恐怕已经超出我的才能了。到阿祖拉之塔找到基塔·费温德。现在只有她才配作你的导师。' WHERE entry=5214; /* Text0_0: You are an exceptional enchanter. Beyond my talents as a teacher, I fear. Seek out Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. Only she can qualify as your instructor now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我相信你能胜任这项任务?你要接受挑战吗?' WHERE entry=5215; /* Text0_0: I believe you are up to this task, will you accept the challenge? */
