UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='明显莫特并没有派你到我这儿来。他知道得很清楚。你还无法理解我能传授给你的知识。去外面找我的儿子莫特，他会对你进行训练的。' WHERE entry=5226; /* Text0_0: Surely Mot didn\'t send you to me? He knows better. You are not yet capable of understanding what I would teach you. See my son Mot, just outside there, and finish training with him. */
