UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它怎麽样了?我喜欢皮革的味道;你不喜欢吗?',Text0_1_loc4='它怎麽样了?我喜欢皮革的味道;你不喜欢吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5259; /* Text0_0: How\'s it going? I love the smell of leather; don\'t you? */ /* Text0_1: How\'s it going? I love the smell of leather; don\'t you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经了解到很多关於时尚的东西。现在那不过就是掌握制革技巧罢了。西蒙能帮助学习制革的。' WHERE entry=5260; /* Text0_0: I already know a lot about style. Now it\'s just a matter of mastering the techniques for working with leather. Good thing Simon\'s a real sport about helping me learn them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='除了对色彩和细节的鉴别能力外，我没有什麽可以教你的。跟西蒙·坦纳尔谈谈;他知道很多制皮的高级技能。' WHERE entry=5261; /* Text0_0: There\'s nothing I can teach you, other than maybe a better eye for color and detail. Talk to Simon Tanner over there; he knows a lot of advanced techniques for working with leather. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这套装备真的让我眼前一亮，你觉得呢?显然，我有多种技能可以使用，我可以将贸易的一些诀窍与你分享。听好了。' WHERE entry=5262; /* Text0_0: This outfit really brings out the blue in my eyes, don\'t you think? It should be obvious I have plenty of skill to go around, so I can afford to share a few of my tricks of the trade. Listen up, okay? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到我们家，$N。拉德纳尔和我没什麽东西拿给你，但是我们会尽最大盛情欢迎你。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到我们家，$N。拉德纳尔和我没什麽东西拿给你，但是我们会尽最大盛情欢迎你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5263; /* Text0_0: Welcome to our home, $N. Radnaal and I have little to offer, but you are welcome to what hospitality we can provide. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to our home, $N. Radnaal and I have little to offer, but you are welcome to what hospitality we can provide. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很抱歉，但你已经学会我所知的一切了。然而，夜精灵法多恩可以提供给你进一步的培训。你可以到达纳苏斯的工匠区找他。',Text0_1_loc4='我很抱歉，但你已经学会我所知的一切了。然而，夜精灵法多恩可以提供给你进一步的培训。你可以到达纳苏斯的工匠区找他。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5264; /* Text0_0: My apologies, but you have already learned everything I know. The night elf Faldron could offer you further training, however. Look for him in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: My apologies, but you have already learned everything I know. The night elf Faldron could offer you further training, however. Look for him in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要把你的针法做得更小些，$N。这样你的箭袋和弹药包就不会有东西掉出来。还有，没有人喜欢穿着鼓鼓囊囊的外套的。',Text0_1_loc4='你要把你的针法做得更小些，$N。这样你的箭袋和弹药包就不会有东西掉出来。还有，没有人喜欢穿着鼓鼓囊囊的外套的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5265; /* Text0_0: You need to make your stitches smaller, $N. Fewer items will slip out of your quivers and ammo pouches. Besides, no one likes a lumpy tunic. */ /* Text0_1: You need to make your stitches smaller, $N. Fewer items will slip out of your quivers and ammo pouches. Besides, no one likes a lumpy tunic. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你对皮革缝纫感兴趣，那你算来对地方了。法多恩和泰龙尼斯都是真正的艺术家，而我希望能从他们那里多学些知识。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你对皮革缝纫感兴趣，那你算来对地方了。法多恩和泰龙尼斯都是真正的艺术家，而我希望能从他们那里多学些知识。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5273; /* Text0_0: If you\'re interested in sewing with leather, you\'ve certainly come to the right place. Faldron and Telonis are true artists, and I hope to learn much from them. */ /* Text0_1: If you\'re interested in sewing with leather, you\'ve certainly come to the right place. Faldron and Telonis are true artists, and I hope to learn much from them. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，我很抱歉，但是对於皮革你知道的比我要多。如果你想多学些知识的话去找那边的法多恩谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='哦，我很抱歉，但是对於皮革你知道的比我要多。如果你想多学些知识的话去找那边的法多恩谈谈。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5274; /* Text0_0: Oh, I\'m sorry, but you know more about leather than I do at this point. Talk to Faldron over there if you wish to learn more. */ /* Text0_1: Oh, I\'m sorry, but you know more about leather than I do at this point. Talk to Faldron over there if you wish to learn more. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在达纳苏斯这里真是太令人兴奋了，到处都是才华横溢的人们!我这才知道我会让我的家人感到骄傲的。或许如果我幸运的话，哨兵们会请我加入他们前线的军队的!',Text0_1_loc4='在达纳苏斯这里真是太令人兴奋了，到处都是才华横溢的人们!我这才知道我会让我的家人感到骄傲的。或许如果我幸运的话，哨兵们会请我加入他们前线的军队的!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5275; /* Text0_0: It\'s so exciting to be here in Darnassus, surrounded by talented people! I just know I\'m going to make my family proud. Maybe if I\'m really lucky, the Sentinels will ask me to join their forces on the front! */ /* Text0_1: It\'s so exciting to be here in Darnassus, surrounded by talented people! I just know I\'m going to make my family proud. Maybe if I\'m really lucky, the Sentinels will ask me to join their forces on the front! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='还没准备好收拾这张皮。我希望做皮革不要花太多时间。肯定有办法削减等待的时间。这对我身体不太好，你知道吗?',Text0_1_loc4='还没准备好收拾这张皮。我希望做皮革不要花太多时间。肯定有办法削减等待的时间。这对我身体不太好，你知道吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5276; /* Text0_0: This hide isn\'t ready to work with yet. I wish it didn\'t take so long to make leather. There has to be some way to cut down on all this waiting. It can\'t be good for my health, you know? */ /* Text0_1: This hide isn\'t ready to work with yet. I wish it didn\'t take so long to make leather. There has to be some way to cut down on all this waiting. It can\'t be good for my health, you know? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，运气真坏!我的技能对你来说一无是处。呃。跟那边的费布·钢轴谈谈吧。他接触皮革的时间比我长多了。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，运气真坏!我的技能对你来说一无是处。呃。跟那边的费布·钢轴谈谈吧。他接触皮革的时间比我长多了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5277; /* Text0_0: Aww, what rotten luck! My skills aren\'t good enough to be of any use to you. Oh well. Talk to Fimble Finespindle over there by the loom. He\'s been working with leather for longer than I have. */ /* Text0_1: Aww, what rotten luck! My skills aren\'t good enough to be of any use to you. Oh well. Talk to Fimble Finespindle over there by the loom. He\'s been working with leather for longer than I have. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，好啊，在我等待时找些别的事情做!你真是救命菩萨，$N!',Text0_1_loc4='哦，好啊，在我等待时找些别的事情做!你真是救命菩萨，$N!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5278; /* Text0_0: Oh, goody, something else to do while I wait! You\'re a real life-saver, $N! */ /* Text0_1: Oh, goody, something else to do while I wait! You\'re a real life-saver, $N! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你喜欢这地毯吗?我亲自把动物杀死并剥皮的。但愿所有的半人马能被同样容易的击倒。',Text0_1_loc4='你喜欢这地毯吗?我亲自把动物杀死并剥皮的。但愿所有的半人马能被同样容易的击倒。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5279; /* Text0_0: You like the rug? I killed and skinned the beast myself. May all the centaur fall as easily. */ /* Text0_1: You like the rug? I killed and skinned the beast myself. May all the centaur fall as easily. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有东西可传授给你了。要是你想进一步学习制皮技能，就找卡洛雷克交谈。',Text0_1_loc4='我没有东西可传授给你了。要是你想进一步学习制皮技能，就找卡洛雷克交谈。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5280; /* Text0_0: I have nothing more to teach you. Talk to Karolek if you wish to further your leatherworking skills. */ /* Text0_1: I have nothing more to teach you. Talk to Karolek if you wish to further your leatherworking skills. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们不能剥下人类及其联盟的皮，这真糟糕。这些皮都白白浪费掉了。尽管如此，谁想穿着你由此制造出的质地极差的皮革?',Text0_1_loc4='我们不能剥下人类及其联盟的皮，这真糟糕。这些皮都白白浪费掉了。尽管如此，谁想穿着你由此制造出的质地极差的皮革?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5281; /* Text0_0: Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it? */ /* Text0_1: Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='肤质很好。它将你包裹其中。你也许已经注意到我的皮肤不是那麽好。我过去常常担心自己的毛孔。这些日子我几乎不担心皮肤了。在某种程度上，它得到了解放。',Text0_1_loc4='肤质很好。它将你包裹其中。你也许已经注意到我的皮肤不是那麽好。我过去常常担心自己的毛孔。这些日子我几乎不担心皮肤了。在某种程度上，它得到了解放。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5282; /* Text0_0: Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing. */ /* Text0_1: Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经掌握了它的用法。我没有什麽要教你的了，但是找亚瑟·摩尔谈谈，他是在幽暗城盗贼区工作的一位被遗忘者。告诉他是我派你去的。',Text0_1_loc4='你已经掌握了它的用法。我没有什麽要教你的了，但是找亚瑟·摩尔谈谈，他是在幽暗城盗贼区工作的一位被遗忘者。告诉他是我派你去的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5283; /* Text0_0: You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在瘟疫来之前，我对皮革一无所知。现在我的知识可以传授别人了。死亡让我有了很多时间供自己支配。',Text0_1_loc4='在瘟疫来之前，我对皮革一无所知。现在我的知识可以传授别人了。死亡让我有了很多时间供自己支配。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5284; /* Text0_0: Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands. */ /* Text0_1: Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='肉、兽皮、骨头……好的猎人是不会浪费任何东西的。每块兽皮都有利用价值，也许能用来增强盟友的武器装备。单独来看，我们每个人都很强大，但是团结在一起我们就无敌了。' WHERE entry=5285; /* Text0_0: Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally\'s armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经没什麽可教你了。带着大地之母的祝福离开吧。在雷霆崖的中央高原西北方的商店找到牛头人塔恩。愿你得到他智慧的指引。' WHERE entry=5286; /* Text0_0: You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在此繁衍生息，生生死死，数年来大地却亘古不动。因此，这片土地并不属於我们，$N。我们是属於大地的。因此，我们守护着它，没有它我们就无法生存。' WHERE entry=5287; /* Text0_0: We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $N. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们脚下的洞穴中有许多奇异的兽皮，如果你想深入其中探险的话，一定要非常小心，$N。要记住你自己的性命比那些兽皮有价值得多。' WHERE entry=5288; /* Text0_0: The caverns below us are a source of strange and wondrous hides, but you must take care if you venture into their depths, $N. Remember that your own skin is far more valuable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对皮革的理解比我要深刻。可能你应该拜访一下贫瘠之地陶拉祖营地的牛头人克鲁姆·满月。对你这麽聪明的学生他有很多知识要教给你。' WHERE entry=5289; /* Text0_0: Your understanding of leather is deeper than my own. Perhaps you should visit the tauren Krulmoo Fullmoon in Camp Taurajo of the Barrens. He has much knowledge to offer a student of your talents. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='凯恩自己住这儿，他们说。一旦我完成了制作一件合适的礼物，我就会把他找出来。或许他会有智慧的话要对我说。' WHERE entry=5291; /* Text0_0: Cairne himself lives here, they say. Once I have finished crafting a fitting gift, I will seek him out. Perhaps he will have words of wisdom for me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的智慧胜於我，朋友。与这里的塔恩谈话;他对皮革的知识比我要丰富得多。我肯定他会欢迎新学生的。' WHERE entry=5292; /* Text0_0: Your talent is beyond my own, friend. Speak with Tarn here; his knowledge of leather is much greater than mine. I\'m sure he would welcome another student. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在你开始任何工作之前都要洗净双手。皮革被血或尘土玷污了会带走它的自然美。' WHERE entry=5293; /* Text0_0: Cleanse your hands before you begin any project. Staining the leather with blood or dirt would take away from its natural beauty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我从墓穴中爬出来后，我本以为我的家人会热烈地欢迎我。相反，他们把我从村里赶了出去，用一种我听不懂的语言高声尖叫着。' WHERE entry=5294; /* Text0_0: When I clawed my way out of the grave, I thought my family would welcome me with open arms. Instead, they drove me from the village, screaming in a language I could no longer understand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能帮助你，我无法胜任。跟棺材那边的亚瑟·摩尔谈谈。他会为你提供更多的训练的。' WHERE entry=5295; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help you; your work is beyond my own. Talk to Arthur Moore, over there by the coffins. He\'ll be able to train you further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='记住我说的每句话。在打败敌人之前，我们绝对不能放弃学习知识、提高自身能力的机会。增强你的实力，绝不能放松警戒。' WHERE entry=5296; /* Text0_0: Take every word I say and commit it to memory. Until our enemies have been eradicated, we must never shirk a chance to further our knowledge. Reinforce your armor, and never relax your guard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经超越我有限的能力了。到达纳苏斯的工匠区寻找夜精灵安尼希尔。她可以教给你更多知识。我很希望我可以跟你一起去。',Text0_1_loc4='你已经超越我有限的能力了。到达纳苏斯的工匠区寻找夜精灵安尼希尔。她可以教给你更多知识。我很希望我可以跟你一起去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5314; /* Text0_0: You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you. */ /* Text0_1: You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对你来说，我的教学在这个阶段略显深奥了。要是你想学习有关药水的更多知识，就跟泰兰希尔谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='对你来说，我的教学在这个阶段略显深奥了。要是你想学习有关药水的更多知识，就跟泰兰希尔谈谈。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5316; /* Text0_0: My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead. */ /* Text0_1: My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听仔细了，$N，我要传授给你的知识很多。',Text0_1_loc4='听仔细了，$N，我要传授给你的知识很多。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5317; /* Text0_0: Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart. */ /* Text0_1: Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='即使我也有我的局限性!如果你想继续学习的话去找幽暗城的拉文尼亚·克洛文谈谈。' WHERE entry=5318; /* Text0_0: Even I have my limitations! Go talk to Lavinia Crowe in Undercity if you wish to further your training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='还行……训练你是不成问题的。很好!我们开始吧?' WHERE entry=5319; /* Text0_0: Not bad... I suppose training you is not out of the question. Very well! Let\'s begin... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='兰达尔打扮得有些像花花公子，但是他是个可靠的人，他比我向许多学生所说的那样更加值得信赖。尽管如此，我还是不能责备他们想要冒险的想法。' WHERE entry=5320; /* Text0_0: Randal\'s a bit of a dandy, but he\'s dependable, which is more than I can say for a lot of the students I take on. Still, I guess I can\'t blame them for wanting a bit of adventure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，我已经没有什麽可以教给你的了。如果你还想学的话，就去达纳苏斯的工匠区找泰龙尼斯吧。我听说他相当有才能。' WHERE entry=5321; /* Text0_0: Sorry, but you\'ve reached the limit of what I can teach. If you want to learn more, go see Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s pretty talented, so I hear. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你接受更多训练以后再回来找我。在那边的兰达尔·沃斯可以帮你。' WHERE entry=5323; /* Text0_0: Come back to me when you\'ve had more training. Randal Worth over there can help you with that. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，我想我可以再收一个学生。好吧，不要傻站在那里。告诉我你想学什麽。' WHERE entry=5324; /* Text0_0: Hmm, I guess I can take on another student. Well, don\'t just stand there. Tell me what you\'re looking to learn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达丽亚娜答应了，但是她的精力如此充沛，很难让她安静下来仔细的聆听。她气力十足又机灵敏捷，我恐怕她不久就会被叫去参加战斗。我们必须快点教她。' WHERE entry=5325; /* Text0_0: Darianna shows promise, but she is so full of energy that it is hard for her to stay still and listen. With her strength and agility, I fear it won\'t be long before she is called to fight. We must teach her quickly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你来这儿是为了得到进一步的训练，那你是高估我的能力了。跟泰龙尼斯谈谈;他应该能帮助你。' WHERE entry=5326; /* Text0_0: If you are here for further training, you have overestimated my abilities. Have a word with Telonis over there; he can help you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你得及时准备好接受我的教学，$N。到那时，找达丽亚娜谈谈，他会帮助你训练的。' WHERE entry=5328; /* Text0_0: In time you will be ready for what I have to teach, $N. Until then, please ask Darianna over there to help you with your training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们可以从死去的动物身上获得原料。别无视它们的牺牲，$N。带着尊敬来处理这些皮革。' WHERE entry=5329; /* Text0_0: Many animals lost their lives so that we could gain these materials. Do not take their sacrifice lightly, $N. Handle the leather with the respect it deserves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要做的事情很多!自从我的兄弟不小心蒸发了诺姆瑞根所有的衣料和皮革之后，事情便多起来了。我只能保持暂时通风!啊，$N，那些日子...' WHERE entry=5330; /* Text0_0: Lots to do! Haven\'t been this busy since my cousin accidentally vaporized all the cloth and leather in Gnomeregan. My, it was drafty for a while! Ah, $N, those were the days.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不，恐怕我不能帮你。你的技能远胜於我!如果你想学习更多的知识，跟达纳苏斯工匠区的夜精灵泰龙尼斯谈谈。他拥有令人惊异的技能!' WHERE entry=5331; /* Text0_0: Nope, can\'t help you, I\'m afraid. Your skills have mine beat! If you want to learn more, talk to the night elf Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s amazing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，我声明!他是个新学生!只要你再多掌握一点技能，我会很乐意将我所知道的一切都教给你的。去跟格雷塔谈谈，好吗?她会教你如何速成技能的。' WHERE entry=5333; /* Text0_0: Well, I declare! It\'s a new student! I\'ll gladly teach you everything I know once you have a little more skill. Go talk to Gretta Finespindle over there, would you? She\'ll have you up to speed in no time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技术在进步,很快你就会拥有一家你自己的皮革商店。我很高兴能帮你，$N。我的速度就只能这麽快了，你知道吗?有那麽多工作要做!' WHERE entry=5334; /* Text0_0: Your skills are coming along nicely. Soon you\'ll be running a leather shop of your own. I\'ll be glad for the help, $N. My hands are only so fast, you know? There\'s so much work to do! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些栖息在这片荒地上的科多兽的兽皮最为坚韧。' WHERE entry=5335; /* Text0_0: The strongest hides come from those kodo that have laid themselves to rest in this wasteland. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能再教你啦:你所掌握的技能已经超过我了。去雷霆崖中央平原西北部的商店找牛头人犹纳吧。她会为你提供更多训练的。' WHERE entry=5336; /* Text0_0: I cannot aid you with further lessons: your skills have surpassed mine. Go and see the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She offers more advanced training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不会给一个学徒训练。去贫瘠之地的哀嚎洞穴找牛头人瓦多尔吧，他会帮助你的。' WHERE entry=5338; /* Text0_0: I do not offer apprentice training. Look for the tauren Waldor in the Wailing Caverns, here in the Barrens. He can assist you with whatever you need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来这里是为了进一步的训练?抖去你身上的尘土吧，让我们马上开始工作。' WHERE entry=5339; /* Text0_0: Have you come for further training? Shake the dust of the road from your garments, then, and let us get to work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的斧头经历过多场战事，我喜欢将它带在身边。敌人曾数次入侵我们的首都，但是别怕:我们总能击退他们。' WHERE entry=5340; /* Text0_0: My axe has seen many battles, and I like to keep it handy. Enemy forces have fought their way into our capital several times now, but have no fear: we have always driven them back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能为你提供更多的训练啦:你的制革技能已经超过我啦。你应该去那儿找犹纳谈谈。如果需要的话我会为你担保的。' WHERE entry=5341; /* Text0_0: I cannot help you with further training: your skill at working with leather rivals my own. You should speak with Una, over there. I will vouch for your skill if need be. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技艺不足以学会我所教授的。去找那边的玛克谈谈。他可以帮你直到你准备好学习更高级的课程。' WHERE entry=5343; /* Text0_0: Your skills are insufficient to learn what I teach. Try talking to Mak over there instead. He can help you out until you\'re ready for more advanced lessons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我目前对你的进步感到很满意。很显然大地之母已经赋予你的双手以灵感了。' WHERE entry=5344; /* Text0_0: I am pleased with your progress so far. Surely the Earth Mother has inspired your hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，我们在这片大陆上只有一处立足之地，但是人类是永远不可能打败我们的。他们很快就会受到报复。我们会割下他们说谎的舌头，惩戒他们的背叛行为。' WHERE entry=5345; /* Text0_0: We have only a small foothold on this continent for now, but the humans can\'t fight us off forever. Then they\'ll pay for enslaving us. We\'ll cut their lying tongues out for their treachery. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是我能的话，我会教你的，但我力所不及。去跟雷霆崖中央高地西北部的商店找牛头人犹纳谈谈。她拥有真正的才能。' WHERE entry=5346; /* Text0_0: I\'d train you if I could, but you\'re too much for me. Tell you what: go talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s got some real talent. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='经过我的训练,你有更多的胆识,现在你去找在奥格瑞玛的兽人卡马吧,他更加适合你现在的情况.' WHERE entry=5348; /* Text0_0: You\'ve got more guts than brains, coming to me without the proper training. Go talk to somebody closer to your skill level, like the orc Kamari, who lives in the Drag of Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我忙吗?这话什麽意思?你觉得我只是成天站在这儿玩弄手指吗?如果你想买些什麽的话，跟罕杜尔谈谈。' WHERE entry=5350; /* Text0_0: Am I busy? What\'s that supposed to mean? Do you think I just stand here all day, twiddling my thumbs? If you\'re here to buy something, talk to Handor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在我这里学不到新的东西了;你知道的已经很多了。如果你想得到更多培训的话，去找雷霆崖中央高原西北方商店里的牛头人尤纳谈谈。替我向她致意，怎麽样?' WHERE entry=5351; /* Text0_0: You won\'t learn anything new from me; you know too much already. If you want more training, talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Send her my regards, eh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在学习好基础知识之前不能学我的技艺。如果你对训练感兴趣的话就去找卡玛瑞谈谈。' WHERE entry=5353; /* Text0_0: You can\'t study my techniques until you\'ve learned the basics. Speak with Kamari if you are interested in training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥格瑞玛地形迂回曲折，能有效地阻止入侵者。你能想像这些矮小的地精在多麽短的时间内就迷失方向吗?哈哈!如果够幸运的话，我会追踪到他们，将他们变成我的宠物。' WHERE entry=5354; /* Text0_0: The twists and turns of Orgrimmar are designed to thwart invaders. Can you imagine how quickly one of those puny gnomes would get lost in here? Ha! If it was lucky, I\'d track it down and keep it as a pet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我生前是一名图书管理员，与战争和灾难无缘。我从未想过要变成现在这样。另一方面，现在我能主宰自己，我是不会不战而降的。' WHERE entry=5355; /* Text0_0: Before my death, I was a librarian; I had nothing to do with wars and plagues. I never asked to become this. On the other hand, now that my mind is my own again, I\'m not about to surrender without a fight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的能力已经超过我了。走吧。嗯，去雷霆崖中央高地西北部的商店找牛头人犹纳。她拥有强大的力量。' WHERE entry=5356; /* Text0_0: I\'m pleased to say that your talents have outpaced my own. Go away now. Err, try the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s very skilled, I assure you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没时间教你这些初学者了,去找那边的丹格斯吧,他是个不错的老师' WHERE entry=5358; /* Text0_0: If I taught novices, there\'d be a lot more students visiting me, and things would get noisy. Go talk to Dan Golthas over there. He\'s a little intense, but he means well, and he\'s a decent teacher. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='起先，我在魔法区开设商店，但是那儿太嘈杂啦。尽管我进行了重新部署，除了有些学生坚持要向我求学之外，环境还是得到了相当的改善。' WHERE entry=5359; /* Text0_0: I first set up shop in the Magic Quarter, but it was pretty noisy there. This is a definite improvement, barring a few persistent students who still track me down, despite the fact that I\'ve relocated. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='月神已经赐予夜精灵很多礼物。作为回报，我们有职责保卫这些森林免受部落带来的恶魔的污染。',Text0_1_loc4='月神已经赐予夜精灵很多礼物。作为回报，我们有职责保卫这些森林免受部落带来的恶魔的污染。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5360; /* Text0_0: Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it. */ /* Text0_1: Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='继续培训你已经超越我的能力了。与达纳苏斯工匠区的泰龙尼斯谈谈。他总是很愿意帮助有才能的学生。',Text0_1_loc4='继续培训你已经超越我的能力了。与达纳苏斯工匠区的泰龙尼斯谈谈。他总是很愿意帮助有才能的学生。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5361; /* Text0_0: Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students. */ /* Text0_1: Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我只教那些掌握基本指示的学生。你必须在达纳苏斯工匠区找到夜精灵达丽亚娜。她的技能与你的是完美的互补。',Text0_1_loc4='我只教那些掌握基本指示的学生。你必须在达纳苏斯工匠区找到夜精灵达丽亚娜。她的技能与你的是完美的互补。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5363; /* Text0_0: I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours. */ /* Text0_1: I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在你开始切割皮革之前一定要仔细检查尺寸。我们可不能浪费材料。',Text0_1_loc4='在你开始切割皮革之前一定要仔细检查尺寸。我们可不能浪费材料。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5364; /* Text0_0: Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials. */ /* Text0_1: Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须去西部荒野的海洋搜寻，朝正西方西─金海岸矿坑与海岸交接处往西北方向。海岸边有一只锚，看来附近一定有艘沉船。水下的压力很大;如果游得太远的话，即使是最优秀的潜水者也可能死於疲劳。$B$B去找一处适宜的自然环境吧，$N─这附近有起泡的海底裂缝，能在深海潜水时提供氧气。' WHERE entry=5373; /* Text0_0: The waters of Westfall is where you must search, due west-northwest of where the Gold Coast Quarry meets with the shore.  An anchor shows where a boat has sunk beyond it, deep within the water.  The underwater pressure is fierce here; swimming too far will crush even the mightiest swimmer from fatigue.  $B$BLook for a natural formation to aid you, $N - a bubbly fissure is near here, offering deep-water swimmers a chance for renewed breath.$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在银松森林北流海岸边缘，海滩上搁着一艘废弃的船。船只以西有你要找的东西;游得太远的话，你会因疲劳无法游回海岸的。海床上有一只上了锁的带锁箱，等着你去取呢。$B$B要是没有人帮忙的话，潜到这样的深度会承受极大的水压，要小心;海床上有一道裂缝，能释放出气泡，有助於你寻找那半块坠饰。好好利用吧。' WHERE entry=5374; /* Text0_0: In the Silverpine Forest along the edges of the North Tide\'s Run, a derelict boat rests on the shore.  Out to the west of this lies what you seek; swim too far and the ocean will crush you from fatigue.  It resides on the ocean floor in a lockbox, waiting for you to claim it.$B$BYou\'ll be hard pressed to survive a dive to such depths without aid, so take heart; a bubbly fissure offers renewed breath to divers seeking this half of the pendant.  Use it wisely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在黑海岸的北面流淌着壁泉河，发源於现今的费伍德森林。随着河流流出并汇入薄雾海，一直蜿蜒到海洋北部最深处。一处被人们称为石爪的地方有你要找的东西。$B$B要当心─蛇颈龙聚集在石爪那里，会攻击侵入他们领地的人。',Text0_1_loc4='在黑海岸的北面流淌着壁泉河，发源於现今的费伍德森林。随着河流流出并汇入薄雾海，一直蜿蜒到海洋北部最深处。一处被人们称为石爪的地方有你要找的东西。$B$B要当心─蛇颈龙聚集在石爪那里，会攻击侵入他们领地的人。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5375; /* Text0_0: In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory. */ /* Text0_1: In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在贫瘠之地的东北部，有一处受到严重污染的水池。当地人称它为淤泥沼泽;风险投资公司将水晶般幽蓝的水域变成工业副产品和废弃品的泥潭。在沼泽的中心有你要找的东西，$N。$B$B要小心，风险投资公司绝不容许有人入侵，他们将不为其工作的人都当作入侵者。你作为自然的保卫者，更是他们极力对抗的目标。',Text0_1_loc4='在贫瘠之地的东北部，有一处受到严重污染的水池。当地人称它为淤泥沼泽;风险投资公司将水晶般幽蓝的水域变成工业副产品和废弃品的泥潭。在沼泽的中心有你要找的东西，$N。$B$B要小心，风险投资公司绝不容许有人入侵，他们将不为其工作的人都当作入侵者。你作为自然的保卫者，更是他们极力对抗的目标。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5376; /* Text0_0: In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose. */ /* Text0_1: In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='草地柔软青葱。空气清新，阳光明媚，歌声飘飘。泰达希尔的梦想终成现实。但是为什麽我感到有种不详的预兆?' WHERE entry=5393; /* Text0_0: The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I\'ve seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的进步已经超越了我能教授的技艺了。现在到辛特兰的鹰巢山去找矮人德拉克·石拳谈话。他的作品太棒了，比我的好多了。' WHERE entry=5394; /* Text0_0: You have advanced beyond my skill to teach you. Journey now to Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands and speak with the dwarf Drakk Stonehand. His work is magnificent, far better than my own. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$g尊敬的先生:女士;，在你掌握制皮的更多知识之前，我还不能帮助你，对此我感到很遗憾。跟法多恩或达丽亚娜谈谈。他们能教你所需的技能。' WHERE entry=5396; /* Text0_0: I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别试图将你的意愿强加到皮革上。而是让其天然的特性显示出自身的形状和功能。这不是一场战役。与皮革协同工作，而不是与其作对。' WHERE entry=5397; /* Text0_0: Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='针太细，线太粗，针脚倒还不错。我们与萨尔和其他人的合约将继续有效。部落不会被驱逐出这片土地的。',Text0_1_loc4='针太细，线太粗，针脚倒还不错。我们与萨尔和其他人的合约将继续有效。部落不会被驱逐出这片土地的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5398; /* Text0_0: The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands. */ /* Text0_1: The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的才能有限，你也已经达到了。恭喜你，$N。你的下一站应该是菲拉斯的莫沙彻营地。牛头人哈拉纳·铁皮住在那里;她的技术很有声望。',Text0_1_loc4='我的才能有限，你也已经达到了。恭喜你，$N。你的下一站应该是菲拉斯的莫沙彻营地。牛头人哈拉纳·铁皮住在那里;她的技术很有声望。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5399; /* Text0_0: Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill. */ /* Text0_1: Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我自己不久前也是一个新手，所以我觉得我不太适合教你。试着跟那边的塔恩或是玛克谈谈。他们之中应该有人能回答你的问题。',Text0_1_loc4='我自己不久前也是一个新手，所以我觉得我不太适合教你。试着跟那边的塔恩或是玛克谈谈。他们之中应该有人能回答你的问题。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5401; /* Text0_0: It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='凯恩把我们带到了一片充满希望的大地。我们很幸运，因此我们再把好运带给别人。这就是我为什麽开始教学的原因，$N。',Text0_1_loc4='凯恩把我们带到了一片充满希望的大地。我们很幸运，因此我们再把好运带给别人。这就是我为什麽开始教学的原因，$N。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5402; /* Text0_0: Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N. */ /* Text0_1: Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以利用在这儿找到的材料制作有趣的东西。这些山林中有许多奇怪的生物!去杀死它们，$N。' WHERE entry=5403; /* Text0_0: I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin\'s beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $N, and bring me back some tall tales. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我喜欢机会;你不喜欢吗?啊，当然你也喜欢。这就是你要按我说的去做的原因。' WHERE entry=5405; /* Text0_0: I love a good challenge; don\'t you? Aye, of course ye do. An\' that\'s why you\'re about to do exactly what I say. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不是来教那些刚离开摇篮的宝宝的。你离我对学生的要求还差远了。你不过是个年幼的$g小夥子:姑娘;，你最好别在这儿烦我了。' WHERE entry=5406; /* Text0_0: I\'m not here to teach babes fresh out of the cradle. Ye\'ve nowhere near the amount of skill I require in my students. In fact, ye\'re a sad figure of a $glad:lass;, an\' I\'ll thank ye not to stand there jibber-jabberin\' at me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我所有的作品都必须由买主亲自来订购。奥尔文常常要我改变这个习惯，但是我就是不改。看看你周围吧，无数战士还指望我给他们打造装甲呢。',Text0_1_loc4='我所有的作品都必须由买主亲自来订购。奥尔文常常要我改变这个习惯，但是我就是不改。看看你周围吧，无数战士还指望我给他们打造装甲呢。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5407; /* Text0_0: All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor. */ /* Text0_1: All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我真希望有更多像你一样的学生。很少有人会冒险深入敌境。我佩服你的勇气。',Text0_1_loc4='我真希望有更多像你一样的学生。很少有人会冒险深入敌境。我佩服你的勇气。' WHERE entry=5408; /* Text0_0: I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage. */ /* Text0_1: I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不会在这场战争中让步。我不分昼夜的制造新装甲，还把旧的装甲修补好。我没时间做其他任务。你愿帮我分担一些吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我不会在这场战争中让步。我不分昼夜的制造新装甲，还把旧的装甲修补好。我没时间做其他任务。你愿帮我分担一些吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5409; /* Text0_0: We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me? */ /* Text0_1: We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来找我求学是浪费了你我的时间，$N。我没时间教授基础技能。我们在这里战斗，而这里是一处前线。在你准备充分之前不要再来找我。',Text0_1_loc4='你来找我求学是浪费了你我的时间，$N。我没时间教授基础技能。我们在这里战斗，而这里是一处前线。在你准备充分之前不要再来找我。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5410; /* Text0_0: You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared. */ /* Text0_1: You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我觉得你的服饰急需维修。' WHERE entry=5413; /* Text0_0: I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我对裁缝业知之甚少，但你需要更多的帮助。我听说有个夜精灵精通裁缝技术。他居住在暴风城的魔法区。' WHERE entry=5414; /* Text0_0: I\'m a simple man who knows a few things about tailoring, but you need more assistance than I can provide. I have heard of a Night Elf who is quite an accomplished tailor. He resides in Stormwind, in the Magic District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想学点东西吗?我会很乐意教你的!' WHERE entry=5415; /* Text0_0: So you would like to learn a few things? I would be happy to get you started! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='生活就像一幅小心编织的锦缎。' WHERE entry=5416; /* Text0_0: Life is like a carefully woven tapestry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯……你需要学的东西有点超出我的能耐了。去找那边的塞拉多斯谈谈。我会的东西全是他教的!' WHERE entry=5417; /* Text0_0: Hmm... the things you need to learn are a little above my head. Have a talk with Sellandus over at Larson\'s Clothiers just up the path to the right. He taught me everything I know! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好，开始学习裁缝吧。' WHERE entry=5418; /* Text0_0: Very well, let your journey of tailoring begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='缝纫需要嫺熟的手法，以及……也是最重要的，耐性。' WHERE entry=5419; /* Text0_0: Needlework requires a steady hand. And patience... above all, patience. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在是你去达纳苏斯跟玫琳恩谈谈的时候了。她将对你进行指导。' WHERE entry=5420; /* Text0_0: It is time for you to journey to Darnassus and speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴能将你收入麾下。让我们开始吧。' WHERE entry=5421; /* Text0_0: I would be happy to take you under my wing. Let us begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到我的商店。我能为你做什麽?' WHERE entry=5422; /* Text0_0: Welcome to me shop. What can I do for ye\'? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等一下，我只是一个助手。如果你想学那些花哨的东西，找那边的老约莫德·石眉谈谈。' WHERE entry=5423; /* Text0_0: Hold on there, I\'m just an assistant. If ye want to start learnin\' the fancy stuff, talk to old Stonebrew over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好!我一直希望收个新学生。那麽就让我们立刻开始吧!' WHERE entry=5424; /* Text0_0: Excellent! I\'ve been hopin\' for a new student. Well, let\'s get started right away then! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们使用动物皮毛制作物品。' WHERE entry=5425; /* Text0_0: We use many animal pelts and skins in our creations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我知道一些，但我不是专家。祝你好远，玛加尔也是。他就站在商店后面。看看他是否能帮助你，但是小心别惹恼他。他脾气有些暴躁。' WHERE entry=5426; /* Text0_0: I know a few things, but I\'m no expert. Lucky for you, Magar is. He\'s standing near the back of the shop. See if he can help you, but be careful not to rile him. He can be irritable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会将我所知道的传授给你的。' WHERE entry=5427; /* Text0_0: I will teach you what I can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们没有浪费狩猎而得的动物的任何一部分。' WHERE entry=5428; /* Text0_0: No part of the animals we hunt is wasted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你寻求更高级的知识。坦帕拥有这种知识。她应该就站在附近……' WHERE entry=5429; /* Text0_0: You seek a higher knowledge. Tepa is blessed with such knowledge. She should be standing somewhere nearby... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='带着大地之母的祝福，我们要开始了。' WHERE entry=5430; /* Text0_0: With the Earth Mother\'s blessing, we shall begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去结交朋友吧。我能帮你吗?' WHERE entry=5431; /* Text0_0: Pleased to make you acquaintance. May I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我知识渊博，但我还不是专家。你知道你该去找谁谈话吗?雷安诺!她就在不远的地方。到幽暗城打听她的下落。' WHERE entry=5432; /* Text0_0: I am knowledgable, but I am not an expert. You know who you should talk to? Rhiannon! She\'s not far. Ask around for her in Undercity */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这麽说...你想当一名裁缝?很好，让我们看看你是否具有这样的潜质。' WHERE entry=5433; /* Text0_0: So... you want to be a tailor? Very well, we\'ll see if you have what it takes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到我们这儿来的客人可不多。你对我感兴趣?' WHERE entry=5434; /* Text0_0: We don\'t get many visitors out here. May I interest you in something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我只是个学生。雷安诺才是专家。她站在那边的木箱旁。你可以从她那儿学到很多东西。' WHERE entry=5435; /* Text0_0: I\'m just a student myself, really. Rhiannon\'s the expert. She\'s standing by the crates over there. You can learn a lot from her. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我认为你有潜力。或许我可以给你看看一两样东西?' WHERE entry=5436; /* Text0_0: Yes, I think you have potential. Maybe I can show you a thing or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有比编织更好的宁神方法了。',Text0_1_loc4='没有比编织更好的宁神方法了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5437; /* Text0_0: There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave. */ /* Text0_1: There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的教育正在继续，而你的知识已超越了我。如果你还想继续学习你就必须找玫琳恩谈谈。她会指引你的。',Text0_1_loc4='你的教育正在继续，而你的知识已超越了我。如果你还想继续学习你就必须找玫琳恩谈谈。她会指引你的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5438; /* Text0_0: My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you. */ /* Text0_1: My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不会失望的，旅行者。裁缝是一种充满乐趣的工作。',Text0_1_loc4='你不会失望的，旅行者。裁缝是一种充满乐趣的工作。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5439; /* Text0_0: You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor. */ /* Text0_1: You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，我能为你做什麽呢?' WHERE entry=5440; /* Text0_0: Hey mon, what can I be doin\' for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你所掌握的知识已经跟我差不多啦。或许你可以去奥格玛找玛加尔。他虽然不是最好的裁缝，但是他一定可以帮助你。' WHERE entry=5441; /* Text0_0: At dis point you know as much as I do, mon. Maybe you go see Magar in Orgrimmar. He not be da happiest tailor around, but he help you anyway. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就对了!拿起针线让我们开始吧!' WHERE entry=5442; /* Text0_0: Dat\'s da attitude! Grab a needle and thread and let\'s get jammin\'! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怕我已不再是个文雅谦逊的人了。年龄和无数战争让我的皮肤和灵魂变得坚硬无比。或许这就是凯恩派我来烈日石居的原因……和煦的暖风和温暖的阳光无法减轻我的痛苦。' WHERE entry=5443; /* Text0_0: I am afraid that I am no longer gentle or humble. Age and countless battles have hardened my skin and soul. Perhaps that is why Cairne assigned me to Sun Rock Retreat... the gentle winds and warm sun does ease the pain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。我们的蝙蝠训练很严而且吃得不错。你不会找到比他们还快的了。' WHERE entry=5453; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  Our bats are well trained and fed.  You\'ll not find faster. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我要如何效劳?' WHERE entry=5454; /* Text0_0: How may I be of service? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，欢迎。我不太擅长微笑，但是相信我;我很高兴能为您服务。' WHERE entry=5455; /* Text0_0: Greetings, and welcome.  I am not very good at smiling, but trust me; I am happy to serve you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='角鹰兽是一种高贵而迅捷的动物。这些训练有素的飞兽可以让它们的骑手以很快的速度旅行。',Text0_1_loc4='角鹰兽是一种高贵而迅捷的动物。这些训练有素的飞兽可以让它们的骑手以很快的速度旅行。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5473; /* Text0_0: The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance. */ /* Text0_1: The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为了与大陆保持联系，我们会定期派出角鹰兽在鲁瑟兰村和黑海岸之间传递资讯的。' WHERE entry=5474; /* Text0_0: To maintain our link to the mainland, we have hippogryphs constantly flying between Rut\'theran Village and Darkshore. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='泰达希尔海岸边的鱼儿又大又精神。有传言说那是因为我们新的世界之树的快速增长而引起的。',Text0_1_loc4='泰达希尔海岸边的鱼儿又大又精神。有传言说那是因为我们新的世界之树的快速增长而引起的。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5475; /* Text0_0: The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause. */ /* Text0_1: The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尽管黑海岸比泰达希尔更危险，但是很多渔夫都在此谋生。' WHERE entry=5476; /* Text0_0: Although the coast of Darkshore is more dangerous than that of Teldrassil, many fishers find profit here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为冒险家服务是我的荣幸，因为他们即将成为英雄。' WHERE entry=5477; /* Text0_0: It is my honor to provide for adventurers, for they are heroes in the making. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鹰巢山这边最快的狮鹫兽了。想乘坐吗?' WHERE entry=5479; /* Text0_0: Fastest gryphons this side of Aerie Peak. Want to take a ride? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以在北部码头搭船前往鲁瑟兰村和达纳苏斯。你可以在南部码头发现穿越无尽之海通往暴风港。西边的码头，直走到底，则航向蓝谜岛，艾克索达的附近。祝你一路平安!' WHERE entry=5480; /* Text0_0: On the northern dock, you can board a ship that will carry you to Rut\'theran Village and Darnassus.  From the southern dock, you can find passage across the Great Sea to Menethil Harbor on Khaz Modan.  Safe journeys to you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个码头?你可以乘船前往夜精灵的领地。地名?嗯，我想是奥伯丁。我不太确定，我只是一名搬运工。' WHERE entry=5481; /* Text0_0: This dock here?  Well you can catch the ship that goes to that Night Elf place.  What\'s it\'s name?  Uhh Auberdine I think.  I don\'t really know for sure, I just load and unload stuff. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要将这些桶运送到挖掘点非常困难，但是要获得火药，还得靠我们自己。$B$B我们必须竭尽所能地对抗黑铁!' WHERE entry=5494; /* Text0_0: Delivering these barrels to the excavation site is hard work, but there are so many depending on us to get the blast powder there.$B$BWe must do what we can against the Dark Irons! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的双足飞龙可以在贫瘠之地高速飞翔。' WHERE entry=5495; /* Text0_0: My wind riders are trained to fly quickly through the hot Barrens air. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='贫瘠之地阳光灼热，那儿的居住者充满敌意，是考验你的力量和决心的最佳地点。' WHERE entry=5496; /* Text0_0: The Barrens, with its hot sun and hostile denizens, is the perfect place to test your strength and fortitude. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。如果你是来找皮件的，那麽你会看到我的货品做工精细。' WHERE entry=5497; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  If you are here for leather goods, then you will find my wares well crafted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来帮助投递物品的吗?米兰就快准备好了。' WHERE entry=5498; /* Text0_0: Are you here to help with the delivery? Miran\'s just about ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当坐在一头双足飞龙背上时，你就会发现它的力量和速度的确不是徒有虚名。' WHERE entry=5500; /* Text0_0: When mounted on the back of a wind rider, one sees that its reputation for strength and speed is well earned. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这真是条危险的路!$B$B米兰刚刚去送东西了，他应该会马上回来。' WHERE entry=5501; /* Text0_0: This is a dangerous line of business!$B$BMiran just left with a delivery. He should be back in a few minutes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你操纵得比我要好!你需要一个经验比我还要多的人。那就是赫伯特·哈尔希医生，一个在幽暗城链金房工作的亡灵。' WHERE entry=5513; /* Text0_0: You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead who works in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看我的肉，朋友。你不会想双手空空就进入贫瘠之地吧。' WHERE entry=5515; /* Text0_0: Have a look at my meats, friend.  You won\'t want to go out into the Barrens without a good stock of provisions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在你从双足飞龙背上往下俯瞰这个世界之前，不能说你真正活过。' WHERE entry=5516; /* Text0_0: You haven\'t lived until you\'ve looked down on the world from the back of a wind rider. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以从这个码头找到去塞拉摩的路。记住我的话，那些地方对从联盟去的人们是非常不安全的。一定要小心谨慎。' WHERE entry=5517; /* Text0_0: You can find passage to Theramore from this dock.  Heed my words, those lands are rarely safe to travel for people of the Alliance.  Watch your step and your back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。' WHERE entry=5519; /* Text0_0: Good day to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的技艺在我的技术水准之上了。乔吉奥·波利罗，转角邓肯布料店老板可能精进你的技能。' WHERE entry=5520; /* Text0_0: You are beyond my level of expertise. Georgio Bolero, the master of Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner could help you advance your skills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去和纺织区左上角的邓肯谈谈吧,他更善于教你这样的初学者.' WHERE entry=5522; /* Text0_0: Speak with Lawrence Shneider at Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner to the left. He is adept at dealing with beginners. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='都是些有用的东西。你的教导可以继续进行了。' WHERE entry=5523; /* Text0_0: A fine display of worthiness. Your instruction may now continue. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，这件达纳苏斯织品品质最好!' WHERE entry=5524; /* Text0_0: Ah, this Darnassian fabric is the finest! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，你这个聪明的家伙!我可以明确地告诉你，你知道的比我多!你可别为此自负，如果你想继续学习的话，就去暴风城找乔吉奥·波利罗谈谈吧。听说他是个很好的裁缝!' WHERE entry=5525; /* Text0_0: Well, aren\'t you the smarty-pants? Ye know more than I do, I can tell ye that! Don\'t go getting\' a big head, but if ye want to keep learnin\', have a chat with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. They say he knows his tailorin\'! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可没时间跟小孩子耗!去跟我的助手阿斯拉谈谈!' WHERE entry=5527; /* Text0_0: I don\'t have time to babysit! Go talk to me assistant, Uthrar! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯……看来还有点希望，我会把那个给你的。那好吧，我们在哪里?' WHERE entry=5528; /* Text0_0: Hmm... you show a little promise, I\'ll give you that. Okay then, where were we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看你的周围，$r。对你今天所看到的抱持感激之心。$B$B与我刚踏入这个森林相比，现在它改变了很多。美好和令人意外的改变....',Text0_1_loc4='看看你的周围，$r。对你今天所看到的抱持感激之心。$B$B与我刚踏入这个森林相比，现在它改变了很多。美好和令人意外的改变....',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5529; /* Text0_0: Do you hear the call of the hunt, $c?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us. */ /* Text0_1: Do you hear the call of the hunt, $c?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能制造你在商店里看见的若干东西。你认为如何?小心回答，这也许能决定你的命运。' WHERE entry=5530; /* Text0_0: I made a lot of the things you see in the store. What do you think? Answer carefully, your life may depend on it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要找一个比我懂得多的人。去找幽暗城的乔瑟夫·格里高利谈谈。那麽，你还在这里干吗?' WHERE entry=5531; /* Text0_0: You need to learn from someone who knows more than I do. Go talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. Well, what are you still doing here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什麽?你为什麽在烦我?哎呀，我打赌你甚至不能制造一件高品质的长袍!去找斯诺恩谈谈，等你水准提高以后再来找我!' WHERE entry=5533; /* Text0_0: What? Why are you bothering me? Why, I bet you can\'t even create a high quality robe! Go talk to Snang and come back when you\'re worthy of my talents! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你那时给我看了某些结果!现在该我给你看看结果了!' WHERE entry=5534; /* Text0_0: About time you showed me some results! Now I\'ll show you results! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们说小洞不补大洞……什麽来着?啊，我记不得了。反正是愚蠢的说法。' WHERE entry=5535; /* Text0_0: They say a stitch in time saves... what, eleven? Ah, I can\'t remember. Stupid saying anyway. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对一个业余者来说……这还行!你的知识量已经跟我持平了。要是你想学习更多知识，就去幽暗城找乔瑟夫·格里高利谈谈。' WHERE entry=5536; /* Text0_0: Not bad... for an amateur! Still, you know about as much as I do. If you wanna\' learn more you\'re gonna\' have to talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，嗯，还不坏。或许我能让你看点什麽……' WHERE entry=5539; /* Text0_0: Well well, not too bad. Maybe I CAN show you a few things... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多好的天气!它让我有了创造新设计的灵感。',Text0_1_loc4='多好的天气!它让我有了创造新设计的灵感。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5540; /* Text0_0: What a fine day! It inspires me to create a new design. */ /* Text0_1: What a fine day! It inspires me to create a new design. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的才能出众!你真是有灵性。你要想继续追求知识的话，找暴风城的乔吉奥·波利罗谈谈。他深受众人尊敬，而且他能深化对你的指导。',Text0_1_loc4='你的才能出众!你真是有灵性。你要想继续追求知识的话，找暴风城的乔吉奥·波利罗谈谈。他深受众人尊敬，而且他能深化对你的指导。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5541; /* Text0_0: Your talents excel! You are truly inspired. To continue your pursuit of knowledge, speak with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. He is held in high regard, and will be able to further your instruction. */ /* Text0_1: Your talents excel! You are truly inspired. To continue your pursuit of knowledge, speak with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. He is held in high regard, and will be able to further your instruction. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是必须学的基础知识. 和站在我旁边的缇娜谈谈吧她可以教你,过一段时间才来找我',Text0_1_loc4='这是必须学的基础知识. 和站在我旁边的缇娜谈谈吧她可以教你,过一段时间才来找我',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5543; /* Text0_0: There are basics that must be learned. Trianna is standing nearby, speak with her and return to me later. */ /* Text0_1: There are basics that must be learned. Trianna is standing nearby, speak with her and return to me later. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你干的很好，旅人。我能收你当徒弟令感到很骄傲!',Text0_1_loc4='你干的很好，旅人。我能收你当徒弟令感到很骄傲!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5544; /* Text0_0: You have done well, traveler. I am proud to call you my student! */ /* Text0_1: You have done well, traveler. I am proud to call you my student! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到我的帐篷。我可以帮你吗?',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到我的帐篷。我可以帮你吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5545; /* Text0_0: Welcome to our tent. May I assist you? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to our tent. May I assist you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的知识很渊博，旅人。你必须向一个比我更聪明的人学习。关於乔瑟夫·格里高利的智慧的故事广为流传。你可以在幽暗城找到他。',Text0_1_loc4='你的知识很渊博，旅人。你必须向一个比我更聪明的人学习。关於乔瑟夫·格里高利的智慧的故事广为流传。你可以在幽暗城找到他。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5546; /* Text0_0: Your knowledge is great, traveler. You must learn from one who is wiser than I. Many tales have been told of the wisdom of Josef Gregorian. You may find him in Undercity. */ /* Text0_1: Your knowledge is great, traveler. You must learn from one who is wiser than I. Many tales have been told of the wisdom of Josef Gregorian. You may find him in Undercity. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='完成得很熟练!现在，让我们继续你的教育……',Text0_1_loc4='完成得很熟练!现在，让我们继续你的教育……',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5549; /* Text0_0: Expertly accomplished! Now, let us continue your education... */ /* Text0_1: Expertly accomplished! Now, let us continue your education... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些图案难道不漂亮吗?每一个都有自己的风格。',Text0_1_loc4='这些图案难道不漂亮吗?每一个都有自己的风格。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5551; /* Text0_0: Aren\'t the patterns beautiful? Each one speaks with its own voice. */ /* Text0_1: Aren\'t the patterns beautiful? Each one speaks with its own voice. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
