UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我给国王提供过装备。如果有正确的训练，你也可以。' WHERE entry=5571; /* Text0_0: I have outfitted kings. With the proper training, you can too. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你走了好远的路了，旅人。还有一项工作要你完成……' WHERE entry=5573; /* Text0_0: You have come a long way, traveler. There is one more task for you to perform... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要学习更多的基本技能，我才能帮助你。当你准备好了再来找我。' WHERE entry=5574; /* Text0_0: I cannot help you until you have learned more of the essentials. Come back to me when you are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方通风良好……但是我还在乎什麽?我已经死了。' WHERE entry=5575; /* Text0_0: The place is a bit drafty... but what do I care? I\'m dead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在缝纫艺术方面做得很好，我必须承认。现在，让我们看看你到底有多棒……' WHERE entry=5577; /* Text0_0: You\'re doing very well in the art of tailoring, I must admit. Now, let\'s see how good you REALLY are... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谁派你来的?你还没有准备好接受我的指令!当你们准备好以后会得到通知的。' WHERE entry=5578; /* Text0_0: Who sent you here? You\'re not ready for my instruction yet! You\'ll be told when you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我确实很喜欢坐在这里，听着大海的声音。哦，什麽?是的，有一艘船会把你带到米奈希尔港。它有时会停在这里。',Text0_1_loc4='我确实很喜欢坐在这里，听着大海的声音。哦，什麽?是的，有一艘船会把你带到米奈希尔港。它有时会停在这里。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5579; /* Text0_0: I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time. */ /* Text0_1: I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='记得我的话!你在东部王国是找不到比塞尔萨玛狮鹫兽更快的狮鹫兽的!' WHERE entry=5580; /* Text0_0: Mark my words!  You won\'t find faster gryphons anywhere in the Eastern Kingdoms than the ones right here in Thelsamar! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你问我的话，没有比矿工更好的职业了，也没有比矮人更好的矿工了!' WHERE entry=5581; /* Text0_0: If you ask me, there\'s no greater profession than a miner.  And if you ask me, there\'s no greater miner than a dwarf! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='蛮锤城堡的矮人也许有奔跑迅速的战马，但是这些鹰巢山的狮鹫兽能承受大锻炉的热量吗?我觉得不能!' WHERE entry=5582; /* Text0_0: The Wildhammer dwarves might have fast steeds, but can those Aerie Peak gryphons stand the heat of The Great Forge?  I think not! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='最好的矿工紧握$g他:她;的铁锄，拥有一颗坚定的心，头发上还散落着一层厚厚的黑灰。' WHERE entry=5583; /* Text0_0: The best miner has a firm grip on $ghis:her; pick, a stout heart in $ghis:her; chest, and thick, black dust in $ghis:her; hair. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那个坚固的木箱在木材厂中间，周围推满了残骸和血色十字军的狂热信徒。' WHERE entry=5584; /* Text0_0: The sturdy crate sits in the middle of the lumber mill surrounded by debris and very zealous followers of the Scarlet Crusade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这只熊漫步在一条靠近深爪小径的路上，在密斯特拉湖和联盟的银风避难所正西方。虽然他是你在梣谷遇到的三个动物之中最好对付的一个，对他也不能掉以轻心。他的出现对於逗留在梣谷和石爪山脉之间的旅客来说是一个巨大的威胁。',Text0_1_loc4='这只熊漫步在一条靠近深爪小径的路上，在密斯特拉湖和联盟的银风避难所正西方。虽然他是你在梣谷遇到的三个动物之中最好对付的一个，对他也不能掉以轻心。他的出现对於逗留在梣谷和石爪山脉之间的旅客来说是一个巨大的威胁。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5593; /* Text0_0: This bear wanders a path close to where the Talondeep Path lies, due west of Mystral Lake and the Alliance outpost of Silverwind Refuge.  While he is the easiest of the three creatures you will face on the Ashenvale Hunt, he should not be trifled with.  His presence is a constant threat to travelers who sojourn between Ashenvale and the Stonetalon Mountains. */ /* Text0_1: This bear wanders a path close to where the Talondeep Path lies, due west of Mystral Lake and the Alliance outpost of Silverwind Refuge.  While he is the easiest of the three creatures you will face on the Ashenvale Hunt, he should not be trifled with.  His presence is a constant threat to travelers who sojourn between Ashenvale and the Stonetalon Mountains. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='作为梣谷猎场最强大的野兽，沙普塔隆可以在这片大地自封的卫兵─夜精灵的陪伴下自由的漫步。沙普塔隆在这里南部寻找猎物，尽情的撕裂着毫无防备的旅客。$B$B要想杀死这样一个野兽需要极大的努力，$N。我希望你在猎杀这个野兽时运气好一点!',Text0_1_loc4='作为梣谷猎场最强大的野兽，沙普塔隆可以在这片大地自封的卫兵─夜精灵的陪伴下自由的漫步。沙普塔隆在这里南部寻找猎物，尽情的撕裂着毫无防备的旅客。$B$B要想杀死这样一个野兽需要极大的努力，$N。我希望你在猎杀这个野兽时运气好一点!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5594; /* Text0_0: The mightiest of all the beasts that make up the Ashenvale Hunt, Sharptalon is let to wander freely by the self-proclaimed guardians of this land, the night elves.  Sharptalon patrols for prey to the south of here, taking delight in rending the unsuspecting and unaware traveler limb from limb.$B$BTo bring down such a beast would be the mightiest of hauls, $N.  I wish you luck in the hunt for this creature! */ /* Text0_1: The mightiest of all the beasts that make up the Ashenvale Hunt, Sharptalon is let to wander freely by the self-proclaimed guardians of this land, the night elves.  Sharptalon patrols for prey to the south of here, taking delight in rending the unsuspecting and unaware traveler limb from limb.$B$BTo bring down such a beast would be the mightiest of hauls, $N.  I wish you luck in the hunt for this creature! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这只黑豹传言在夜精灵和他们的同盟面前很驯服，这使她成为一个更有价值的对手。萨杜布拉的猎杀路线把她从瑞恩伍德居所赶到了我们的西方，最终在那里的正西方登陆。她的皮毛是沥青一般的颜色，而她的速度也不能低估。',Text0_1_loc4='这只黑豹传言在夜精灵和他们的同盟面前很驯服，这使她成为一个更有价值的对手。萨杜布拉的猎杀路线把她从瑞恩伍德居所赶到了我们的西方，最终在那里的正西方登陆。她的皮毛是沥青一般的颜色，而她的速度也不能低估。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5595; /* Text0_0: This nightsaber is rumored to be docile in the presence of night elves and their allies, which makes her an even more worthy opponent.  Shadumbra\'s hunting path takes her from the Raynewood Retreat to our west, ultimately to lands due west of there.  Her fur is the color of pitch, and her speed is not to be underestimated. */ /* Text0_1: This nightsaber is rumored to be docile in the presence of night elves and their allies, which makes her an even more worthy opponent.  Shadumbra\'s hunting path takes her from the Raynewood Retreat to our west, ultimately to lands due west of there.  Her fur is the color of pitch, and her speed is not to be underestimated. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好$c--欢迎来到我们征服梣谷的前线!如果你在找事做的话，那麽你算来对地方了。我总是在寻找体格健壮的人来为部落带来荣誉!' WHERE entry=5613; /* Text0_0: Greetings $c - welcome to the front lines in our conquest of Ashenvale!  If you are looking for something to do, then you\'ve come to the right place.  I\'m always looking for able-bodied individuals to help bring glory to the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='龙族用高贵的外表掩饰自己。这些石板会将她的本来面目还原的……如果我所见到的都是真的，朋友，我会在这场战争中丧命。你必须完成我未完成的事业。你准备好了吗?我们将听命於你。' WHERE entry=5633; /* Text0_0: The dragon hides behind a royal facade. The tablets will reveal her for what she is... If what I have seen holds true, I will not survive this battle, friend. It is you that must finish what I have started. Are your forces ready? Are you ready? We will begin on your command. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想知道碎木岗哨的商旅来往情况，我恰好就是你要找的兽人。不幸的是，我不喜欢人群。$B$B要是你想要什麽的话，就快说。' WHERE entry=5653; /* Text0_0: If you want to know about the comings and goings of caravans and merchants here in Splintertree Post, then I am fortunately the orc you are looking for.  Unfortunately for you though, I don\'t like people.$B$BIf you want something, make it quick. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素在跟我们讲话，$c。他们分享着我们必须掌握的知识以及不能泄漏的秘密。' WHERE entry=5654; /* Text0_0: The elements speak to us, $c.  They share knowledge that we must learn, and they share secrets that must be kept. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在严格的训练中，我必须除去那些学生先前所学的所有知识，以便传授新知识。我所提供的服务越来越难以完成。为此，每次训练的费用也越来越昂贵。你愿意除去你先前学习的技能吗?',Text0_1_loc4='在严格的训练中，我必须除去那些学生先前所学的所有知识，以便传授新知识。我所提供的服务越来越难以完成。为此，每次训练的费用也越来越昂贵。你愿意除去你先前学习的技能吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5673; /* Text0_0: Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned? */ /* Text0_1: Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你愿意的话，除了训练之外，我还可以用自己的力量将天赋从你的头脑中抹去。我要警告你的是，你每经历一次这样的过程，执行这过程的难度就会增加一分，因此所需的费用也会随之上升。',Text0_1_loc4='要是你愿意的话，除了训练之外，我还可以用自己的力量将天赋从你的头脑中抹去。我要警告你的是，你每经历一次这样的过程，执行这过程的难度就会增加一分，因此所需的费用也会随之上升。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=5674; /* Text0_0: If you desire, in addition to training, I have it within my power to erase the knowledge of your talents from your mind.  Be warned that every time you undergo this procedure the more difficult it is to perform, and therefore the more expensive it becomes. */ /* Text0_1: If you desire, in addition to training, I have it within my power to erase the knowledge of your talents from your mind.  Be warned that every time you undergo this procedure the more difficult it is to perform, and therefore the more expensive it becomes. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
