UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊……这些家伙让我整天都不得安宁!你看见他们了吗?$B$B我真希望自己能藏到地下，避开他们……' WHERE entry=6741; /* Text0_0: Ugh... these pests keep me busy night and day! Haven\'t you seen them?$B$BI wish I could just jump down a pipe to get away from them... */
