UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我统治这个王国已经有一万年啦。在那时，我从那些神圣的辛德拉家族成员那儿听到很多令人着迷的故事。$B$B由於我必须待在这儿，所以我常常和访问者沟通交谈。你可以为我讲个故事吗，或许你想听听我的故事?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。' WHERE entry=6909; /* Text0_0: For 10,000 years I have ruled this kingdom. In that time, I have heard many fascinating tales from those that would walk the hallowed grounds of the House of Shen\'dralar.$B$BAs I am bound to this place, I often exchange stories with visitors. Do you have a story for me or perhaps you would like to hear a story? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text0_1_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text1_0_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text1_1_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。' WHERE entry=6911; /* Text0_0: We mustn\'t anger the Master. His is a wrath that is cruel beyond measure. */ /* Text0_1: We mustn\'t anger the Master. His is a wrath that is cruel beyond measure. */ /* Text1_0: Keep your voice down, stranger. You do not want to disrupt the Master\'s meditations. */ /* Text1_1: Keep your voice down, stranger. You do not want to disrupt the Master\'s meditations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text2_1_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text3_0_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。',Text3_1_loc4='我们可不能惹恼了他。他发起火来就没有节制啦。' WHERE entry=6911; /* Text2_0: Many have come to this sanctuary, few have left. */ /* Text2_1: Many have come to this sanctuary, few have left. */ /* Text3_0: The Lorekeeper is an ancient. He has served under our glorious Queen! */ /* Text3_1: The Lorekeeper is an ancient. He has served under our glorious Queen! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='最近书本丢失甚多。博学者和他的助手非常恼怒。他们怀疑在埃雷萨拉斯有人妄图不轨。',Text4_1_loc4='最近书本丢失甚多。博学者和他的助手非常恼怒。他们怀疑在埃雷萨拉斯有人妄图不轨。',Text5_0_loc4='王子不再讲述灰烬使者的故事了吗？在他的诸多故事中，我们最喜欢这个。他的爱好则是寻找灰烬使者的下落。当然，没人能从他口中得知那个故事。',Text5_1_loc4='王子不再讲述灰烬使者的故事了吗？在他的诸多故事中，我们最喜欢这个。他的爱好则是寻找灰烬使者的下落。当然，没人能从他口中得知那个故事。' WHERE entry=6911; /* Text4_0: Books have been disappearing as of late. The Lorekeeper and his assistants are in a frenzy. They suspect foul play within Eldre\'Thalas. */ /* Text4_1: Books have been disappearing as of late. The Lorekeeper and his assistants are in a frenzy. They suspect foul play within Eldre\'Thalas. */ /* Text5_0: Has the Prince recanted the tale of the Ashbringer? It is our most favorite of his stories. His favorite is the followup to the Ashbringer. Of course, nobody has ever been able to get that story out of him. */ /* Text5_1: Has the Prince recanted the tale of the Ashbringer? It is our most favorite of his stories. His favorite is the followup to the Ashbringer. Of course, nobody has ever been able to get that story out of him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我猜想那些小鬼在偷学知识。',Text6_1_loc4='我猜想那些小鬼在偷学知识。',Text7_0_loc4='王子对奈法利安的巢穴非常感兴趣。如果有谁能杀死巨龙及其属下，并将战斗经过告诉王子，我敢打赌王子会非常满意的。找到灰烬使者之日可待啦！',Text7_1_loc4='王子对奈法利安的巢穴非常感兴趣。如果有谁能杀死巨龙及其属下，并将战斗经过告诉王子，我敢打赌王子会非常满意的。找到灰烬使者之日可待啦！' WHERE entry=6911; /* Text6_0: I suspect that the imps are stealing knowledge. */ /* Text6_1: I suspect that the imps are stealing knowledge. */ /* Text7_0: The Master holds great interest in the lair of Nefarian. If only someone would defeat the dragon and his minions and retell the tale to the Prince. I bet that would loosen the Prince\'s lips. The Ashbringer could be found! */ /* Text7_1: The Master holds great interest in the lair of Nefarian. If only someone would defeat the dragon and his minions and retell the tale to the Prince. I bet that would loosen the Prince\'s lips. The Ashbringer could be found! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在附近闲逛什麽?为什麽不把那些小家伙锁起来?!' WHERE entry=6913; /* Text0_0: What you doin\' wanderin\' around here?  Why them small fries not in da shackles?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在你变得强大了!向戈多克的新国王致敬!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。' WHERE entry=6914; /* Text0_0: You da strong one now!  All hail to da new king of da Gordok! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为什麽他们身上还有武器?你为什麽不拿走他们的武器?!' WHERE entry=6915; /* Text0_0: Do I see them with weapons still?  Why you let them keep their weapons?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老大手下的所有下属─践踏者克雷格、三名守卫、克罗卡斯和观察者─都为新的国王献上贡品。如果你杀死了一名下属，这名下属就不能为新国王上贡啦!留下的活口越多，你得到的贡品就越多。别杀他们，你会得到很多东西的!$B$B就是这样的!' WHERE entry=6916; /* Text0_0: All henchmen of da boss - Stomper Kreeg, all three of da Guards, Captain Kromcrush, and da Observer - give tribute to da new boss.  If you kill a henchman, then that henchman can\'t give tribute!  Each one you keep alive will give you more tribute.  Keep all of them alive and you get da BIG tribute!$B$BYeah! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，真恐怖!这是个悲剧!我们就要突破啦，但也有可能遭遇全军覆灭的惨剧。',Text0_1_loc4='哦，真恐怖!这是个悲剧!我们就要突破啦，但也有可能遭遇全军覆灭的惨剧。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=6917; /* Text0_0: Oh the horror! The tragedy! We are on the verge of a breakthrough, yet all could be lost. */ /* Text0_1: Oh the horror! The tragedy! We are on the verge of a breakthrough, yet all could be lost. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呃...很抱歉我袭击了你。不要杀我，求你了!?你是国王啦，我会为你提供更多的贡品的!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。' WHERE entry=6918; /* Text0_0: Uh... I sorry I attack you boss.  You no kill me, please OK!?  You da king now, and I help make your tribute better! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='粗略地检查一下骨骸，上面的肉已经乾枯了。真是令人毛骨悚然的场景。' WHERE entry=6919; /* Text0_0: A cursory examination of the skeletal remains indicates that the flesh was seared off. Quite a grisly sight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从可怕的精灵王子那儿取回戈多克的圣物，或许你能比老头目做得更好!' WHERE entry=6920; /* Text0_0: Maybe you do better at getting back prized Gordok relic from creepy Highborne prince than da old boss did! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='向新国王致敬!',Text1_0_loc4='向新国王致敬!' WHERE entry=6922; /* Text0_0: Hail to da new king! */ /* Text1_0: When I scowled at you before you became da new king... um... I was just joking.$B$BYeah! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='向新国王致敬!',Text3_0_loc4='向新国王致敬!' WHERE entry=6922; /* Text2_0: Dem other ogres was dumb to attack you, boss!  Dat\'s why I\'m still alive - I\'m smart and stuff! */ /* Text3_0: We a lot cleaner than da ogres in Tanaris.  All over da desert as far as da eye can see - ogre poo.  Not here, no $g sir : ma\'am;! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='只要你跟我们呆在一起，你就是国王。你离开的话，会有其它食人魔取代你的位置的。这就是戈多克的行事之道！',Text5_0_loc4='我很聪明！我知道二加二等于五！' WHERE entry=6922; /* Text4_0: So long as you stay here with us, you da king.  You take off, and some other ogre will take your place.  That\'s da way of da Gordok! */ /* Text5_0: I am so smart!  S-M-R-T! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='老国王死了吗？那不可能！',Text7_0_loc4='国王陛下，我可没有给你带来什么麻烦。' WHERE entry=6922; /* Text6_0: Old king got dead?  That\'s unpossible! */ /* Text7_0: I cause you no trouble, boss. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不跟米兹勒讲话，你就不能变成国王!跟狡猾的米兹勒讲话!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。' WHERE entry=6923; /* Text0_0: If you not talk to Mizzle, you not become da king!  Take to Mizzle da Crafty! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那麽...你杀死了国王?我就知道这些家伙会拥戴你成为新国王的。我就知道!那些家伙只知道力量。$B$B似乎你赦免的跟随者越多，献殷勤的人也就越多。别这麽不公平─我是说来一次有趣的挑战。如果你离开，我也不敢期望继续当国王。这些家伙肯定有人趁机取代你的地位。$B$B还有...你找到了我的钥匙，是吗?' WHERE entry=6924; /* Text0_0: So... you took out the King eh?  I knew that these bozos would make you the new king, I just knew it!  That\'s all these bozos understand - power.$B$BIt would seem that the more henchmen you keep alive, the higher your tribute will be.  Not to shabby - makes for an interesting challenge I\'d say.  If you leave, I wouldn\'t expect to remain king.  One of these yokels will no doubt step up and take your place.$B$BOne more thing... you didn\'t happen to find my key, did you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须明白，像我这样活了一万年的人，对生命有独特的看法。现在你经受的考验和磨难都是毫无意义的。' WHERE entry=6925; /* Text0_0: What you must understand is that being able to index 10,000 years of existence has given me a rather unique perspective on life. Your present day trials and tribulations are meaningless. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，年轻的主人制造的这一系列事件和慌乱。可以想像，世界的命运就掌控在他手中。只有人类才会对世界产生这种扭曲的看法。$B$B唉，他将秘法的秘密都告诉了我……圣契之类的无用之物。这种东西对我来说是一无是处，但是或许你对它们感兴趣。' WHERE entry=6926; /* Text0_0: Oh the drama and fuss the young Master exerted. You would think the fate of the world rested squarely on his shoulders. Only mortals could have such a skewed perspective on our world.$B$BAlas, he left me with his meager magical secrets... Librams or some such nonsense. I have no use for these paultry magics but perhaps you might be interested in their enchantments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='被偷啦，$r!我们最珍贵的三卷卷轴。如果你能找回来的话，一定会得到丰厚的报酬的。' WHERE entry=6927; /* Text0_0: They\'ve been stolen, $r! Three of our most prized volumes. Should you return the tomes, a reward will most certainly be yours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你无法理解这份卷轴上记载的任何技术。>' WHERE entry=6929; /* Text0_0: <You cannot comprehend any of the technical mumbo jumbo on this scroll.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<羊皮纸上画着的是修理机器人的结构示意图。>' WHERE entry=6930; /* Text0_0: <Drawn out on this parchment is the schematic for a field repair robot.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<依你目前的工程学技能是看不懂这张复杂的结构图的。>' WHERE entry=6931; /* Text0_0: <The complicated schematics are too much for your meager engineering talents to discern.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你精通制造和操作这个机器人。>' WHERE entry=6932; /* Text0_0: <You are well versed in the creation and function of this robot.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='世界的构造精妙细致。只靠某些知识和对已知知识的应用是不可能破坏世界构造的。裂隙也由此产生。' WHERE entry=6933; /* Text0_0: The fabric of which our world is woven is most delicate. It merely takes some knowledge and the application of said knowledge to tear the fabric. It is thusly that rifts are born. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='盯着敌人，$r。看吧，强大的部落足以对付巨龙!所有跟我们做对的人都是这种下场!' WHERE entry=6934; /* Text0_0: Gaze upon the enemy, $r. See what the might of the Horde reduces even the most powerful of dragons to! All that oppose us shall meet a similar fate! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我当然是来传达大酋长的命令的。我是部落的。' WHERE entry=6935; /* Text0_0: I am he that carries out the Warchief\'s commands without question. I am Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我活着就是为了为国王服务。' WHERE entry=6936; /* Text0_0: I live only to serve our King. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='或许有一天，你对联盟的贡献会跟你今日所见的英雄一样伟大。尊重英雄吧，$N。' WHERE entry=6937; /* Text0_0: Perhaps one day, your contributions to the Alliance will be as great as the heroes you have seen this day. Honor them, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='拥有万年历史的知识卷轴将那些邪恶的家伙吸引到图书馆。大量的书籍被盗，被找回之后再次被盗。' WHERE entry=6939; /* Text0_0: 10,000 years of recorded knowledge tends to draw the wrong element to the Athenaeum. Books are stolen, recovered and stolen again on a daily basis. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='基尔达斯总是过分夸大。比如，「迦罗娜:潜行与诡计研究」已经被偷过400多次啦。$B$B图书馆的标志保护着这本卷轴，防止任何人偷看。',Text0_1_loc4='基尔达斯总是过分夸大。比如，「迦罗娜:潜行与诡计研究」已经被偷过400多次啦。$B$B图书馆的标志保护着这本卷轴，防止任何人偷看。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=6940; /* Text0_0: Kildrath tends to overdramatize the situation. For example, Garona: A Study on Stealth and Treachery, has been stolen over 400 times.$B$BThe mark of the Athenaeum protects the tomes, preventing any unauthorized viewings. */ /* Text0_1: Kildrath tends to overdramatize the situation. For example, Garona: A Study on Stealth and Treachery, has been stolen over 400 times.$B$BThe mark of the Athenaeum protects the tomes, preventing any unauthorized viewings. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可没时间停下来。' WHERE entry=6947; /* Text0_0: I have no time for interruptions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你吗?' WHERE entry=6948; /* Text0_0: Can I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我知道埃德萨拉斯。多年前，那儿曾是夜精灵的魔法要塞。$B$B你知道埃德萨拉斯吗，年轻人?也许有人会说这跟我目前的处境一致……但是我可不相信巧合这回事。' WHERE entry=6949; /* Text0_0: Aye, but I know it by its true name - Eldre\'Thalas.  It was a bastion of magical power for the night elves many, many years ago.$B$BYou know of Eldre\'Thalas, young one?  One might say that is coincidental to my current plight... but I am one not to believe in coincidence. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='塞纳里奥议会的人已经了解埃德萨拉斯的近况了。我陷入僵局，不知如何是好。我很可能向那些体格强健、善於作战的人寻求帮助。$B$B但是，要对埃德萨拉斯采取行动，就要了解关於丰硕的果实的知识。' WHERE entry=6950; /* Text0_0: Agents of the Cenarion Circle have uncovered disturbing information pertaining to the current situation in Eldre\'Thalas.  I am at an impasse as to what to do about it, and I will no doubt soon seek the aid of able bodied beings capable of handling themselves in a fight.$B$BTo properly take action in Eldre\'Thalas, however, is to understand the lore of an object known as the Fruit of Fertility. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多年前，埃德萨拉斯是魔法师的集中地，居住在那些神圣的大厅中的人都能使用强大的魔法。米莉仙·瑟琳就是这样一名夜精灵─她是个自然学家，能将自然本身的力量灌输到她铸造的神器中。$B$B丰饶之果便是她的杰作……她利用特殊的月井制造出一种奇异的葡萄酒，具备保护和生长的效力。埃德萨拉斯在葡萄酒的滋养下日益繁华起来。' WHERE entry=6951; /* Text0_0: In ages past, Eldre\'Thalas was a nexus of magical power, and those who dwelt within its hallowed halls wielded immense power.  One such night elf was Millicent Serene - a naturalist who willed the power of nature itself into potent artifacts she forged.$B$BThe Fruit of Fertility was her crowning achievement... she used a specially prepared moonwell to grow an exotic and vibrant vine that was imbued with an aura of protection and growth.  All of Eldre\'Thalas flourished from its existence. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='唉，事情似乎总是这样。和塞纳里奥议会的其他人一样，我也认为是米利的造物在先祖之战中毁掉了。但是我已经认识到，这种观点是错误的。$B$B丰硕的果实并未被摧毁……尽管现在它被称为恶魔之藤。它被埃德萨拉斯的恶魔领主『狂野变形者』奥兹恩污染了。' WHERE entry=6952; /* Text0_0: Alas, it always seems like it does.  I - as did the rest of the Cenarion Circle - had assumed that Milli\'s creation was destroyed during the War of the Ancients.  This, as I have come to learn, is far from correct.$B$BThe Fruit of Fertility survived... though now it is known as the Felvine.  It is being corrupted by the demonic lord of that section of Eldre\'Thalas, Alzzin the Wildshaper. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我……我无法开始想像，$N。我只知道我不能让这件事发生。它会被摧毁的─就算不毁在我们对巨魔的防御上，也会毁在米莉仙·瑟琳的记忆上……米莉……$B$B我的朋友，这就是我希望你伸出援手的事情。' WHERE entry=6953; /* Text0_0: I... cannot begin to imagine, $N.  All I know is that I am not going to allow it to happen.  It will be destroyed - if not for our continued safety from demonic taint, then for the memory of Millicent Serene... Milli...$B$BThis, my friend, this is where I hope you will come in. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<德米提恩跪倒在地。>$B$B你已经找回了主人的牢笼！$B$B我期待这一天已经很久很久了，我的愿望终于实现了。$B$B必须解放我的主人！' WHERE entry=6954; /* Text0_0: <Demitrian falls to his knees.>$B$BYou have recovered my Master\'s eternal prison!$B$BOh long have I waited for this day and finally, it is realized.$B$BHe must be released! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这里有他的重生之瓶。如果你决心接受这项任务，就必须保护好这只小瓶，并击败拉格纳罗斯！' WHERE entry=6955; /* Text0_0: I hold the vessel of his rebirth. Should you be prepared to take on this task, you will be required to fortify the vessel and ultimately, break the hold of Ragnaros himself! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='必须使用源质对重生之瓶进行加固。我只知道这种矿物的一种原料：位于这个世界核心中的元素领域。$B$B塑地者对这种东西的了解比我多得多。你必须找到塑地者！' WHERE entry=6956; /* Text0_0: The vessel of rebirth must be fortified with elementium. I know of only one source of the mineral: the elemental planes, at the core of our world.$B$BThere is one, an Earthshaper, who may know more than I about the acquisition of such things. You must find this Earthshaper! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='向你致敬，英雄!我有来自大陆和岛屿的最新消息，供你参考。',Text0_1_loc4='向你致敬，英雄!我有来自大陆和岛屿的最新消息，供你参考。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=6957; /* Text0_0: Greetings and salutations, hero!  I have the latest news from both continents and points beyond for your consideration. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings and salutations, hero!  I have the latest news from both continents and points beyond for your consideration. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须摧毁拉格纳罗斯的肉身，他的精华将在尸体的残骸中出现。在他极度虚弱的时候，他对桑德兰的控制将被大大减弱。精华本身就是一把钥匙……' WHERE entry=6958; /* Text0_0: The corporeal form of Ragnaros must be destroyed. From the remnants, his essence shall emerge. In this weakened state, Ragnaros\' grip on the prison of Thunderaan is loosed. The essence itself acting as a key... */
