UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='唉...很抱歉，我现在还不能告诉你关於你的命运，你不久前才从我这儿获得了关於命运的资讯。$B$B过几个小时你再来找我吧。命运的力量将会有所改变，那时候我就可以洞察你的未来了。' WHERE entry=7393; /* Text0_0: Alas... I am sorry to say I cannot currently give you your fortune, as you have recently received a fortune reading from me.$B$BReturn to me several hours from when you first received your fortune.  The forces of Fate will have properly recalibrated themselves, and I will be able to see into your future. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$N，很高兴再次见到你!你玩得开心吗?$B$B想要来比腕力吗?不，当然不……你还想保有自己的手臂吧!',Text0_1_loc4='$N，很高兴再次见到你!你玩得开心吗?$B$B想要来比腕力吗?不，当然不……你还想保有自己的手臂吧!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7394; /* Text0_0: $N, it\'s good to see you again!  Are you having fun at the Faire?$B$BWant to arm wrestle?  No, of course not... you want to keep your arm! */ /* Text0_1: $N, it\'s good to see you again!  Are you having fun at the Faire?$B$BWant to arm wrestle?  No, of course not... you want to keep your arm! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。我是克洛诺斯－－过目不忘的克洛诺斯。我的记忆力毫无瑕疵，而且连最微小的细节都记得一清二楚。$B$B相信我。' WHERE entry=7395; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  I am Chronos - He Who Never Forgets.  My memory is without flaw, and exact to the most minor detail.$B$BTrust me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好!欢迎你!恐怕我的摊位还不能开张...有很多东西得修理...$B$B但是我仍然受制於血的诅咒，求你啦，笑一笑吧。如果你的脸上没有笑容的话，我就得砍下我的手，并且在手掌再生之前不得食用任何肉类...' WHERE entry=7397; /* Text0_0: Hello!  And welcome!  I\'m afraid my booth is not open... many repairs are needed...$B$BBut I am still bound by blood oath to put a smile on your face.  So please, smile, or I must cut off my hand and consume no living flesh until it regenerates... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我找不到我的宠物啾啾啦。她喜欢喝黑铁麦芽酒，那是她唯一肯喝的饮料，但是却很难取得!现在麦芽酒已经没有了...啾啾一定是自己跑去找酒喝了!$B$B我希望她可以赶快回来...',Text0_1_loc4='我找不到我的宠物啾啾啦。她喜欢喝黑铁麦芽酒，那是她唯一肯喝的饮料，但是却很难取得!现在麦芽酒已经没有了...啾啾一定是自己跑去找酒喝了!$B$B我希望她可以赶快回来...',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7400; /* Text0_0: I can\'t find my pet frog, Jubjub.  She loves Dark Iron Ale, it\'s all she ever drinks, but can be so hard to get!  Now I\'m out... and Jubjub must have run away to find more!$B$BI wish she would come back... */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t find my pet frog, Jubjub.  She loves Dark Iron Ale, it\'s all she ever drinks, but can be so hard to get!  Now I\'m out... and Jubjub must have run away to find more!$B$BI wish she would come back... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
