UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='臭泥鱼是一种散发着特殊臭味的鱼，它们生活在热带水域中。祖利安臭泥鱼则是其中最臭的一种，只有在祖尔格拉布的水域中才能找到。$B$B我想一定是祖力安臭泥鱼引来了加兹兰卡，尽管食人妖会告诉你它是食人妖膜拜的众多神灵之一，但是……$B$B相信自己─用祖利安臭泥鱼制成的诱饵去捕捉加兹兰卡吧，那家伙肯定会上钩的!' WHERE entry=7645; /* Text0_0: Mudskunks are a particularly smelly breed of fish that likes tropical waters.  The Zulian Mudskunk - the smelliest of them all, can only be found in the steamy waters of Zul\'Gurub.$B$BThe Zulian Mudskunks are what I believe attracted Gahz\'ranka to the place, though trolls will probably tell you he\'s one of their gods...$B$BBelieve what you like, but mark me - fill one of my lures with Zulian Mudskunks and that old boy will come, for sure! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text0_1_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text1_0_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text1_1_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。' WHERE entry=7646; /* Text0_0: You go Royal Quarter.  See Sir Malory Wheeler.  Him scary. */ /* Text0_1: You go Royal Quarter.  See Sir Malory Wheeler.  Him scary. */ /* Text1_0: Arathi Basin place to take from soft humans.  Sir Malory Wheeler send you there. */ /* Text1_1: Arathi Basin place to take from soft humans.  Sir Malory Wheeler send you there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁・林塞。他会帮助你转至阿拉希盆地。',Text0_1_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁・林塞。他会帮助你转至阿拉希盆地。',Text1_0_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁·林塞。他会帮助你前往阿拉希盆地。',Text1_1_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁·林塞。他会帮助你前往阿拉希盆地。' WHERE entry=7648; /* Text0_0: You may seek out Martin Lindsey inside the Pools of Vision, underneath the Spirit Rise.  He will assist you on your way to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text0_1: You may seek out Martin Lindsey inside the Pools of Vision, underneath the Spirit Rise.  He will assist you on your way to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_0: You wish to aid The Defilers in their fight against The League of Arathor in Arathi Basin?  Very well, you should ask Martin Lindsey for his assistance then.  Look for him in the Pools of Vision. */ /* Text1_1: You wish to aid The Defilers in their fight against The League of Arathor in Arathi Basin?  Very well, you should ask Martin Lindsey for his assistance then.  Look for him in the Pools of Vision. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔・奥斯古德谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔・奥斯古德谈谈。',Text1_0_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔·奥斯古德谈谈。',Text1_1_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔·奥斯古德谈谈。' WHERE entry=7649; /* Text0_0: The humans are in need of your assistance in their fight against The Forsaken at Arathi Basin.  Go to the Hall of Arms and speak with their representative, Donal Osgood. */ /* Text0_1: The humans are in need of your assistance in their fight against The Forsaken at Arathi Basin.  Go to the Hall of Arms and speak with their representative, Donal Osgood. */ /* Text1_0: The League of Arathor is trying to reclaim their ancestral holdings in Arathi Basin from the Forsaken.  If you would aid them $N speak to Donal Osgood in the Hall of Arms. */ /* Text1_1: The League of Arathor is trying to reclaim their ancestral holdings in Arathi Basin from the Forsaken.  If you would aid them $N speak to Donal Osgood in the Hall of Arms. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你转至阿拉希盆地的。',Text0_1_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你转至阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_0_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你前往阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_1_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你前往阿拉希盆地的。' WHERE entry=7650; /* Text0_0: In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers. */ /* Text0_1: In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers. */ /* Text1_0: It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_1: It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人类迫切需要我们在阿拉希盆地给予援助，有个人你可能需要和他谈谈，他叫克拉斯·狼心，他就在战士区等着你呢。',Text0_1_loc4='人类迫切需要我们在阿拉希盆地给予援助，有个人你可能需要和他谈谈，他叫克拉斯·狼心，他就在战士区等着你呢。',Text1_0_loc4='$c，如果那就是你的愿望，那么去战士区找克拉斯·沃夫哈特谈谈。他是阿拉索联军的代表，能帮助你到达阿拉希盆地。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7651; /* Text0_0: The humans definitely need all of our help in Arathi Basin.  The one that you wish to speak to is named Keras Wolfheart.  He stands ready to assist you on the Warrior\'s Terrace. */ /* Text0_1: The humans definitely need all of our help in Arathi Basin.  The one that you wish to speak to is named Keras Wolfheart.  He stands ready to assist you on the Warrior\'s Terrace. */ /* Text1_0: If that is your wish $c, then you will need to speak to Keras Wolfheart on the Warrior\'s Terrace.  He is a representative of The League of Arathor and can help you to get to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
