UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为了部落，$c!奥特兰克山谷需要你。我可以把你加到名单上吗?',Text0_1_loc4='为了部落，$c!奥特兰克山谷需要你。我可以把你加到名单上吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7660; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar $c!  We have need of your services in Alterac Valley.  Shall I add you to the lists? */ /* Text0_1: Lok\'tar $c!  We have need of your services in Alterac Valley.  Shall I add you to the lists? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在奥特兰克山谷的军队需要运用谋略才能获胜，$c。你看起来是个不错的领导者。' WHERE entry=7661; /* Text0_0: Our forces in Alterac Valley need wisdom to achieve victory $c.  You look like the one to lead them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希望你是来奥特兰克山谷作战的，$N。我们会竭尽所能，利用一切援助。' WHERE entry=7662; /* Text0_0: I hope that you are here to go to Alterac Valley $N.  We can use all o\' the help that we can get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人类和他们所谓的阿拉索联军想把我们赶出阿拉希盆地。我可不这麽想，$c!你得动身前往那儿，证明该离开阿拉希盆地的是他们而不是污染者，准备好了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='人类和他们所谓的阿拉索联军想把我们赶出阿拉希盆地。我可不这麽想，$c!你得动身前往那儿，证明该离开阿拉希盆地的是他们而不是污染者，准备好了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7663; /* Text0_0: The humans and their so-called League of Arathor think to push us out of Arathi Basin.  I think not $c!  Are you ready to be sent there and demonstrate that it is they, and not The Defilers, that will be leaving soon? */ /* Text0_1: The humans and their so-called League of Arathor think to push us out of Arathi Basin.  I think not $c!  Are you ready to be sent there and demonstrate that it is they, and not The Defilers, that will be leaving soon? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿拉希盆地曾经是我们的家园，有了你的帮助，我们会收复失地的!你愿意帮助我们吗，$c?' WHERE entry=7664; /* Text0_0: Arathi Basin was once our home, and will be again with your aid!  Will you help us $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你是来帮助我们从污染者手中夺回阿拉希盆地的。你说是吗，$N?' WHERE entry=7665; /* Text0_0: I hope that you\'re here to help us take back Arathi Basin from The Defilers.  What do you say $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一直在盼着你呢，$N。我们在阿拉希盆地的战斗需要你的帮助，你准备好了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我一直在盼着你呢，$N。我们在阿拉希盆地的战斗需要你的帮助，你准备好了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7666; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been expecting you $N.  Are you ready to assist us in Arathi Basin? */ /* Text0_1: I\'ve been expecting you $N.  Are you ready to assist us in Arathi Basin? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为你能摧毁阿拉索联军吗，$c?希望如此。你究竟想要干什麽呢，还是你根本就是来浪费我的时间的?' WHERE entry=7667; /* Text0_0: You think you have what it takes to destroy The League of Arathor, $c?  I hope so.  What is it that you want, or are you simply here to waste my time? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看四周，$c。你身边的朋友并不多，我想你需要证明自己的价值。嗯，或许我应该同意你帮助我们在阿拉希盆地作战。你愿意吗?' WHERE entry=7668; /* Text0_0: Look around you $c.  You are in rare company to be certain, yet still I think you need to prove yourself.  Hmm, perhaps I shall allow you to aid us in our cause at Arathi Basin.  Would you like that? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='钢铁之血格里雷克$B$B漫游者。愿他的力量和对战争的渴望生生不息。$B$B格里雷克就在疯狂之缘那边……' WHERE entry=7669; /* Text0_0: Gri\'lek, of the Iron Blood$B$BThe wanderer.  May his strength and lust for battle pierce the ages.$B$BGri\'lek now lingers near the edge of madness... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='织梦者哈札拉尔。$B$B他拥有梦魇的力量，愿他的敌人永远沉睡。$B$B哈札拉尔正在遥远的地方徘徊。总有一天，他会回来的……' WHERE entry=7670; /* Text0_0: Hazza\'rah, the Dreamweaver.$B$BHis is the power of nightmares, and may his foes ever sleep.  $B$BHazza\'rah now dwells far from here.  One day, he may return... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='千刃之王雷纳塔基。$B$B痛苦是他的生命。恐怖是他的夥伴。愿他早日重返世间。$B$B雷纳塔基就在疯狂之缘那边。' WHERE entry=7673; /* Text0_0: Renataki, of the Thousand Blades.$B$BPain is his lifeblood.  Fear, his ally.  May he one day return and bring joyous bloodshed with him.$B$BRenataki now dwells near the edge of madness. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='『雷巫』乌苏雷。$B$B他拥有天空、雨水和大地的力量。愿他再次统治古拉巴什。$B$B乌苏雷正在遥远的地方徘徊。总有一天，他会回来的……' WHERE entry=7674; /* Text0_0: Wushoolay, the Storm Witch.$B$BHer power is the power of the sky, the rain, and the shattered earth.  May she once again reign mother to the Gurubashi.  $B$BWushoolay now dwells far from here.  One day, she may return... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿嘿嘿!我是来这里推广荆棘谷的超棒钓鱼锦标赛的，不过你首先得有足够的生存能力在这里活下去，然后还需要足以在这里钓鱼的精湛技巧。$B$B当你更符合以上条件的时候再回到这里来吧!' WHERE entry=7676; /* Text0_0: Hey Hey Hey!  I am here to promote a fabulous fishing tournament in Stranglethorn but you need to be tough enough to survive there and have enough skill in fishing to fish those waters.$B$BCome back later when you are more qualified!$B$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨!嗨!嗨!如果你想要试试自己的钓鱼技能，那麽你来对地方啦!本周日荆棘谷将举办一场钓鱼大赛!' WHERE entry=7677; /* Text0_0: Heya Heya Heya!   If you want to test your fishing skills then I have just the place for you!   This Sunday we have a fishing tournament in Stranglethorn!$B$B */
