UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$C。看来你最近在进行一项秘密的收集工作?你还是老样子，但是这是个繁忙的城市。$B$B如果你参加了那场会议，你就该得到一段验证码。把验证码告诉我，我就会给你一份特殊的奖励作为回报。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$C。看来你最近在进行一项秘密的收集工作?你还是老样子，但是这是个繁忙的城市。$B$B如果你参加了那场会议，你就该得到一段验证码。把验证码告诉我，我就会给你一份特殊的奖励作为回报。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7780; /* Text0_0: Hail $c. Didn\'t I see you recently at an exclusive gathering? You look familiar, but then again this city is a busy place.$B$BIf you attended that convention, then surely you were given a secret code. Tell me your code and I will give you a special prize in return. */ /* Text0_1: Hail $c. Didn\'t I see you recently at an exclusive gathering? You look familiar, but then again this city is a busy place.$B$BIf you attended that convention, then surely you were given a secret code. Tell me your code and I will give you a special prize in return. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$N!我希望你已经准备好要工作了，因为在逐日者之岛有很多事等着你做。$B$B自从阿萨斯和天谴军团摧毁了太阳之井，我们就在海边过着漂浮不定的生活。我们存活在被遗忘的边缘。一切将会改变，$c，你将会学习很多的东西，并同时协助我们重建。$B$B外域正等着我们!',Text0_1_loc4='$N!我希望你已经准备好要工作了，因为在逐日者之岛有很多事等着你做。$B$B自从阿萨斯和天谴军团摧毁了太阳之井，我们就在海边过着漂浮不定的生活。我们存活在被遗忘的边缘。一切将会改变，$c，你将会学习很多的东西，并同时协助我们重建。$B$B外域正等着我们!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7781; /* Text0_0: $N!  I hope you\'re ready to get to work, because there is much for you to do here on Sunstrider Isle.$B$BEver since the destruction of the Sunwell by Arthas and the Scourge, we have been a race adrift on a sea of uncertainty.  We teeter on the edge of oblivion.  This will change, $c, and you will learn and aid our recovery at the same time.$B$BThe Outland awaits us! */ /* Text0_1: $N!  I hope you\'re ready to get to work, because there is much for you to do here on Sunstrider Isle.$B$BEver since the destruction of the Sunwell by Arthas and the Scourge, we have been a race adrift on a sea of uncertainty.  We teeter on the edge of oblivion.  This will change, $c, and you will learn and aid our recovery at the same time.$B$BThe Outland awaits us! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='塞纳里奥议会是睿智的，他们发现了很多有关大地的秘密。愿意聆听这些德鲁伊的教诲的工匠总是会得到许多宝贵的知识。',Text0_1_loc4='塞纳里奥议会是睿智的，他们发现了很多有关大地的秘密。愿意聆听这些德鲁伊的教诲的工匠总是会得到许多宝贵的知识。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7782; /* Text0_0: The Cenarion Circle is wise, and has delved into many of earth\'s secrets.  Craftsmen would do well to heed the words of these druids. */ /* Text0_1: The Cenarion Circle is wise, and has delved into many of earth\'s secrets.  Craftsmen would do well to heed the words of these druids. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个鬼魅般的身影不信任地看着你，并且保持着沉默。',Text0_1_loc4='这个鬼魅般的身影不信任地看着你，并且保持着沉默。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7783; /* Text0_0: The ghostly figure looks at you with mistrust in her eyes and remains silent. */ /* Text0_1: The ghostly figure looks at you with mistrust in her eyes and remains silent. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='曾经……日尖塔处於太阳之井旁的优渥位置。如今我们的生活方式从天堂掉落了地狱，$N，但我们仍在努力向前迈进。我们是幸存者，这是我们的生存方式。$B$B如果你想从这场动乱中活下来……靠自己的力量活下去，那你一定要学会如何生存。所有的血精灵都是如此。你一定要在心中对於魔法永无止尽的渴望主宰你之前先主宰它。' WHERE entry=7784; /* Text0_0: The Sunspire held a beautiful vantage of the Sunwell... once.  Our lives have been turned upside down, $N, but we nonetheless carry on.  It is our way; we are survivors.$B$BIf you are to survive this upheaval... to carry on in your own right, then you MUST learn how to survive.  All blood elves must do this.  You must master your insatiable hungering for magic before it masters you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对血精灵长久以来的贡献是我们种族生存最重要的助力!我们一定要同心协力突破目前的困境。$B$B如果你已经做好了准备，那就让我们开始吧。' WHERE entry=7785; /* Text0_0: Your continued service to the Blood Elves is paramount to our survival!  We must all pitch in and pull ourselves out of the mire we all find ourselves in.$B$BIf you\'re ready to work, then let\'s get started. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='知识就是力量 - 真正的力量，我年轻的朋友。获得越多知识就会让你越有智慧，并且从那些有智慧的人身上学习吧。$B$B在太阳之井被夷平前，我们还自以为我们的文明发展已经攀上了最高峰。是天谴军团迫使我们屈服……并且，看清这个事实。' WHERE entry=7786; /* Text0_0: Knowledge is power - TRUE power, my young friend.  You\'ll be wise to acquire as much of it as you can, and pay proper heed to those who have already done so.$B$BBefore the razing of the Sunwell, we fooled ourselves into thinking we had neared the apex of our civilization.  It took the Scourge to bring us to our knees... and in a way, back to reality. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在我研究最关键的时刻打扰了我!别担心，欢迎你加入我一起安静的沉思……重点是「安静」，如果你不介意的话。' WHERE entry=7787; /* Text0_0: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research!  No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你正前往那座城市的话，那麽我有一件重要的事情要你去做!',Text0_1_loc4='如果你正前往那座城市的话，那麽我有一件重要的事情要你去做!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7788; /* Text0_0: If you\'re heading toward the city, then I have something important for you to do! */ /* Text0_1: If you\'re heading toward the city, then I have something important for you to do! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎!上前来，不要害羞。这是我最自豪的发明……冲击者5000型超级大炮!她难道不漂亮吗?她实在就是很漂亮啊!看起来对於炮管的中段来说，你的体型稍微大了一点，但是我想这不是什麽大问题。飞行充满了乐趣，你想要学学吗?',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎!上前来，不要害羞。这是我最自豪的发明……冲击者5000型超级大炮!她难道不漂亮吗?她实在就是很漂亮啊!看起来对於炮管的中段来说，你的体型稍微大了一点，但是我想这不是什麽大问题。飞行充满了乐趣，你想要学学吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7789; /* Text0_0: Welcome! Step right up, don\'t be shy. This here is my pride and joy... the Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon! Ain\'t she pretty? You look a little big around the mid section, but I think you\'ll fit. Flying is so much fun, want to learn how? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome! Step right up, don\'t be shy. This here is my pride and joy... the Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon! Ain\'t she pretty? You look a little big around the mid section, but I think you\'ll fit. Flying is so much fun, want to learn how? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，很简单的!这东西的使用方法和你以前用过的那些东西没什麽两样。别担心，我会负责点火。当你升空之后，你会发现自己正「飘浮」在空中，但是这种情况不会持续很久。你将被发射到湖边的一个目标那里去。只要记得在适当的时候将你的「翅膀」分离，就可以安全地掉入湖中了!不然的话，嗯，我不负责出售人身保险。',Text0_1_loc4='嗯，很简单的!这东西的使用方法和你以前用过的那些东西没什麽两样。别担心，我会负责点火。当你升空之后，你会发现自己正「飘浮」在空中，但是这种情况不会持续很久。你将被发射到湖边的一个目标那里去。只要记得在适当的时候将你的「翅膀」分离，就可以安全地掉入湖中了!不然的话，嗯，我不负责出售人身保险。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7790; /* Text0_0: Oh that\'s simple! You use it like anything else you might activate. Don\'t worry, I\'ll take care of lighting the fuse. Once you\'re up in the air you\'ll notice that you\'ll seem to "float," but that won\'t last forever. What you\'re aiming for is a target on the lake way over yonder. Make sure that you begin your descent by detaching your "wings" at the right time to land in the water, or, well, I don\'t sell life insurance. */ /* Text0_1: Oh that\'s simple! You use it like anything else you might activate. Don\'t worry, I\'ll take care of lighting the fuse. Once you\'re up in the air you\'ll notice that you\'ll seem to "float," but that won\'t last forever. What you\'re aiming for is a target on the lake way over yonder. Make sure that you begin your descent by detaching your "wings" at the right time to land in the water, or, well, I don\'t sell life insurance. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='您好，$c，欢迎来到暗月马戏团。在马戏团这里有太多可以做的事情了，所以第一次来的客人可能感到有些不知所措。这就是我在这里帮忙的原因。您有什麽问题吗?',Text0_1_loc4='您好，$c，欢迎来到暗月马戏团。在马戏团这里有太多可以做的事情了，所以第一次来的客人可能感到有些不知所措。这就是我在这里帮忙的原因。您有什麽问题吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7792; /* Text0_0: Hello $c, and welcome to the Darkmoon Faire. There is so much to do here at the faire that it can be a little overwhelming for our first time visitors. That\'s why I\'m here to help. Do you have any questions? */ /* Text0_1: Hello $c, and welcome to the Darkmoon Faire. There is so much to do here at the faire that it can be a little overwhelming for our first time visitors. That\'s why I\'m here to help. Do you have any questions? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个很好的问题!我们马戏团这里有很多东西出售。如果您对食物和饮料感兴趣的话，那麽您可以去斯塔姆和塞兰妮亚的小店看看。我最喜欢的就是暗月特别套餐。$B$B如果您想要购买一些特别的东西，那麽兰拉出售的货物将会很适合您。她擅长於从世界各地收集稀有的东西。$B$B另外从到处跑来跑去的弗里克那里购买可以用於投掷的球和宠物青蛙。',Text0_1_loc4='一个很好的问题!我们马戏团这里有很多东西出售。如果您对食物和饮料感兴趣的话，那麽您可以去斯塔姆和塞兰妮亚的小店看看。我最喜欢的就是暗月特别套餐。$B$B如果您想要购买一些特别的东西，那麽兰拉出售的货物将会很适合您。她擅长於从世界各地收集稀有的东西。$B$B另外从到处跑来跑去的弗里克那里购买可以用於投掷的球和宠物青蛙。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7793; /* Text0_0: An excellent question! We have many things for sale here at the faire. If you are interested in food and drink, then head over to Stamp and Sylannia\'s booth. My favorite is the Darkmoon Special Reserve.$B$BIf you\'d rather purchase something more exotic, then Lhara may have just the thing for you. She specializes in rarities from all over the world.$B$BAnd then there is Flik running around here somewhere. If you can grab him he sells balls for throwing and frogs to keep as pets.$B */ /* Text0_1: An excellent question! We have many things for sale here at the faire. If you are interested in food and drink, then head over to Stamp and Sylannia\'s booth. My favorite is the Darkmoon Special Reserve.$B$BIf you\'d rather purchase something more exotic, then Lhara may have just the thing for you. She specializes in rarities from all over the world.$B$BAnd then there is Flik running around here somewhere. If you can grab him he sells balls for throwing and frogs to keep as pets.$B */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴您问到这个问题。暗月马戏团奖品券是我们鼓励大家帮助马戏团所推出的，您可以使用这些奖品券来兑换特别的奖品!$B$B首先您可以找克洛诺斯、克莉·希克斯和亚布·尼比盖尔谈谈来看看您有什麽可以帮他们的。他们总是需要帮助。$B$B当您有足够的奖品券时，和吉瓦斯·格里加特谈谈，他有很多奖品可供选择。',Text0_1_loc4='很高兴您问到这个问题。暗月马戏团奖品券是我们鼓励大家帮助马戏团所推出的，您可以使用这些奖品券来兑换特别的奖品!$B$B首先您可以找克洛诺斯、克莉·希克斯和亚布·尼比盖尔谈谈来看看您有什麽可以帮他们的。他们总是需要帮助。$B$B当您有足够的奖品券时，和吉瓦斯·格里加特谈谈，他有很多奖品可供选择。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7794; /* Text0_0: Glad you asked. Darkmoon Faire Prize Tickets are our way of letting you help with the faire, and in return you can turn in your tickets for special prizes!$B$BTo get started you\'ll want to talk to Chronos, Kerri Hicks, Ringling and Yebb Nebblegear to see who you can best help. They always have something that needs doing to improve and expand our attractions.$B$BThen when you have enough tickets, speak with Gelvas Grimegate and he will give you a list of prizes to choose from.$B */ /* Text0_1: Glad you asked. Darkmoon Faire Prize Tickets are our way of letting you help with the faire, and in return you can turn in your tickets for special prizes!$B$BTo get started you\'ll want to talk to Chronos, Kerri Hicks, Ringling and Yebb Nebblegear to see who you can best help. They always have something that needs doing to improve and expand our attractions.$B$BThen when you have enough tickets, speak with Gelvas Grimegate and he will give you a list of prizes to choose from.$B */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有人知道谁制作了暗月卡片，或者他们真正的意图是什麽，但是我可以告诉你，在艾泽拉斯各地都可以找到它们，尤其是在那些试图揭开它秘密的邪恶怪物手中。',Text0_1_loc4='没有人知道谁制作了暗月卡片，或者他们真正的意图是什麽，但是我可以告诉你，在艾泽拉斯各地都可以找到它们，尤其是在那些试图揭开它秘密的邪恶怪物手中。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7795; /* Text0_0: No one really knows who made the Darkmoon Cards or what their true purpose is, but I can tell you that they have been found all over Azeroth, usually in the hands of a villain attempting to unlock their mysteries. */ /* Text0_1: No one really knows who made the Darkmoon Cards or what their true purpose is, but I can tell you that they have been found all over Azeroth, usually in the hands of a villain attempting to unlock their mysteries. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我极度推荐你去拜访赛吉得到你的未来预言。我知道，我知道…他是个食人妖。不过他是一个非常特别的食人妖，拥有占卜你未来的能力!$B$B而且我们一直持续地扩展马戏团在各方面的新吸引力!',Text0_1_loc4='我极度推荐你去拜访赛吉得到你的未来预言。我知道，我知道…他是个食人妖。不过他是一个非常特别的食人妖，拥有占卜你未来的能力!$B$B而且我们一直持续地扩展马戏团在各方面的新吸引力!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7796; /* Text0_0: I highly recommend that you visit Sayge to get your fortune told. I know, I know... he\'s a gnoll.  But he\'s a very special gnoll with the power to divine your future!$B$BAnd we are constantly expanding the faire with all manner of new attractions! */ /* Text0_1: I highly recommend that you visit Sayge to get your fortune told. I know, I know... he\'s a gnoll.  But he\'s a very special gnoll with the power to divine your future!$B$BAnd we are constantly expanding the faire with all manner of new attractions! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
