UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是个皮革商吧?我对兽皮的味道再熟悉不过了。$B$B我的父亲过去常常跟我谈起数世纪前一位居住在南风村的着名工匠。很遗憾，那儿已是一片废墟了。',Text0_1_loc4='你是个皮革商吧?我对兽皮的味道再熟悉不过了。$B$B我的父亲过去常常跟我谈起数世纪前一位居住在南风村的着名工匠。很遗憾，那儿已是一片废墟了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7820; /* Text0_0: You\'re a leatherworker by trade, aren\'t you?  It\'s that faint smell of cured hides, I\'d recognize it anywhere.$B$BMy father used to talk about a famous artisan who lived in Southwind Village centuries ago.  It\'s a shame the place is in ruins now. */ /* Text0_1: You\'re a leatherworker by trade, aren\'t you?  It\'s that faint smell of cured hides, I\'d recognize it anywhere.$B$BMy father used to talk about a famous artisan who lived in Southwind Village centuries ago.  It\'s a shame the place is in ruins now. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
