UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，我需要更多的铜锭。安其拉大门正在酝酿一场大战，我们需要补给！联盟已经收集了 $1997w 铜锭，我们总共需要 $1998w 铜锭。如果我收集不齐铜锭，我的脑袋就保不住了！' WHERE entry=7824; /* Text0_0: $C, I need more copper bars! There\'s a war brewing at the Gates of Ahn\'Qiraj and we need supplies! The Alliance has collected $1997w and we need $1998w copper bars in total. If I don\'t get those copper bars, it\'s going to be my head on a platter! */
