UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='詹迪斯·巴罗夫的日记写满了不死族夸大的豪言壮语。翻到书的最后一页，似乎出现一个某种制作背包的裁缝术语。以你对裁缝的了解还无法让你破解这术语。',Text0_1_loc4='詹迪斯·巴罗夫的日记写满了不死族夸大的豪言壮语。翻到书的最后一页，似乎出现一个某种制作背包的裁缝术语。以你对裁缝的了解还无法让你破解这术语。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8120; /* Text0_0: The journal of Jandice Barov is filled with rantings and ravings about the undead. Towards the end of the book is what appears to be a tailoring pattern for the creation of a bag of some sort. Your understanding of tailoring is insufficient to decipher the pattern. */ /* Text0_1: The journal of Jandice Barov is filled with rantings and ravings about the undead. Towards the end of the book is what appears to be a tailoring pattern for the creation of a bag of some sort. Your understanding of tailoring is insufficient to decipher the pattern. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有那些证明自己没有对木喉部族心怀敌意的人才能在部落被攻击时不感到害怕。你想努力赢得我们的信任吗，外来者?' WHERE entry=8123; /* Text0_0: Only those who have proven themselves to not be hostile toward the Timbermaw may pass through the Hold without fear of being attacked.  Have you made an effort to earn our trust, outsider? */
