UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鄙恶者一直是我方的眼中钉，$N。他们不是在汲取不稳定的秘法能源以满足其渴望，就是在计画着打垮我们美好的家园。' WHERE entry=8229; /* Text0_0: The Wretched are a constant thorn in my side, $N.  When they\'re not being a danger to themselves by tapping unstable arcane sources to satisfy their cravings, they\'re cooking up half-brained schemes against our respectable society. */
