UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='爱之硬币就是爱的小讯息，你可以给热情的城乡人们。他们会回送你象徵爱意的礼物。$B$B或者说，有人爱慕或崇拜你，他们也会给你友谊之礼。',Text0_1_loc4='爱之硬币就是爱的小讯息，你可以给热情的城乡人们。他们会回送你象徵爱意的礼物。$B$B或者说，有人爱慕或崇拜你，他们也会给你友谊之礼。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8307; /* Text0_0: Love tokens are small messages of affection you can give to amorous town and city folk.  Such people will reward you with a gift of adoration.$B$BOr, if you are already adored by another, then at the least they\'ll give you a gift of friendship. */ /* Text0_1: Love tokens are small messages of affection you can give to amorous town and city folk.  Such people will reward you with a gift of adoration.$B$BOr, if you are already adored by another, then at the least they\'ll give you a gift of friendship. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你喷点古龙水或香水，你就会发现某个人正含情脉脉的示意。他们专收爱之硬币…然后再回送你礼物。$B$B请记住:给别人硬币时，你也要闻起来香香的才行!男人喜欢香水的味道，而女人则偏爱古龙水的香味。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你喷点古龙水或香水，你就会发现某个人正含情脉脉的示意。他们专收爱之硬币…然后再回送你礼物。$B$B请记住:给别人硬币时，你也要闻起来香香的才行!男人喜欢香水的味道，而女人则偏爱古龙水的香味。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8308; /* Text0_0: If you put on cologne or perfume, then you\'ll see who is amorous.  Those are the ones who accept love tokens... and offer a gift in return.$B$BBut remember: to give someone a love token, you have to smell just right!  Men like the scent of perfume, while women prefer cologne. */ /* Text0_1: If you put on cologne or perfume, then you\'ll see who is amorous.  Those are the ones who accept love tokens... and offer a gift in return.$B$BBut remember: to give someone a love token, you have to smell just right!  Men like the scent of perfume, while women prefer cologne. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
