UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能教你龙鳞制皮，$N你必须去塔纳利斯，并找到纳里安·柔想的家。你到了那儿以后，询问有关一本叫做《新手的预言入门》的书。',Text0_1_loc4='我不能教你龙鳞制皮，$N你必须去塔纳利斯，并找到纳里安·柔想的家。你到了那儿以后，询问有关一本叫做《新手的预言入门》的书。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8327; /* Text0_0: I cannot teach you dragonscale leatherworking, $N. You must go to Tanaris and find the home of Narain Soothfancy. Once there, consult the book "Soothsaying for Dummies." */ /* Text0_1: I cannot teach you dragonscale leatherworking, $N. You must go to Tanaris and find the home of Narain Soothfancy. Once there, consult the book "Soothsaying for Dummies." */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='索尔让我进入他领地中的圣域是对我释出相当大的善意。无论如何，我不求久留。给我们的领导者带来任何麻烦都是极大的侮辱。' WHERE entry=8332; /* Text0_0: Thrall has shown great kindness in granting me sanctuary within his domain.  I do not wish to overstay my welcome, at any rate.  It would be a great dishonor if I brought any trouble to our leader. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='试着别引来太多注目，我正等着国王觐见。我不介意等待，在这些魁梧的守卫旁边我觉得相当有安全感。',Text0_1_loc4='试着别引来太多注目，我正等着国王觐见。我不介意等待，在这些魁梧的守卫旁边我觉得相当有安全感。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8333; /* Text0_0: Try not to draw too much attention, I\'m waiting for the King to grant me audience.  Not that I mind waiting, I feel pretty safe around all these burly guards. */ /* Text0_1: Try not to draw too much attention, I\'m waiting for the King to grant me audience.  Not that I mind waiting, I feel pretty safe around all these burly guards. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='丧命的危险是我常碰到的事。但失去亚希达是我不能容忍的事，就算我死了也是一样。' WHERE entry=8334; /* Text0_0: Losing my life was a danger I had come to terms with.  Losing Ysida is something I cannot endure, even after my own death. */
