UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一套无畏护甲是专为血色大领主莫格莱尼订做的。完成时，大领主觉得自己活生生像是从冥府来的恶魔。$B$B没错，这的确是个绝佳机会亲见莫格莱尼精神饱满的率领血色十字军，齐声呐喊、高举挥舞着灰烬使者，眼看另一端敌军於燃火飞尘之中在他的双脚下慌张撤离。' WHERE entry=8363; /* Text0_0: The first suit of Dreadnaught armor was made exclusively for the Scarlet Highlord Mograine. Whilst donning the full suit, the Highlord looked himself to be a demon from the depths of the Nether.$B$BAye, \'twas quite a sight to behold as Mograine would wade into a hundred Scourge, Ashbringer held high, and come out on the other side in a cloud of dust and flames - enemies left in ashes beneath his feet." */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在饱受争议的死亡事件之后，洛丹伦的骑士与战士为了向他们倒下的英雄表示敬意，纷纷都穿起类似的战袍。而莫格莱尼的死对科尔苏加德是伟大的胜利，最后殉难的结果要一直到战争结束才知分晓。$B$B一王倒下，他强必崛起…' WHERE entry=8364; /* Text0_0: It was not until after his controversial death that the knights and warriors of Lordaeron would wear similarly fashioned suits in honor of their fallen hero. While the death of Mograine was a great victory for Kel\'Thuzad, the resulting martyrdom would be felt until the end of the war.$B$BWhere one did fall, many would rise... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就是你口中的资本家，$r。' WHERE entry=8366; /* Text0_0: I\'m what you call a capitalist, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔，哈罗…嗯，你是?$B$B不要紧，是什麽风把你吹来我在这美丽乡村的离家之园啊?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8374; /* Text0_0: Oh, hello there.. um, what\'s your name?$B$BNo matter, what brings you to my home-away-from-home here out in the beautiful countryside? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$c。想必你们一定玩得很开心吧?你们觉得的派对好玩吗?希望我们派对上的东西都够供应。饮料跟开胃点心如果不够就是派对的致命伤啊，对吧?$B$B嗯，好啦，我要去招待其他宾客罗。尽兴玩。' WHERE entry=8375; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c. I trust that you are enjoying youself? What do you think of the party? I do so hope that we aren\'t running out of anything. Nothing kills a fete faster than running out of drinks and hors d\'oeuvres, wouldn\'t you say?$B$BYes, well, I must be about attending to my other guests. Do enjoy your stay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$g大人:小姐;。我相信你一定玩的很开心吧?',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$g大人:小姐;。我相信你一定玩的很开心吧?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8378; /* Text0_0: Greetings, my $g lord : lady;. I trust that you are having a pleasant time? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, my $g lord : lady;. I trust that you are having a pleasant time? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不觉得很好玩吗?我真高兴萨瑟里领主每晚都举办舞会，尤其是那些令人作呕的东西滚到南方，感觉就像把它们抛诸脑后，对吧?',Text0_1_loc4='你不觉得很好玩吗?我真高兴萨瑟里领主每晚都举办舞会，尤其是那些令人作呕的东西滚到南方，感觉就像把它们抛诸脑后，对吧?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8379; /* Text0_0: Isn\'t this just so much fun? I\'m so glad that Lord Saltheril throws these parties every night, especially with all of that nastiness occurring to the south. Kind of just makes all of that go away, don\'t you think? */ /* Text0_1: Isn\'t this just so much fun? I\'m so glad that Lord Saltheril throws these parties every night, especially with all of that nastiness occurring to the south. Kind of just makes all of that go away, don\'t you think? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我跟科尔苏加德一样都曾经是祈伦托的法师，我们也都在遍寻传说中的守护者之杖，阿泰丝。我们的命运是如此纠缠着，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='我跟科尔苏加德一样都曾经是祈伦托的法师，我们也都在遍寻传说中的守护者之杖，阿泰丝。我们的命运是如此纠缠着，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8388; /* Text0_0: Like Kel\'Thuzad, I too was once a mage of the Kirin Tor. And like Kel\'Thuzad, I seek the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian. Our fates are intertwined as such, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Like Kel\'Thuzad, I too was once a mage of the Kirin Tor. And like Kel\'Thuzad, I seek the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian. Our fates are intertwined as such, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='艾格文的后裔，他会成为提瑞斯法最后一位守护者…麦迪文。',Text0_1_loc4='艾格文的后裔，他会成为提瑞斯法最后一位守护者…麦迪文。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8389; /* Text0_0: Progeny of Aegwynn, he that would be the last Guardian of Tirisfal... Medivh. */ /* Text0_1: Progeny of Aegwynn, he that would be the last Guardian of Tirisfal... Medivh. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是一个传奇，这也是个我没时间和意愿重述的故事，只要知道麦迪文是最后一位守护者。阿泰丝大法杖是权力的核心，也是堕落的极点。',Text0_1_loc4='这是一个传奇，这也是个我没时间和意愿重述的故事，只要知道麦迪文是最后一位守护者。阿泰丝大法杖是权力的核心，也是堕落的极点。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8390; /* Text0_0: It is a story of legend and one that I do not have the time nor the inclination to retell. Just know that Medivh was the last of the Guardians. The greatstaff of Atiesh was a focal point of his power and a focal point of corruption. */ /* Text0_1: It is a story of legend and one that I do not have the time nor the inclination to retell. Just know that Medivh was the last of the Guardians. The greatstaff of Atiesh was a focal point of his power and a focal point of corruption. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='失败巨人的腐败，毁灭者的堕落。终究这法杖还是由仇恨的种子所锻造。也就是说，这当然是我来这里的主因…',Text0_1_loc4='失败巨人的腐败，毁灭者的堕落。终究这法杖还是由仇恨的种子所锻造。也就是说，这当然是我来这里的主因…',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8391; /* Text0_0: The corruption of a fallen titan. The corruption of the Destroyer. After all, the staff was forged from the seed of hate. That is, of course, what has brought me here... */ /* Text0_1: The corruption of a fallen titan. The corruption of the Destroyer. After all, the staff was forged from the seed of hate. That is, of course, what has brought me here... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在卡拉赞倒下后，祈伦托派了一群法师到哨塔搜索，并扣押所有进口的物品……就为了「研究」的目的。就是那时候才发现了寓言中的法杖，并将它带回达拉然。',Text0_1_loc4='在卡拉赞倒下后，祈伦托派了一群法师到哨塔搜索，并扣押所有进口的物品……就为了「研究」的目的。就是那时候才发现了寓言中的法杖，并将它带回达拉然。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8392; /* Text0_0: After the fall of Karazhan, the Kirin Tor dispatched an assembly of mages to search the tower and seize all items of import... for the purposes of "research." It was then that the fabled staff was discovered and brought back to Dalaran. */ /* Text0_1: After the fall of Karazhan, the Kirin Tor dispatched an assembly of mages to search the tower and seize all items of import... for the purposes of "research." It was then that the fabled staff was discovered and brought back to Dalaran. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所跟随的是一连串的悲剧，以致每位只要接触阿泰丝的祈伦托法师都会死亡。$B$B你看，这是有知觉的神器，是萨格拉斯赋予它的…',Text0_1_loc4='所跟随的是一连串的悲剧，以致每位只要接触阿泰丝的祈伦托法师都会死亡。$B$B你看，这是有知觉的神器，是萨格拉斯赋予它的…',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8393; /* Text0_0: What followed were a series of tragic events, leading to the death of every Kirin Tor mage that came into contact with Atiesh.$B$BYou see, it was an artifact with sentience. A sentience granted to it by Sargeras... */ /* Text0_1: What followed were a series of tragic events, leading to the death of every Kirin Tor mage that came into contact with Atiesh.$B$BYou see, it was an artifact with sentience. A sentience granted to it by Sargeras... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<安琪拉点头。>$B$B他们死后，六人决定最好的应变措施，就是藉由坚固的魔法屏障来隔离法杖，并且任命守护者︰法杖的守护者…而我就是那位守护者。',Text0_1_loc4='<安琪拉点头。>$B$B他们死后，六人决定最好的应变措施，就是藉由坚固的魔法屏障来隔离法杖，并且任命守护者︰法杖的守护者…而我就是那位守护者。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8394; /* Text0_0: <Angela nods.>$B$BAfter the deaths, the Six decided that the best course of action was to seal the staff behind impenetrable barriers of magic and appoint a watcher: A guardian of the staff... I would be that watcher. */ /* Text0_1: <Angela nods.>$B$BAfter the deaths, the Six decided that the best course of action was to seal the staff behind impenetrable barriers of magic and appoint a watcher: A guardian of the staff... I would be that watcher. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没什麽好说的。达拉然几乎全被阿克蒙德破坏，法杖遗失了，可能遭到故障防护装置机所粉碎了。$B$B有些人相信就是因为法杖，所以引起阿克蒙德的报复。',Text0_1_loc4='没什麽好说的。达拉然几乎全被阿克蒙德破坏，法杖遗失了，可能遭到故障防护装置机所粉碎了。$B$B有些人相信就是因为法杖，所以引起阿克蒙德的报复。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8395; /* Text0_0: There is not much more to tell. Dalaran was nearly wholly destroyed by Archimonde, the staff lost, presumably shattered by the barrier\'s fail-safe mechanisms.$B$BThere are those that believe the staff to be the cause of Archimonde\'s reprisal. */ /* Text0_1: There is not much more to tell. Dalaran was nearly wholly destroyed by Archimonde, the staff lost, presumably shattered by the barrier\'s fail-safe mechanisms.$B$BThere are those that believe the staff to be the cause of Archimonde\'s reprisal. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在达拉然被陷落之后，我也离开了祈伦托。我花了好几年寻找阿泰丝，希望能取回祈伦托在某次可怕的突袭中，从我身上夺取的东西。就算要花一辈子，我也要找到法杖。那就是为什麽我参加银色黎明，还有我现在为什麽在这里的原因。',Text0_1_loc4='在达拉然被陷落之后，我也离开了祈伦托。我花了好几年寻找阿泰丝，希望能取回祈伦托在某次可怕的突袭中，从我身上夺取的东西。就算要花一辈子，我也要找到法杖。那就是为什麽我参加银色黎明，还有我现在为什麽在这里的原因。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8396; /* Text0_0: After the fall of Dalaran, I took my leave from the Kirin Tor. I spent years watching over Atiesh, only to have my purpose amongst the Kirin Tor taken from me in one fell swoop. I would find the staff, though it might take a lifetime. That is how I came to join the Argent Dawn and why I am here now. */ /* Text0_1: After the fall of Dalaran, I took my leave from the Kirin Tor. I spent years watching over Atiesh, only to have my purpose amongst the Kirin Tor taken from me in one fell swoop. I would find the staff, though it might take a lifetime. That is how I came to join the Argent Dawn and why I am here now. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我横跨世界追踪了各式各样的法杖碎片，还因此发现科尔苏加德改良法杖的计画。他目前收集一些法杖碎片，并且由他最信赖的副官保管着。$B$B努力让守护者的大法杖远离科尔苏加德的控制，这重要性可是非比寻常。坦白说，除了史诗部分的大灾难外，我不知道结果将如何。',Text0_1_loc4='我横跨世界追踪了各式各样的法杖碎片，还因此发现科尔苏加德改良法杖的计画。他目前收集一些法杖碎片，并且由他最信赖的副官保管着。$B$B努力让守护者的大法杖远离科尔苏加德的控制，这重要性可是非比寻常。坦白说，除了史诗部分的大灾难外，我不知道结果将如何。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8397; /* Text0_0: I have tracked the various fragments of the staff across this world and in doing so, discovered Kel\'Thuzad\'s plans to reform the staff. He has already collected several of the staff\'s fragments - which are being held by his most trusted lieutenants.$B$BI cannot emphasize enough the importance of keeping the greatstaff of the Guardian out of Kel\'Thuzad\'s grasp. Frankly, I do not know what the result would be, other than a catastrophe of epic proportion. */ /* Text0_1: I have tracked the various fragments of the staff across this world and in doing so, discovered Kel\'Thuzad\'s plans to reform the staff. He has already collected several of the staff\'s fragments - which are being held by his most trusted lieutenants.$B$BI cannot emphasize enough the importance of keeping the greatstaff of the Guardian out of Kel\'Thuzad\'s grasp. Frankly, I do not know what the result would be, other than a catastrophe of epic proportion. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是权力，低能儿。<麦特斯眼眸加深。>$B$B这些傻瓜派了像你这样的白痴到纳克萨玛斯，取回玷污的护甲以便净化它，重组零件恢复昔日光采。$B$B<麦特斯啐了一口。>就是这种愚蠢至极的想法让我反胃想吐。$B$B我也去寻找护甲，我要找玷污以及被亵渎最深的护甲。' WHERE entry=8398; /* Text0_0: It is power, imbecile.$B$B<Mataus\'s eyes darken.>$B$BThese fools send idiots like you into Naxxramas to retrieve desecrated armor so that they may purify it and restore the pieces to their former glory.$B$B<Mataus spits.>$B$BJust the thought of such utter stupidity brings the bile up to my throat.$B$BI too seek that armor, but in its most foul and desecrated form. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不会装模作样，蛆虫。这种黑暗物品所支配的力量可以把我们两个都摧毁。这就是为什麽价格如此高昂的原因。如果我就要死了，也会是个富翁。$B$B你死了我也不会对你吐一口豺狼人的口水，照我的话做就对了。把我要的东西带来，我们就能双方受惠 - 或者死;我已经解释过了……' WHERE entry=8399; /* Text0_0: I make no pretenses, maggot. The darkness such items hold could very well destroy the both of us. That is why the price is so high. If I\'m going to die, it\'s going to be as a rich man.$B$BAnd I don\'t give an ounce of gnoll spit how you die, only that you do as I ask. Bring me what I require and we will both benefit - or die, but I\'ve already explained this... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们对那些生物都太仁慈了。我们应该用剑刺进每一具身体内。$B$B牠们先拿下了日帆，下一个是谁都还不知道呢?' WHERE entry=8402; /* Text0_0: We\'re too merciful with the Wretched. We ought to drive a sword through each of them.$B$BTheir boldness in Sunsail Anchorage is unpardonable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无止尽行进到死亡之痕，削减无心智的天谴军团，花了一整天时间。不要浪费时间了，除非你是来帮忙的，否则我很享受现在的安宁不想被打扰。',Text0_1_loc4='无止尽行进到死亡之痕，削减无心智的天谴军团，花了一整天时间。不要浪费时间了，除非你是来帮忙的，否则我很享受现在的安宁不想被打扰。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8403; /* Text0_0: It\'s been a long day of cutting down the mindless Scourge that endlessly parade down the Dead Scar.  I hope you\'re here to lend a hand and not to waste my time with idle chatter. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s been a long day of cutting down the mindless Scourge that endlessly parade down the Dead Scar.  I hope you\'re here to lend a hand and not to waste my time with idle chatter. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些该死的害虫!' WHERE entry=8406; /* Text0_0: Missing US text */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不想教牛头人骑乘迅猛龙。',Text0_1_loc4='我不想教牛头人骑乘迅猛龙。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8407; /* Text0_0: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些污秽的野兽充斥此地。$B$B如果你喜欢在户外狩猎的话，你可以在病木林跟恐惧谷寻获牠们大部分的踪迹，也请特别留意恶蛛隧道。牠们也可能出没在东瘟疫之地的天谴军团紮营处。$B$B假如你热衷於地城，你在斯坦索姆会发现更多牠们的踪影，另外，在通灵学院可以找到一些通灵魔。' WHERE entry=8408; /* Text0_0: Those filthy beasts are all over the place.$B$BIf you prefer hunting outdoors, you\'ll find most of them around Plaguewood and Terrordale, with a good concentration of them in the Terrorweb tunnel. They are also likely to appear at almost any Scourge encampment in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BIf you\'re a hearty dungeon crawler, you\'ll find a good lot of them in Stratholme and a few of the necrofiend variety in Scholomance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是笨蛋吗?遗失了你回程时那堆散乱路旁的骷髅类生物?<洛汉叹气。>$B$B如果你是户外型的人，你可在东、西瘟疫之地找到骷髅生物。相信我，你不能搞丢牠们－如果他们可以的话，他们一定不会放过你。倘若你是地城冒险型，斯坦索姆和通灵学院正是寻找为骨头碎片的地方。' WHERE entry=8409; /* Text0_0: Are you daft? Did you miss the BONY SKELETAL CREATURES littering the landscape on your way over here?$B$B<Rohan sighs.>$B$BIf you\'re the outdoor type, you\'ll find skeletal creatures all over both the Western and Eastern Plaguelands. Trust me, you can\'t miss \'em - they certainly won\'t miss you if they get the chance.$B$BIf you\'re a dungeon type, Stratholme and Scholomance are definitely the place to be for bone fragments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='今日的安宁地又是个美好且阴郁的一天，你说是吧，$c?$B$B有需要我帮忙的地方吗?',Text0_1_loc4='今日的安宁地又是个美好且阴郁的一天，你说是吧，$c?$B$B有需要我帮忙的地方吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8410; /* Text0_0: Another lovely, gloomy day here in Tranquillien, wouldn\'t you say, $c?$B$BWhat can I do for you? */ /* Text0_1: Another lovely, gloomy day here in Tranquillien, wouldn\'t you say, $c?$B$BWhat can I do for you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有什麽是比翱翔天空更自由的事，$c。有什麽需要我帮忙的吗?' WHERE entry=8411; /* Text0_0: No greater freedom than to soar through the skies, $c. What can I do for you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈罗，朋友。需要什麽吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8412; /* Text0_0: Hello, friend. How may I be of service to you today? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，好问题。$B$B如果你爱在大户外猎战的话，告诉你几个有元素的地方:瘟疫之地、艾萨拉、燃烧平原、费伍德、希利苏斯、冬泉谷，甚至戈洛环形山。$B$B又或者，假如你笑谈悠游於危险之中，我听说厄运之槌那有很多变形元素在墙里。你也可到黑石深渊里，好好找找黑铁矮人使用的元素。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，好问题。$B$B如果你爱在大户外猎战的话，告诉你几个有元素的地方:瘟疫之地、艾萨拉、燃烧平原、费伍德、希利苏斯、冬泉谷，甚至戈洛环形山。$B$B又或者，假如你笑谈悠游於危险之中，我听说厄运之槌那有很多变形元素在墙里。你也可到黑石深渊里，好好找找黑铁矮人使用的元素。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8414; /* Text0_0: Ah, a good question.$B$BIf you prefer hunting in the great outdoors, there are elementals here in the Plaguelands, Azshara, Burning Steppes, Felwood, Silithus, Winterspring, and even Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BIf you are the type that laughs in the face of danger, then perhaps you should visit Dire Maul. I have heard that a great many elemental abberations exist within its walls. You would also do well in seeking out the elementals employed by the Dark Iron dwarves of Blackrock Depths. */ /* Text0_1: Ah, a good question.$B$BIf you prefer hunting in the great outdoors, there are elementals here in the Plaguelands, Azshara, Burning Steppes, Felwood, Silithus, Winterspring, and even Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BIf you are the type that laughs in the face of danger, then perhaps you should visit Dire Maul. I have heard that a great many elemental abberations exist within its walls. You would also do well in seeking out the elementals employed by the Dark Iron dwarves of Blackrock Depths. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是很严肃的问题?你真的不知道?$B$B如果你是懦弱型的深怕脏了手，你可以在燃烧平原与灼热峡谷，找找生物身上的黑铁碎块。$B$B如果你是嗜血如命的冒险型，你到黑石塔和黑石深渊的地城，会发现有数以万计的黑铁碎块等着你。' WHERE entry=8415; /* Text0_0: Is this a serious question? You really don\'t know?$B$BIf you are the cowardly sort, afraid to get their hands too dirty, you will find Dark Iron scraps on the creatures in the Burning Steppes and Searing Gorge.$B$BIf you\'re the bloodthirsty adventuring type, the dungeons of Blackrock Spire and Blackrock Depths hold quite a large supply of the scraps. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你比较有兴趣在户外狩猎的话，那费伍德树人与安戈洛鞭笞者就是你很好的树叶资源。$B$B若你是位更热爱挑战的勇者，厄运之槌的东、西双翼能补给你取之不尽、用之不竭的原始树叶。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你比较有兴趣在户外狩猎的话，那费伍德树人与安戈洛鞭笞者就是你很好的树叶资源。$B$B若你是位更热爱挑战的勇者，厄运之槌的东、西双翼能补给你取之不尽、用之不竭的原始树叶。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8416; /* Text0_0: If you are one that prefers to hunt in the outdoor world, both Felwood\'s treants and Un\'Goro\'s lashers are an excellent source of fronds.$B$BIf you are more of a risk-taker, the eastern and western wings of Dire Maul will provide you with a nearly limitless supply of savage fronds. */ /* Text0_1: If you are one that prefers to hunt in the outdoor world, both Felwood\'s treants and Un\'Goro\'s lashers are an excellent source of fronds.$B$BIf you are more of a risk-taker, the eastern and western wings of Dire Maul will provide you with a nearly limitless supply of savage fronds. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，看看他们对我们可爱的土地做了什麽。天谴军团一定要被消灭!' WHERE entry=8417; /* Text0_0: $C, look what they\'ve done to our beloved land. The Scourge must be destroyed! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这需要费点功夫，不过我相信我们能拯救血精灵的性命。',Text0_1_loc4='这需要费点功夫，不过我相信我们能拯救血精灵的性命。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8418; /* Text0_0: It\'s going to take a bit of work, but I think we can save this blood elf\'s life. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s going to take a bit of work, but I think we can save this blood elf\'s life. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我…不行了…我失败了。' WHERE entry=8419; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  I feel... so... cold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们辛多雷失守了这麽多老家园的土地真是可耻。我们一定能很快恢复元气，然后从天谴军团那夺回属於我们的土地!',Text0_1_loc4='我们辛多雷失守了这麽多老家园的土地真是可耻。我们一定能很快恢复元气，然后从天谴军团那夺回属於我们的土地!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8421; /* Text0_0: It is shameful that we sin\'dorei have lost so much of what we used to call home. It shall not be long before we regain our strength and retake our southern lands back from the Scourge! */ /* Text0_1: It is shameful that we sin\'dorei have lost so much of what we used to call home.  It shall not be long before we regain our strength and retake our southern lands back from the Scourge! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没那时间跟你玩猜谜游戏，$r。说出你的来意，然后消失在我眼前吧!' WHERE entry=8422; /* Text0_0: I\'m far too busy to be playing \'guess the smell\' with you, $r. State your business or get out of my sight! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高阶执行官和阿莉法娜奥丝夫人让我在哪边枯等，但我真的没时间!我朋友正在垂死边缘挣扎啊，$c!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8423; /* Text0_0: The high executor and Dame Auriferous are making me wait, but I don\'t have time for this! My friends are out there dying, $c! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一天多前就派游侠沙里莎往南去了营地，还有游侠莱斯瓦林往西去安宁地!你都没见到他们两个吗?你是被派回来的援军吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我一天多前就派游侠沙里莎往南去了营地，还有游侠莱斯瓦林往西去安宁地!你都没见到他们两个吗?你是被派回来的援军吗?',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8424; /* Text0_0: I sent Ranger Salissa south to the enclave and Ranger Lethvalin west to Tranquillien more than a day ago! Have you seen either of them? Are you the aid that\'s been sent back? */ /* Text0_1: I sent Ranger Salissa south to the enclave and Ranger Lethvalin west to Tranquillien more than a day ago! Have you seen either of them? Are you the aid that\'s been sent back? */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有时候我觉得我好像永远也无法回归到简单正常的生活来效忠阿莉法娜奥丝夫人。我永远也离不开战争。$B$B幸好总是有像你这样的人热切於见到奎尔萨拉斯回到它原来的样貌。摧毁天谴军团，$c!不管你在何方都要摧毁他们!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8425; /* Text0_0: Sometimes it feels like I\'ll never go back to being a simple functionary in service to Dame Auriferous. I\'m not cut out for war.$B$BThankfully there are those like you who burn to see Quel\'Thalas restored to its former beauty. Crush the Scourge, $c! Crush them wherever you can! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，$g英雄:女英雄;来了!好开心再见到你，$N!我相信你仍在消灭看到的天谴军团吧?',Text0_1_loc4='啊，$g英雄:女英雄;来了!好开心再见到你，$N!我相信你仍在消灭看到的天谴军团吧?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8426; /* Text0_0: Ah, here\'s the $g hero : heroine; of the hour now! Good to see you again, $N! I trust that you\'re still destroying the Scourge wherever you find them? */ /* Text0_1: Ah, here\'s the $g hero : heroine; of the hour now! Good to see you again, $N! I trust that you\'re still destroying the Scourge wherever you find them? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我得到消息说你帮助了游侠瓦兰娜和派往塞布索雷的上尉。$B$B感谢你，$c。我想我现在应该回远行者营地了。' WHERE entry=8428; /* Text0_0: I received word that you were able to help Ranger Valanna and the lieutenant at Zeb\'Sora.$B$BThank you, $c. I suppose I should make my way back to Farstrider Enclave now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是什麽风把你吹到这里来，$c?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8429; /* Text0_0: What business brings you here, $c? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你好，$r。如你所见，我还没开始营业。所以，如果你不介意，我要先忙了。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8431; /* Text0_0: Ah, hello there, $r. As you can see, I\'m not open for business quite yet. Now, if you\'ll excuse me, I\'m very busy. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再见到你，$c。不，真的。你是我会在这里赚钱，掌管一切的原因。$B$B那麽，你今天想跟我买些什麽?' WHERE entry=8432; /* Text0_0: Such a delight to see you again, $c. No, really. You\'re the reason that I\'m making money here, hand over fist.$B$BNow, what can I sell to you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到安宁地，$c。很抱歉你发现了这样的状况。如你所见，我们有了些麻烦，不过被遗忘者，和他们的领导者希瓦娜斯·风行者，非常好心的在我们有需要的时候给予我们大量的援助。$B$B如果你能伸出援手请千万不要犹豫。我们在面临无数军力对抗的时候会善用各种能获得的协助。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到安宁地，$c。很抱歉你发现了这样的状况。如你所见，我们有了些麻烦，不过被遗忘者，和他们的领导者希瓦娜斯·风行者，非常好心的在我们有需要的时候给予我们大量的援助。$B$B如果你能伸出援手请千万不要犹豫。我们在面临无数军力对抗的时候会善用各种能获得的协助。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8433; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Tranquillien, $c. I apologize for the state that you find it in. As you can see, we\'ve been having some trouble, but the Forsaken, and their Lady Sylvanas Windrunner, have been gracious enough to lend us a great deal of assistance in our time of need.$B$BIf you can lend a hand please do not hesitate to do so. We can use all of the help that we can get in our struggle against the myriad forces arrayed against us. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Tranquillien, $c. I apologize for the state that you find it in. As you can see, we\'ve been having some trouble, but the Forsaken, and their Lady Sylvanas Windrunner, have been gracious enough to lend us a great deal of assistance in our time of need.$B$BIf you can lend a hand please do not hesitate to do so. We can use all of the help that we can get in our struggle against the myriad forces arrayed against us. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该是部落和联盟注意北裂境和巫妖王入侵的时候了。最近这些日子，整个卡林多和东部王国都遭到攻击。你是否会开始全副武装保护你的土地免於他们的摧毁呢?' WHERE entry=8434; /* Text0_0: The time has come for Horde and Alliance to look towards the north and the invasion of the Scourge. In recent days, territories across Kalimdor and the Eastern Kindgoms have come under attack. Will you take up arms to save your land from destruction at their hands? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='剑而已，不用害怕。要小心羊肉才是真的！' WHERE entry=8435; /* Text0_0: Don\'t be afraid of the sword, nubling. It\'s the mutton that gets ya! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怖的事情是，发生在那些骡身上的事…这次失败，梅兹一定需要我的掩护。' WHERE entry=8438; /* Text0_0: Terrible thing, what happened to them mules... Metz is gonna have my hide for this failure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们了解夜精灵到底在搞什麽鬼是相当重要的，$c!请全心致力於对抗他们直到最后。',Text0_1_loc4='让我们了解夜精灵到底在搞什麽鬼是相当重要的，$c!请全心致力於对抗他们直到最后。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8439; /* Text0_0: It is very important that we find out what the the night elves are up to, $c! Please concentrate all of your efforts toward that end. */ /* Text0_1: It is very important that we find out what the the night elves are up to, $c! Please concentrate all of your efforts toward that end. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对暗夜精灵们采取的行动让我们感到非常高兴。你揭开了他们利用魔网能量线的阴谋，以及他们使用所谓的月亮水晶来监视我们的计划。这些都坚实地巩固了我们在这里的地位。$B$B我们非常感谢你，$n。',Text0_1_loc4='你对暗夜精灵们采取的行动让我们感到非常高兴。你揭开了他们利用魔网能量线的阴谋，以及他们使用所谓的月亮水晶来监视我们的计划。这些都坚实地巩固了我们在这里的地位。$B$B我们非常感谢你，$n。' WHERE entry=8440; /* Text0_0: We are most pleased with your actions against the night elves. When you uncovered their plot to use the ley-line nexi and their so-called moon crystals to spy upon us, you strengthened our position here by an order of magnitude.$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N. */ /* Text0_1: We are most pleased with your actions against the night elves. When you uncovered their plot to use the ley-line nexi and their so-called moon crystals to spy upon us, you strengthened our position here by an order of magnitude.$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是援军吗?夜精灵已被击溃了!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8441; /* Text0_0: Are you the reinforcements? The night elves have been routed! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你将安欧恩的月水晶能源关闭是一件好事，$c!如果你想为我这里的研究提供一点贡献欢迎你随时过来。' WHERE entry=8442; /* Text0_0: Good thing that you deactivated the moon crystal at An\'owyn when you did, $c! Come around any time you feel like pitching in with my research here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这样的情况之下我要怎麽工作?!还有全部这些恶心的被遗忘者!我为安宁地和奎尔萨拉斯悲叹!' WHERE entry=8445; /* Text0_0: How can I work under these conditions?! And all of these disgusting Forsaken around here! I weep for Tranquillien and Quel\'Thalas! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$R，报告!你带了什麽重要的消息来?快点说吧……我和阿莉法娜奥丝夫人正在做策略的商讨。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8447; /* Text0_0: $R, report! What news of significance do you bring? Be quick about your business... Dame Auriferous and I are in the middle of a strategic discussion. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎光临圣光之愿礼拜堂，陌生人。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎光临圣光之愿礼拜堂，陌生人。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8448; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Light\'s Hope Chapel, stranger. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Light\'s Hope Chapel, stranger. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的商队大约一天出队2次，万一天谴军团又去阻止迪笛儿，还有要送往前线的那些骡，那到时我就会被指责。这还是我前所未见最疯狂的事情。但愿我们有英勇的冒险精神能保护这运送过程...' WHERE entry=8452; /* Text0_0: Our caravans go out \'bout twice a day, but I\'ll be damned if the Scourge haven\'t gone out of their way to stop Didier and his mules from getting shipments to the front lines. Craziest thing I\'ve ever seen. If only we had the heroic adventurin\' types to help protect the shipments... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。',Text0_1_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8454; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way. */ /* Text0_1: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
