UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊……我的头快痛死了。$B$B他们一定是派你来救我。他们拖了真够久的!你知道他们对这里的犯人都做了些什麽吗?',Text0_1_loc4='啊……我的头快痛死了。$B$B他们一定是派你来救我。他们拖了真够久的!你知道他们对这里的犯人都做了些什麽吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8460; /* Text0_0: Ahhhhggg... this pain in my head is killing me.$B$BThey must\'ve sent you to rescue me.  Took them long enough!  Do you have any idea of the things they do to prisoners here? */ /* Text0_1: Ahhhhggg... this pain in my head is killing me.$B$BThey must\'ve sent you to rescue me.  Took them long enough!  Do you have any idea of the things they do to prisoners here? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<血精灵毫无生气地躺在桌上。虽然他还有呼吸，但他明显地中了高效的镇静毒素。>' WHERE entry=8461; /* Text0_0: <The blood elf lies limp on the table.  While he\'s still breathing, he appears to have been the victim of potent sedative toxins.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。我是听从高阶执行官的建议来到这里。我有信心只要我们团结一致就能打造一个前所未有的强大部落并消灭所有的天谴军团威胁。' WHERE entry=8462; /* Text0_0: Well met, $r. I am here as a resource of advice for the High Executor to make use of as he will. I am confident that together we can forge the Horde into something that is even stronger than before and turn back the Scourge menace once and for all! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<当恢复药剂开始生效瓦尼司激烈地咳嗽。>$B$B谢谢你救了我。我一定要立刻回到安宁地!' WHERE entry=8463; /* Text0_0: <Varnis coughs violently as the restorative draught takes effect.>$B$BThank you for rescuing me.  I must go back to Tranquillien at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从永歌森林三不五时吹来的风真让我作呕，你懂我的意思吧。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8464; /* Text0_0: The drafts of fresh air that blow from Eversong from time to time really upset my stomach, if you know what I mean. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你要和我说的是很重要的事，$c，或许找阿莉法娜奥丝夫人一起来听会比较妥当。不过我警告你，她很忙碌所以你要等上好一阵子。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你要和我说的是很重要的事，$c，或许找阿莉法娜奥丝夫人一起来听会比较妥当。不过我警告你，她很忙碌所以你要等上好一阵子。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8466; /* Text0_0: If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $c, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait. */ /* Text0_1: If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $c, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='通常我不会允许你直接和我对谈;确切的说，你应该请女士也来听听。不过，我的确是直接给了你一个任务，那麽我们到底需要谈论什麽?',Text0_1_loc4='通常我不会允许你直接和我对谈;确切的说，你应该请女士也来听听。不过，我的确是直接给了你一个任务，那麽我们到底需要谈论什麽?',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8467; /* Text0_0: Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss? */ /* Text0_1: Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss? */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，奥莉菲洛丝夫人向我转达了她对你的欣赏之情。她想告诉你，她希望你能继续作为一个辛多雷的勇士，在幽魂之地奋战。',Text0_1_loc4='$c，奥莉菲洛丝夫人向我转达了她对你的欣赏之情。她想告诉你，她希望你能继续作为一个辛多雷的勇士，在幽魂之地奋战。' WHERE entry=8468; /* Text0_0: $C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands. */ /* Text0_1: $C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这块告示写着许多宣布事项和奖励办法。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8469; /* Text0_0: This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们有重要的工作要做，$N。让我们在敌人的守卫失去警戒时攻击他们。让他们知道辛多雷的复仇从不会遗忘也不会原谅。',Text0_1_loc4='我们有重要的工作要做，$N。让我们在敌人的守卫失去警戒时攻击他们。让他们知道辛多雷的复仇从不会遗忘也不会原谅。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8470; /* Text0_0: We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives. */ /* Text0_1: We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战争浪潮又再度袭来。巫妖王的亡域军队已经从寒冷的北方，包围了我们的土地。他派出了飞行的亡域入侵全世界。' WHERE entry=8471; /* Text0_0: The tides of war have come again. From the cold north, the Lich King\'s necropolises have laid siege to our lands.  He and his cursed general, Kel\'Thuzad, send flying necropolises to invade across the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这真是麻烦!矿坑充满了讨厌的豺狼人，我要怎麽帮博学者收集矿石样本?',Text0_1_loc4='这真是麻烦!矿坑充满了讨厌的豺狼人，我要怎麽帮博学者收集矿石样本?',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8472; /* Text0_0: Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin? */ /* Text0_1: Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin? */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='她会在哪?我满早以前就派我的学徒，莎夏莉雅去西边的光底矿坑了。我们需要把那些矿石样本带回来，要快，否则我们的实验就会失败!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8474; /* Text0_0: Where could she possibly be? I sent my apprentice, Shatharia, to the Underlight Mines to the west quite some time ago. We need those ore samples back, and fast or our experiment is going to fail! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果没有那个光底矿石，这样的情况下，我们的研究一定会失败。$B$B等莎夏莉雅回来这里再说吧。我有一些有趣的任务要交给她，你可以相信我!' WHERE entry=8475; /* Text0_0: Without delivery of the Underlight ore in such a timely fashion, our research would have failed.$B$BJust wait until Shatharia shows her head here again. I\'ve got some interesting tasks for her, you can be sure of it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='辛多雷在过去几年已失去太多。我们的土地，我们的家园，甚至我们自己……$B$B是时候开始把一切夺回来了。',Text0_1_loc4='辛多雷在过去几年已失去太多。我们的土地，我们的家园，甚至我们自己……$B$B是时候开始把一切夺回来了。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8476; /* Text0_0: Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back. */ /* Text0_1: Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们战胜像天谴军团和阿曼尼这些外患之前，一定要先克服内忧。鄙恶者已经惹人厌够久了，是时候消灭他们了。' WHERE entry=8477; /* Text0_0: Before we can overcome external obstacles like the Scourge and the Amani trolls, we must overcome obstacles from within.  The Wretched have been a nuisance for long enough; it is time we vanquished them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以帮我离开这里吗?',Text0_1_loc4='你可以帮我离开这里吗?',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8478; /* Text0_0: Think you could help me to get out of here? */ /* Text0_1: Think you could help me to get out of here? */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在那几张羊皮纸里有核对清单和其他远行者的资料，其中有一张特别抢眼。那是一张丑陋的食人妖素描，可能是你见过最可怕的生物!' WHERE entry=8479; /* Text0_0: Amongst the various pieces of parchment containing checklists and other information from the Farstriders, one stands out. It is a drawing of a hideous troll, perhaps the most fearsome creature that you have ever seen! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='的确，冬泉谷山丘一带正尝试要抵挡重生的天谴军团攻击。你的帮忙对他们来说很重要。$B$B剩余的亡域:$2284W' WHERE entry=8480; /* Text0_0: Indeed, the hills of Winterspring are currently attempting to withstand a renewed Scourge assault. Your assistance would help them greatly.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2284W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方目前暂时脱离天谴军团的威胁了。我担心他们很快又要回来了。' WHERE entry=8481; /* Text0_0: For the time being, that area is free of Scourge influence. I fear it will only be a matter of time before they return. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果援军不能及时赶到燃烧平原，我怕天谴军团会在那里建立指挥基地。如果你可以，就应该赶快到那边协助防卫部队。$B$B剩余的亡域:$2281W' WHERE entry=8484; /* Text0_0: If additional support is not soon sent to the Burning Steppes, I fear the Scourge will establish a base of operations there. If you can, you should go there to aid the defenders.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2281W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='了解我们的敌人能有许多好处。把这件事情牢记在心，$N。$B$B我们对天谴军团了解得越多，我们越能够击败他们。',Text0_1_loc4='了解我们的敌人能有许多好处。把这件事情牢记在心，$N。$B$B我们对天谴军团了解得越多，我们越能够击败他们。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8485; /* Text0_0: Many an advantage can be gained from getting to know your enemy.  Take that lesson to heart, $N.$B$BThe more we learn about the Scourge the better prepared we are to defeat them. */ /* Text0_1: Many an advantage can be gained from getting to know your enemy.  Take that lesson to heart, $N.$B$BThe more we learn about the Scourge the better prepared we are to defeat them. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天谴军团正在攻击地区设置火力点，接收横跨天际的亡域的通讯协助，和其他方面的军援，我们知道，将他们根除的方法就是杀掉所有地面基地的军力。' WHERE entry=8486; /* Text0_0: The Scourge are establishing small staging points in the places under attack, receiving communications and other assistance from the necropolises that fly overhead. From what we can tell, the only way to root them out is by killing the ground forces that surround the points. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎在旅行者营地停留，你想待多久都可以，$c。我们欢迎任何帮助我们在鬼魂之地努力的人。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎在旅行者营地停留，你想待多久都可以，$c。我们欢迎任何帮助我们在鬼魂之地努力的人。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8487; /* Text0_0: You\'re welcome to stay at the Farstrider Enclave for as long as you\'d like, $c.  We welcome any who would aid us in our endeavors in the Ghostlands. */ /* Text0_1: You\'re welcome to stay at the Farstrider Enclave for as long as you\'d like, $c.  We welcome any who would aid us in our endeavors in the Ghostlands. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='流散的秘法力量会对大地，元素，甚至亡者的灵魂做出奇怪的事情。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8488; /* Text0_0: Stray arcane forces can do strange things to the land, the elements and even the spirits of the dead. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高阶执行官是个很忙的人，$c。有什麽事我可以帮你吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8489; /* Text0_0: The High Executor is a very busy man, $c.  Maybe I can help you with whatever you need? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是我们的楷模，$N。在对付光底矿坑的豺狼人和阿曼尼地下墓穴的屍化食人妖之后，你对我们的敌人击出了致命的一击!$B$B$G做得好!:我们应该找个时间好好喝一杯，你觉得怎麽样?;' WHERE entry=8490; /* Text0_0: You\'ve done us exemplary service, $N. Between dealing with the gnolls at the Underlight Mines, and the mummified trolls in the Amani Catacombs, you\'ve dealt a mighty blow to our enemies!$B$B$G Good job! : We should get together for drinks sometime, what do you say?; */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再见到你，$g老兄!:美女!;我们合作愉快;$g下回再见。:我希望我们还有机会合作。;',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8491; /* Text0_0: Good to see you again, $g man! : gorgeous!; We work well together; $g see you around. : I hope we get to continue to do so.; */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人们对你将项链归还给希尔瓦娜斯女王一事议论纷纷。我坚持认为你做了件好事，不要担心女王会对此做何反应。$B$B去做你自己的事好了。' WHERE entry=8492; /* Text0_0: Word got back to me through channels concerning Lady Sylvanas\'s reaction to you and the recovery of her necklace. I still think you did the right thing; don\'t worry too much about how the lady reacted.$B$BNow, state your business. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能说什麽，$c?你是个真正的$g英雄:女英雄;!你不仅个人救了我许多的游侠，还帮助我们对影松食人妖击出致命一击。你确定你不要留下来成为我手下的远行者之一吗?$B$B再见了，$N。' WHERE entry=8493; /* Text0_0: What can I say, $c? You\'re a true $g hero : heroine;! Not only have you personally saved many of my rangers, but you\'ve dealt a decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls. Are you sure that you don\'t want to stay here and be one of my Farstriders?$B$BFare well, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对我们对抗影松食人妖的帮助可说是无法比拟，$c。继续保持我们或许就能将注意力转回来对付天谴军团。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8495; /* Text0_0: Your help with the Shadowpine trolls is proving invaluable, $c. Keep this up and maybe we\'ll be able to turn our attention back to dealing with the Scourge. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你给了影松食人妖重重一击，$N。我只希望我们可以在他们从祖阿曼获得援军前召集我的军队铲除他们。$B$B如果安宁地愿意给我们支援会非常好。' WHERE entry=8496; /* Text0_0: You\'ve dealt the decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls, $N. I only hope that we can muster our forces quickly enough to finish them off before they receive reinforcements from Zul\'Aman.$B$BIt would be nice if Tranquillien were to reinforce us. */
