UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次感谢你补充了我们的治疗水晶。我听说你到处在帮忙人们。保持下去!' WHERE entry=8669; /* Text0_0: Thank you again for replenishing our healing crystals. I hear that you\'re helping out all over the place. Keep up the good work! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你不是为了麦芽酒而来的。我们没有酒可以分享了!$B$B这不是我们的错，没有人有将啤酒带到外域去的远见，只有我们。' WHERE entry=8673; /* Text0_0: I hope yer not here for our ale. We\'re not sharing and that\'s final!$B$BIt\'s not our fault no one had the good sense to bring beer to Outland but us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希望外域并不会像这个区域一样全为贫瘠之地。这和永歌森林的翠绿草地和森林相比简直是天壤之别。',Text0_1_loc4='希望外域并不会像这个区域一样全为贫瘠之地。这和永歌森林的翠绿草地和森林相比简直是天壤之别。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8674; /* Text0_0: Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong. */ /* Text0_1: Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域里存在着比我们以前见过还强大很多的恶魔势力。$B$B强大的力量应该给予那些不会畏惧的人，但能学着驾驭和控制它的力量。' WHERE entry=8675; /* Text0_0: There exist in Outland demonic presences much more powerful than anything we\'d ever seen in the old world.$B$BGreat power shall come to those who do not shy away from it, but learn to harness and master its strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙?',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8678; /* Text0_0: How may I serve? */ /* Text0_1: How may I serve? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域散发着魔法能量，就在那空气中。你能感觉到吗，$N?我想不到比这更适合我们种族的地方了。很快辛多雷就有自己的新土地了!' WHERE entry=8680; /* Text0_0: Outland just oozes with magical energy, it\'s in the very air.  Can you feel it, $N?  I can\'t think of a place better suited to our race.  Soon the sin\'dorei shall have a new land to call our own! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的丈夫失踪好几天了。我们一起去朝圣，本来是要一起结束的。$B$B这样的担心让我比平常更常汲取法力水晶。',Text0_1_loc4='我的丈夫失踪好几天了。我们一起去朝圣，本来是要一起结束的。$B$B这样的担心让我比平常更常汲取法力水晶。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8681; /* Text0_0: My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should. */ /* Text0_1: My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果有适当地照料，龙鹰是相当温驯的。你不觉得这很棒吗?如果好好抚养它们是如此的友善好相处，如果在野外生长又是如此的凶恶致命……我真是爱死它们了。',Text0_1_loc4='如果有适当地照料，龙鹰是相当温驯的。你不觉得这很棒吗?如果好好抚养它们是如此的友善好相处，如果在野外生长又是如此的凶恶致命……我真是爱死它们了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8682; /* Text0_0: Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much. */ /* Text0_1: Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别...担心...我...' WHERE entry=8683; /* Text0_0: Don\'t... worry... about me... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不真的认为我们的情况有那麽糟。我确定一切会很快好转，太阳之井的能量会恢复。它就是不可能像大家说的那样糟。',Text0_1_loc4='我不真的认为我们的情况有那麽糟。我确定一切会很快好转，太阳之井的能量会恢复。它就是不可能像大家说的那样糟。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8684; /* Text0_0: I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be. */ /* Text0_1: I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='和逐日者交朋友各有各的好处;我用只能在外域找到的实验品来进行研究，而他们则获得...我迷人的个性和粗犷的帅脸蛋。' WHERE entry=8685; /* Text0_0: Befriending the Sunstriders has paid off; I get to conduct research with subjects I can only find in Outland and they get... my charming personality and rugged good looks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我父亲被派来这片荒地时我只是个婴儿。所有我知道关於他的事都是别人告诉我的。$B$B你的梦会变吗，$N?我的不会。我只有一个梦:一条赤红的军团地平线包围着我，数量庞大无法计算，在远处作战。我在一个人的躯体前跪下，他大概就是我的父亲，然后哭泣。当他喘着气时，他的身体整个被压碎，他虚弱的说着一些话。尽管我再怎麽努力;还是听不到他要和我说的话。' WHERE entry=8688; /* Text0_0: I was only an infant when my father was deployed to this wasteland. All that I have ever known of him is what others have told me.$B$BDo your dreams change, $N? Mine do not. I have one dream: A crimson skyline envelops me as Legion, numbering beyond comprehension, battle in the distance. I kneel before the body of a man, presumably my father, and weep. As he is gasping for air, his body wholly crushed, he whispers something. Despite every effort, I am unable to hear what he is trying to tell me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为我对这个小人太残忍了吗?$B$B他们这个月已经杀了我手下两个人!我们对这些鄙恶人渣太仁慈了。' WHERE entry=8698; /* Text0_0: You think I\'m being cruel to this worm?$B$BThey\'ve killed two of my men this month!  We\'re too kind to this Wretched scum. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到晴风村。银月城已经败在我们手下了，但我们拒绝离开。这里是我们的家。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到晴风村。银月城已经败在我们手下了，但我们拒绝离开。这里是我们的家。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8699; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Fairbreeze Village. Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave. This is our home. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Fairbreeze Village.  Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave.  This is our home. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的工作包含一个任务也只是唯一的任务:确定西部圣所正常运作。$B$B你要原谅我脾气这麽差但是，如你所见，这里的状况已经有点失控了。',Text0_1_loc4='我的工作包含一个任务也只是唯一的任务:确定西部圣所正常运作。$B$B你要原谅我脾气这麽差但是，如你所见，这里的状况已经有点失控了。',Text1_0_loc4='我的工作包含一个任务也只是唯一的任务:确定西部圣所正常运作。

你要原谅我脾气这麽差但是，如你所见，这里的状况已经有点失控了。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8700; /* Text0_0: My job consists of one task and one task only: ensuring that the West Sanctum runs smoothly.$B$BYou\'ll have to excuse my temper but, as you can see, the situation here is a bit out of hand. */ /* Text0_1: My job consists of one task and one task only: ensuring that the West Sanctum runs smoothly.$B$BYou\'ll have to excuse my temper but, as you can see, the situation here is a bit out of hand. */ /* Text1_0: Could night elf saboteurs be behind this? I doubt it. With the load we\'ve been putting on the West Sanctum it was only a matter of time until something went wrong. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='双子帝王被杀之后，神庙里的魔法防护阻碍传送就大幅衰弱。如果你想的话，我可以将你传送至帝王的巢穴。',Text0_1_loc4='双子帝王被杀之后，神庙里的魔法防护阻碍传送就大幅衰弱。如果你想的话，我可以将你传送至帝王的巢穴。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8701; /* Text0_0: With the Emperors slain, the magical protection blocking teleportation within the temple has been greatly weakened. If you desire, I am able to translocate you to the Emperors\' lair. */ /* Text0_1: With the Emperors slain, the magical protection blocking teleportation within the temple has been greatly weakened. If you desire, I am able to translocate you to the Emperors\' lair. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥罗被杀后通往最后房间的路就显而易见了。如果你想的话，我可以将你传送至那里。',Text0_1_loc4='奥罗被杀后通往最后房间的路就显而易见了。如果你想的话，我可以将你传送至那里。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8702; /* Text0_0: With Ouro slain the way is clear to the final chamber. I am able to transport you there, if you desire. */ /* Text0_1: With Ouro slain the way is clear to the final chamber. I am able to transport you there, if you desire. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喜欢这个节庆吗，$c?$B$B虽说火焰管理者偏向当前的火焰，但我也不只是个只熟悉节庆过去的历史学家而已。当然，我也记录今年的节庆活动。目前一切进展的很顺利，你不觉得吗?$B$B你知道的，$n，在节日中持续燃烧的节庆火焰中潜藏着力量。我们看顾着我们的火焰，但我确信在我们敌人的城市深处有着神圣的火焰在燃烧着...',Text0_1_loc4='喜欢这个节庆吗，$c?$B$B虽说火焰管理者偏向当前的火焰，但我也不只是个只熟悉节庆过去的历史学家而已。当然，我也记录今年的节庆活动。目前一切进展的很顺利，你不觉得吗?$B$B你知道的，$n，在节日中持续燃烧的节庆火焰中潜藏着力量。我们看顾着我们的火焰，但我确信在我们敌人的城市深处有着神圣的火焰在燃烧着...',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8703; /* Text0_0: Enjoying the festival, $c?$b$bWhile the Flame Wardens tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$b$bYou know, $n, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities... */ /* Text0_1: Enjoying the festival, $c?$b$bWhile the Flame Wardens tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$b$bYou know, $n, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你在找工作，$C，拿起一个工具开始挖吧。这里所见都是废墟!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8712; /* Text0_0: If you\'re looking for work, $c, grab yourself a pick and get to digging. There\'re ruins out there as far as the eye can see! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$N。我亲爱的洛萨之子，我困在这个悲惨的世界已经接近二十年了。我们尽力做到最好，但我们过去失败的阴影威胁今日依旧令人感到震惊。$B$B或许你愿意帮助我们改正它?',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$N。我亲爱的洛萨之子，我困在这个悲惨的世界已经接近二十年了。我们尽力做到最好，但我们过去失败的阴影威胁今日依旧令人感到震惊。$B$B或许你愿意帮助我们改正它?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8713; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $N. My fellow Sons of Lothar and I have been stuck on this miserable world for close to twenty years now. We held on as best we could, but it still amazes me that the threats we face today are just the shadows of our past failures.$B$BPerhaps you will help us atone for them?  $B */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $N. My fellow Sons of Lothar and I have been stuck on this miserable world for close to twenty years now. We held on as best we could, but it still amazes me that the threats we face today are just the shadows of our past failures.$B$BPerhaps you will help us atone for them?  $B */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域的腐败程度真的相当惊人，$c。塞纳里奥议会想了解这土地的生物如何在这麽艰难的环境下生存。研究这块破碎，受尽折磨的土地和它的居民，或许能教我们如何治疗这生病的世界。',Text0_1_loc4='外域的腐败程度真的相当惊人，$c。塞纳里奥议会想了解这土地的生物如何在这麽艰难的环境下生存。研究这块破碎，受尽折磨的土地和它的居民，或许能教我们如何治疗这生病的世界。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8715; /* Text0_0: The extent of the corruption in Outland is truly astonishing, $c. The Cenarion Circle hopes to understand how these creatures have managed to survive. Studying this broken, tortured land and its inhabitants may yet teach us how to heal ailing parts of our own world. */ /* Text0_1: The extent of the corruption in Outland is truly astonishing, $c. The Cenarion Circle hopes to understand how these creatures have managed to survive. Studying this broken, tortured land and its inhabitants may yet teach us how to heal ailing parts of our own world. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域的腐败程度真的相当惊人，$c。塞纳里奥远征队想了解这土地的生物如何在这麽艰难的环境下生存。研究这块破碎，受尽折磨的土地和它的居民，或许能教我们如何治疗这生病的世界。' WHERE entry=8716; /* Text0_0: It is sad to see what has happened to this land.  The Cenarion Expedition will do what it can to understand and heal the damage that has been done. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来若有所失，$c。不要逼我让你和那些苦工一样到墙上去工作。' WHERE entry=8717; /* Text0_0: You look lost, $c. Don\'t make me put you to work on the walls with the other peons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。你在这时候到达索尔玛是最好的时机了。大酋长需要我们，因为他不能独自在这里。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。你在这时候到达索尔玛是最好的时机了。大酋长需要我们，因为他不能独自在这里。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8718; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c. Your arrival in Thrallmar could not have occurred at a better time. The warchief is depending on us, since he cannot be here himself. */ /* Text0_1: Well met, $c. Your arrival in Thrallmar could not have occurred at a better time. The warchief is depending on us, since he cannot be here himself. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='索尔玛需要你，$c。大酋长需要你。准备好履行你的职责。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8719; /* Text0_0: Thrallmar needs you, $c. The warchief needs you. Stand ready to do your duty. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠着蛮力赢了几场比赛。那很奸诈，最后靠着你在武器上的本能反应和知识获得胜利。',Text0_1_loc4='靠着蛮力赢了几场比赛。那很奸诈，最后靠着你在武器上的本能反应和知识获得胜利。' WHERE entry=8724; /* Text0_0: Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end. */ /* Text0_1: Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='另一个英雄?命运今天对我们微笑，$N。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8733; /* Text0_0: Another hero? The fates smile upon us on this day, $N. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说过你的一些功绩，$N。我知道当你在这被遗忘者的土地时你会带着尊严行动，像个辛多雷真正的英雄。' WHERE entry=8740; /* Text0_0: I\'ve heard something of your exploits, $N.  I know that while you\'re here in Forsaken lands that you\'ll comport yourself with dignity and as a true hero of the sin\'dorei! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我向你表示欢迎之意，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='我向你表示欢迎之意，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8750; /* Text0_0: I bid you welcome, $c. */ /* Text0_1: I bid you welcome, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没时间闲聊，$c。我一定要照料那些朝圣者确保他们为前方漫长的旅途做好准备。' WHERE entry=8751; /* Text0_0: I haven\'t time for idle chatter, $c. I must see to the pilgrims and ensure they are prepared for the long journey ahead. */
