UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我们教导联盟其他种族的人，我们有很多要和他们多学习的地方。保持你的眼睛、耳朵和你的心处於学习状态，$c。' WHERE entry=8799; /* Text0_0: While we have much to teach the other races of the Alliance, we have as much to learn from them.  Keep your eyes, ears and mind open, $c. */
