UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探奸笑。>$B$B别担心，新成员，还有更多传送门控制器和更多适合的传送地点。我相信赛罗娜斯很快就会有一个新的入口了。这些蓝皮肤的狗在这世界活不久了。赛罗娜斯和憎恨会把太阳之鹰军队留下的所有事物都清理的一乾二净。',Text0_1_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探奸笑。>$B$B别担心，新成员，还有更多传送门控制器和更多适合的传送地点。我相信赛罗娜斯很快就会有一个新的入口了。这些蓝皮肤的狗在这世界活不久了。赛罗娜斯和憎恨会把太阳之鹰军队留下的所有事物都清理的一乾二净。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9137; /* Text0_0: <The captured Sunhawk agent smirks.>$B$BDon\'t worry, new blood, there are many more portal controllers and many more suitable locations for portals. I am certain that Sironas will have a new gate up very soon. These blue skinned dogs are not long for this world. Sironas and the abomination will clean up whatever the Sunhawk forces leave behind. */ /* Text0_1: <The captured Sunhawk agent smirks.>$B$BDon\'t worry, new blood, there are many more portal controllers and many more suitable locations for portals. I am certain that Sironas will have a new gate up very soon. These blue skinned dogs are not long for this world. Sironas and the abomination will clean up whatever the Sunhawk forces leave behind. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
