UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很多?它有两个弱点:那栋建筑物西边和东边的底部。嘿，等等。你怎麽会知道旋绕导航器的事?你不是说你在成形之前都被俘虏了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='很多?它有两个弱点:那栋建筑物西边和东边的底部。嘿，等等。你怎麽会知道旋绕导航器的事?你不是说你在成形之前都被俘虏了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9141; /* Text0_0: Numerous? It has two weak points: The base of the structure on the west side and the base of the structure on the east side. Hey, wait a minute. How would you know anything about the Vector Coil? Didn\'t you say that you were captured before you even materialized? */ /* Text0_1: Numerous? It has two weak points: The base of the structure on the west side and the base of the structure on the east side. Hey, wait a minute. How would you know anything about the Vector Coil? Didn\'t you say that you were captured before you even materialized? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
