UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<奥翠司转头面向你并微笑。>$B$B我不这麽认为。$B$B<奥翠司指着他的骏马，尼轩德玛斯。>$B$B不管他们正在建造什麽东西，我们一定要在这些炼冶场完成之前阻止他们。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9423; /* Text0_0: <Altruis turns to face you and smiles.>$B$BI do not.$B$B<Altruis points to his steed, Nethrandamus.>$B$BWe must stop them before these forge camps are able to complete whatever it is that they are building. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那就是这些把风景弄的乱七八糟的结构。军团雇用了莫阿格和甘纳格在这些活动炼冶场建造大规模毁灭性武器。我们不用知道他们到底想在纳葛兰这里建造些什麽!$B$B你们就是我的眼睛。你们的武器就是我的狂怒。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9424; /* Text0_0: That is what these structures that litter the landscape are called. The Legion have employed the mo\'arg and gan\'arg to build weapons of mass destruction at these mobile forge camps. Let us not find out what it is that they intend to build here in Nagrand!$B$BYou will be my eyes. Your weapons will be my fury. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
