UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你禁不住吧，你可以吗?想要更好，更强大，更快吗?这些护身符中的每一个都保证可做到我所说的。走向前并且买一个这些奇迹般的小玩意!以两倍便宜的价格买到喔!' WHERE entry=9755; /* Text0_0: Ahh, ya couldn\'t resist, could ya? Want to be better, stronger, faster? Each one of these amulets be guaranteed to do just what I say they be doin\'. Step up and buy one of these miraculous baubles! Cheap at twice the price! */
