UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你被军团抓到，告诉他们「(恶魔语)沙尔·伊欧·罗马斯·达·泰斯比。」他们将因为你侮辱他们的神而立刻杀死你，让你免於遭受惨忍的拷问或更惨的事...' WHERE entry=9771; /* Text0_0: If you\'re ever captured by the Legion, tell them "Xar il romath da tidesbi." They will kill you instantly for insulting their god, saving you intolerable torture or worse... */
