UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你曾到过赞格沼泽，你可能遇到一个名叫丹尼尔的人。你知道的 -- 戴一顶奇怪的盔帽，只会回答「专家」的人。$B$B当然，他知道的一切都是我教的。$B$B不要让这身华丽的衣服欺骗了你。我内心里仍然是一名盗贼。丹尼尔和我一同在战壕中度过许多时光，但是在我退休之前。据我所知，他仍然在外头，教训敌人。' WHERE entry=10031; /* Text0_0: If you\'ve been to Zangarmarsh, you might\'ve run into a fellow named Daniels. You know -- wears a strange helmet, only answers to "the Specialist."$B$BOf course, I taught him everything he knows.$B$BDon\'t let the fine clothing fool you. I\'m still a rogue at heart. Daniels and I spent a lot of time in the trenches together, but that was before I retired. As far as I know, he\'s still out there, giving \'em hell. */
