UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='幽暗城的皇家药剂师学会积极要援助我们在外域的兽人盟友。这是一个强化我们的团结性以及发现可以进行研究的新种类及混合物的机会。$B$B混合物...比如说毒药。',Text0_1_loc4='幽暗城的皇家药剂师学会积极要援助我们在外域的兽人盟友。这是一个强化我们的团结性以及发现可以进行研究的新种类及混合物的机会。$B$B混合物...比如说毒药。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10293; /* Text0_0: The Royal Apothecary Society of the Undercity is eager to aid our orc allies here, in Outland.  It is an opportunity to strengthen our bonds, and to find new specimens and compounds for study.$B$BCompounds...such as poisons. */ /* Text0_1: The Royal Apothecary Society of the Undercity is eager to aid our orc allies here, in Outland.  It is an opportunity to strengthen our bonds, and to find new specimens and compounds for study.$B$BCompounds...such as poisons. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='白沙岗哨对我来说就像是个意外的一站，温和的放下它。我的客户正指望我运送达我的货品，我开始怀疑我是否可以在所有的耽搁下把东西即时送达。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10299; /* Text0_0: Whitereach Post is something of an unintended stop for me, to put it mildly. My clients are counting on me to deliver my wares and I\'m starting to wonder if I\'m going to make it in time with all the delays involved. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
