UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='远行者旅店坐落在长者步道与集市之间，两边都能进去。',Text0_1_loc4='远行者旅店坐落在长者步道与集市之间，两边都能进去。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10727; /* Text0_0: The Wayfarer\'s Rest tavern is located between the Walk of Elders and the Bazaar. You can reach it from either location. */ /* Text0_1: The Wayfarer\'s Rest tavern is located between the Walk of Elders and the Bazaar. You can reach it from either location. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域的战争比我之前所经历过的任何战争都要惨烈。大部分受害者都是那些留在后方的孩子。$B$B现在，斯克提斯的鸦人对沙塔斯城的威胁进一步加剧，那里会有更多的孤儿需要照顾。这些孩子几乎已经看不到光明的未来。$B$B但是，你却有能力为他们做些什么。儿童周来了，$c，我恳求你给这些孩子的生活带来些乐趣和奇迹吧。',Text0_1_loc4='外域的战争比我之前所经历过的任何战争都要惨烈。大部分受害者都是那些留在后方的孩子。$B$B现在，斯克提斯的鸦人对沙塔斯城的威胁进一步加剧，那里会有更多的孤儿需要照顾。这些孩子几乎已经看不到光明的未来。$B$B但是，你却有能力为他们做些什么。儿童周来了，$c，我恳求你给这些孩子的生活带来些乐趣和奇迹吧。' WHERE entry=10729; /* Text0_0: The conflicts in Outland are deadlier than any I have seen.  And their most tragic victims are the children that are left behind.$B$BNow, with the threat against Shattrath from the arakkoa of Skettis, there will be even more orphans to take care of.  These children often live without the hope of a bright future.$B$BBut you have the power to do something about that.  It\'s Children\'s Week, $c, and I implore you to volunteer to bring joy and wonder into a child\'s life. */ /* Text0_1: The conflicts in Outland are deadlier than any I have seen.  And their most tragic victims are the children that are left behind.$B$BNow, with the threat against Shattrath from the arakkoa of Skettis, there will be even more orphans to take care of.  These children often live without the hope of a bright future.$B$BBut you have the power to do something about that.  It\'s Children\'s Week, $c, and I implore you to volunteer to bring joy and wonder into a child\'s life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很寂寞。我希望在这里有更多的和我同龄的孩子。有时候，我真的很怀念在沙塔斯城孤儿院的日子。' WHERE entry=10730; /* Text0_0: I\'m lonely.  I wish that there were more kids my age around here.  Sometimes I miss being at the orphanage in Shattrath City. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='还没到吗？',Text0_1_loc4='还没到吗？',Text1_0_loc4='到了吗?',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10732; /* Text0_0: Are we there yet? */ /* Text0_1: Are we there yet? */ /* Text1_0: If the demons fell, where did they fall from? */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我觉得我需要洗个澡。*嗅* 我想你也要洗个澡！',Text2_1_loc4='欢迎来到我们的酒店!',Text3_0_loc4='一个牛头人圣骑士会是一头圣牛吗？',Text3_1_loc4='我的主人普拉格·史帕齐林是个不错的老板，而且他赚了很多钱。他的钱包都快要被撑破了!' WHERE entry=10732; /* Text2_0: I think I need a bath.  *sniff*  I think you need one, too! */ /* Text2_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text2: */ /* Text3_0: Would a tauren paladin be a holy cow? */ /* Text3_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text3: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我穿这条裙子是不是看起来比较胖？',Text4_1_loc4='嘘……你闻到什么东西?',Text5_0_loc4='我敢打赌伊利丹其实是个好人，他只是需要母爱。',Text5_1_loc4='我听说你已经死啦……嗯，以后你想要装死的话就不那么容易啦！' WHERE entry=10732; /* Text4_0: Does this dress make me look fat? */ /* Text4_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text4: */ /* Text5_0: I bet Illidan is a nice guy underneath.  He just needs a mama, too. */ /* Text5_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text5: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我敢打赌要是冰淇淋打过孔的话味道肯定会更好！',Text6_1_loc4='老国王死了吗？那不可能！',Text7_0_loc4='男孩有虱子女孩有美貌！',Text7_1_loc4='国王陛下，我可没有给你带来什么麻烦。' WHERE entry=10732; /* Text6_0: I bet ice cream would taste better if it were socketed! */ /* Text6_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text6: */ /* Text7_0: Boys have cooties and girls have beauty! */ /* Text7_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text7: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我自由了!可是那件秘密…危险了。必须警告阿卡玛!',Text0_1_loc4='我自由了!可是那件秘密…危险了。必须警告阿卡玛!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10733; /* Text0_0: I am free!  But the secret... is now in peril.  Akama must be warned! */ /* Text0_1: I am free!  But the secret... is now in peril.  Akama must be warned! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
