UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='关於这个...人，已经有一些抱怨出现了。我听说他在从事见不得人的勾当。我是到此来判定他的这档生意是否合法...并於可证明其他事物时提出诉讼。',Text0_1_loc4='关於这个...人，已经有一些抱怨出现了。我听说他在从事见不得人的勾当。我是到此来判定他的这档生意是否合法...并於可证明其他事物时提出诉讼。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10830; /* Text0_0: There have been some complaints filed about this... individual. I\'m told he\'s something of a shady character. I am here to determine whether or not this business of his is legitimate... and take action if it proves otherwise. */ /* Text0_1: There have been some complaints filed about this... individual. I\'m told he\'s something of a shady character. I am here to determine whether or not this business of his is legitimate... and take action if it proves otherwise. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你设法集满了全套的风暴套卡你就会得到愤怒之高级暗月卡片。这将会增加你法术或物理攻击的致命一击机率直到击杀为止。' WHERE entry=10831; /* Text0_0: If you manage to complete a deck of Storms cards you will be rewarded with a Greater Darkmoon card of Wrath.   This will increase your chance to get a critical hit with spells or physical attacks until you achieve one. */
