UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='记得你一天只能选一样收集工作来做。除那之外，我们一直都在寻找更多的水晶。任何没用的苦工都能将那些水晶带回到营地。' WHERE entry=10863; /* Text0_0: Just remember that you can only pick one gathering job to do per day. Aside from that, we\'re always looking for more crystals. Any worthless peon can bring those back to the base camp. */
