UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我感觉你为我的盟友杀出一条生路。我与他们及神庙的感应仍然很强烈。你想要再往深处搜索吗?' WHERE entry=11081; /* Text0_0: I sense you\'ve cleared the path to my brethren.  My connection to them and to the temple is still strong.  Do you wish to delve deeper inside? */
