UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔，你说我是个厨师?我想你说的没错。酒吧女服务员总是偶尔要在厨房里干活，而多年来我已经学会了一些食谱。虽然不是什麽特别的菜肴，但是可以丰盛地满足葛罗克的大胃口。',Text0_1_loc4='喔，你说我是个厨师?我想你说的没错。酒吧女服务员总是偶尔要在厨房里干活，而多年来我已经学会了一些食谱。虽然不是什麽特别的菜肴，但是可以丰盛地满足葛罗克的大胃口。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=11231; /* Text0_0: Oh, me a cook?  I suppose that\'s true.  A barmaid\'s got to work in the kitchens from time to time, and I\'ve learned a few recipes over the years.  Nothing too special, but they\'re hearty enough to fill Grok\'s substantial belly. */ /* Text0_1: Oh, me a cook?  I suppose that\'s true.  A barmaid\'s got to work in the kitchens from time to time, and I\'ve learned a few recipes over the years.  Nothing too special, but they\'re hearty enough to fill Grok\'s substantial belly. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，$N。你已经学会了我所有的烹饪技巧。当然你永远不知道我们的厨艺什麽时候会研发出新的食谱，所以别害羞，有空的时候尽管回来找我。',Text0_1_loc4='很抱歉，$N。你已经学会了我所有的烹饪技巧。当然你永远不知道我们的厨艺什麽时候会研发出新的食谱，所以别害羞，有空的时候尽管回来找我。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=11233; /* Text0_0: I\'m sorry $N, but you\'ve already learned all I know about cooking.  Of course, you never know when our cooks will whip up something new, so don\'t be shy and be sure to visit again some time. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m sorry $N, but you\'ve already learned all I know about cooking.  Of course, you never know when our cooks will whip up something new, so don\'t be shy and be sure to visit again some time. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的兄弟克里克斯克觉得他在奥格玛的工作不好。没有比这个地方更臭了。至少老板知情理付我安全费用!$B$B什麽?你想看看飞艇在哪了?我这有好东西飞艇追踪器!',Text0_1_loc4='我的兄弟克里克斯克觉得他在奥格玛的工作不好。没有比这个地方更臭了。至少老板知情理付我安全费用!$B$B什麽?你想看看飞艇在哪了?我这有好东西飞艇追踪器!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=11234; /* Text0_0: My brother Krixx thinks he has it bad working in Orgrimmar. Nothing compares to the stench of this place. At least the boss had the decency to give me hazard pay!$B$BWhat? Do you want to see where the zeppelin is? Good thing I\'ve got my zeppelin tracker right here! */ /* Text0_1: My brother Krixx thinks he has it bad working in Orgrimmar. Nothing compares to the stench of this place. At least the boss had the decency to give me hazard pay!$B$BWhat? Do you want to see where the zeppelin is? Good thing I\'ve got my zeppelin tracker right here! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
