UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='「如果你得到了够多的啤酒节奖品券，位於啤酒营地后面的贝尔碧·迅移可以给你一个『名誉酒友』的手盖戳。$B$B那个戳印将可让我卖给你一匹啤酒节骑乘用山羊。不过提醒你，它们可不便宜啊!」',Text0_1_loc4='「如果你得到了够多的啤酒节奖品券，位於啤酒营地后面的贝尔碧·迅移可以给你一个『名誉酒友』的手盖戳。$B$B那个戳印将可让我卖给你一匹啤酒节骑乘用山羊。不过提醒你，它们可不便宜啊!」',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12092; /* Text0_0: If you earn enough Brewfest prize tickets, the ticket redeemer in the Brewfest camp can give you an "Honorary Brewer" hand stamp.$b$bThat stamp will allow me to sell you a Brewfest riding ram. But they don\'t come cheap, mind you! */ /* Text0_1: If you earn enough Brewfest prize tickets, the ticket redeemer in the Brewfest camp can give you an "Honorary Brewer" hand stamp.$b$bThat stamp will allow me to sell you a Brewfest riding ram. But they don\'t come cheap, mind you! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿朋友，我手上的东西是个大发现，从来没有见过这样的东西喔!现在正出售中，便宜的呢!$B$B瞧，我已经懒得在酒馆中花钱寻找完美的人。所以我做了这些护目镜，而现在每个人看起来都超完美的。我是指你就不会搞错那些自大的傻小子啦!$B$B那麽，你想要试试看这些东西，帮我的荷包赚点钱吗?因为你看起来这麽棒，我还会给你折扣喔!',Text0_1_loc4='嘿朋友，我手上的东西是个大发现，从来没有见过这样的东西喔!现在正出售中，便宜的呢!$B$B瞧，我已经懒得在酒馆中花钱寻找完美的人。所以我做了这些护目镜，而现在每个人看起来都超完美的。我是指你就不会搞错那些自大的傻小子啦!$B$B那麽，你想要试试看这些东西，帮我的荷包赚点钱吗?因为你看起来这麽棒，我还会给你折扣喔!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12098; /* Text0_0: Hey friend, what I\'ve got here is a breakthrough, the likes of which have never been seen!  And it\'s for sale, for cheap!$b$bYou see, I got tired of spending money in taverns looking for the perfect person.  So I made these goggles and now EVERYONE looks like pure perfection.  I mean you CAN\'T go wrong with these puppies!$b$bSo, you wanna try these out, help pad my pockets a bit?  Since you look soo good, I\'ll even give you a discount! */ /* Text0_1: Hey friend, what I\'ve got here is a breakthrough, the likes of which have never been seen!  And it\'s for sale, for cheap!$b$bYou see, I got tired of spending money in taverns looking for the perfect person.  So I made these goggles and now EVERYONE looks like pure perfection.  I mean you CAN\'T go wrong with these puppies!$b$bSo, you wanna try these out, help pad my pockets a bit?  Since you look soo good, I\'ll even give you a discount! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看着你走过并希望你会停下来。那麽甜心，我可以帮你什麽呢?' WHERE entry=12100; /* Text0_0: I saw you across the way and was hoping you were going to stop by.  So what can I do for you sweetie? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='正常的狗根本不敢靠近我。当我发现这点时深受打击……我其实是很喜欢动物的。$B$B天灾犬是不错的替代品。当然，它们的模样……并不好看。但你知道吗，我的相貌也好看不到哪儿去！' WHERE entry=12103; /* Text0_0: Normal dogs won\'t come anywhere near me nowadays.  I was devastated when I found out... I used to love the beasts.$B$BPlaguehounds make for a fine substitute, however.  They\'re not quite as... easy on the eyes.  But then again, neither am I! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在艾泽拉斯找不到更好的啤酒啦。' WHERE entry=12104; /* Text0_0: You won\'t find a better brew in Azeroth. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老兄，你想试试诸国最棒的啤酒吗?' WHERE entry=12105; /* Text0_0: Hey mon, you ready to try da best brew in all da realms? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里是练习灭火技术的地方，为了被遗忘者！',Text0_1_loc4='这里是练习灭火技术的地方，为了被遗忘者！' WHERE entry=12108; /* Text0_0: Here we practice fire fighting techniques.  Power to the Forsaken! */ /* Text0_1: Here we practice fire fighting techniques.  Power to the Forsaken! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='发生在这里及剃刀岭之间的爆炸将我们的啤酒配送机制搞得一团乱!黑铁矮人好像大约一个小时会来攻击一次!$B$B所以如果你想帮忙的话，这有解决方法。我会借你一些缰绳以及一头我的山羊。$B$B每次你带给我一桶酒桶，我就会给你一些奖品章。你每带一桶酒桶给我，我还会让你使用这只山羊的时间延长一点!$B$B不过，一旦你开始了，到明天之前你都不能再进行一次。$B$B你确定你准备好要开始了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='发生在这里及剃刀岭之间的爆炸将我们的啤酒配送机制搞得一团乱!黑铁矮人好像大约一个小时会来攻击一次!$B$B所以如果你想帮忙的话，这有解决方法。我会借你一些缰绳以及一头我的山羊。$B$B每次你带给我一桶酒桶，我就会给你一些奖品章。你每带一桶酒桶给我，我还会让你使用这只山羊的时间延长一点!$B$B不过，一旦你开始了，到明天之前你都不能再进行一次。$B$B你确定你准备好要开始了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12113; /* Text0_0: That crash between here and Razor Hill really messed up the brew flow!  It doesn\'t help that Dark Iron dwarves seem to be attacking every hour or so!$b$bSo if you want to help, here\'s the deal.  I\'ll let you borrow some reins and one of my rams.$b$bEvery time you bring me a keg, I\'ll give you some tokens.  I\'ll even let you use the ram for a bit longer for every keg you bring me!$b$bBUT, once you start this, you won\'t be able to do it again until tomorrow.$b$bAre you sure you\'re ready to do this? */ /* Text0_1: That crash between here and Razor Hill really messed up the brew flow!  It doesn\'t help that Dark Iron dwarves seem to be attacking every hour or so!$b$bSo if you want to help, here\'s the deal.  I\'ll let you borrow some reins and one of my rams.$b$bEvery time you bring me a keg, I\'ll give you some tokens.  I\'ll even let you use the ram for a bit longer for every keg you bring me!$b$bBUT, once you start this, you won\'t be able to do it again until tomorrow.$b$bAre you sure you\'re ready to do this? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看到你在欣赏我们合法取得的竞速山羊…我看得出来你想要感受山羊竞速的快感…但在你能够骑上山羊并且竞速之前，你得先工作。$B$B没错，工作跟竞速对这些山羊来说是一样的。' WHERE entry=12114; /* Text0_0: I see you checking out our legally obtained racing rams...  I can see you want in on the ram racing sensation...  But before you can play, you gotta work.$b$bWell, work and play are pretty much the same when it comes to these rams. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喂，你！干嘛呢，勤快点！$B$B没看到这里人人都忙着么，你这个饭桶！',Text1_0_loc4='朋友，瞧你那副得意忘形的模样！你是不是从哪个富商那儿抢到什么好东西了？财富是要大家分享的……朋友，别小气嘛！' WHERE entry=12120; /* Text0_0: Ahoy, mon!  What be happenin\', ye salty \'at steppa!$B$BDis place be all chacka-chacka, ye scallywag! */ /* Text1_0: Lookin\' mighty cris, me bucko!  Ye pillage a fat sutler?  Best ye spread da wealth... don\'t be a craven choke puppy, mon! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='瞧那边！那蠢货把农夫给惹火了。这下麻烦了吧，我看他的小命难保啦。',Text3_0_loc4='朋友，我说的是实话！北海海盗是世界上最强硬的海盗。$B$B你最好不要惹事。算啦！反正所有的白痴海盗都会被处死！' WHERE entry=12120; /* Text2_0: Ku ovah yonder, matey!  Dat scurvy bobo be all up inne quashie\'s face.  Dat hard-eared swab gonnna get salt, mon... gonna get keelhauled and gonna be made into a duppy, mon. */ /* Text3_0: Issa truut, matey!  Neh tougher salts anyweh but da northsea freebootahs yahso, mon!$B$BBest not brindle s\'mady, mon.  Scuppah dat!  \'Alf eediat swabs get feh kiss da gunnah\'s dawta, mate! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，你这样就很无耻了。你是想惹我发火是吧？滚，你这个懦弱的海盗。明天再见！' WHERE entry=12121; /* Text0_0: Now ye just be fass and facety, mon!  Ye fixin\' fe vex me, ye maga dog blaggard?$B$BG\'waan den, ye lily-livered scallywag.  Be seen ya first light! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<老冰鳞警惕地盯着你，他漫不经心地晃动着脑袋，眨巴着死鱼眼。>' WHERE entry=12130; /* Text0_0: <Old Icefin eyes you warily, his fishy eye blinking as he bobs his head up and down once in a curt dismissal.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有其它假日能跟啤酒节的大吃大喝可以相比!',Text0_1_loc4='没有其它假日能跟啤酒节的大吃大喝可以相比!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12134; /* Text0_0: No other holiday matches the feasting and drinking of Brewfest! */ /* Text0_1: No other holiday matches the feasting and drinking of Brewfest! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奉劝你一句话，陌生人，回到你原来的地方吧。$B$B这里并不适合无忧无虑的探险者。这里会将你这种人吞食掉，只留下骨头而已。' WHERE entry=12135; /* Text0_0: A word to the wise, stranger, go back to wherever you\'re from.$b$bThis is no place for lighthearted adventurers. It\'ll chew up the likes of you and spit out your bones. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个大型的南瓜灯笼座落在村落的中央。' WHERE entry=12137; /* Text0_0: This large jack-o\'-lantern rests in the middle of the village. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个南瓜已经被砸碎过了，不再提供任何宝物。' WHERE entry=12138; /* Text0_0: The pumpkin has been smashed, and offers no more treasure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='将南瓜砸碎显示了一样隐藏的宝物!这是你有过最棒的一天了!' WHERE entry=12140; /* Text0_0: Smashing the pumpkin reveals a hidden treasure!  This is the greatest day you\'ve ever known! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎光临啤酒节场地，朋友!当我们在庆祝酿酒场对手间友善竞赛的精神时，这里还有许多东西可以好好享用。如果你有任何疑问的话，请告诉我!' WHERE entry=12152; /* Text0_0: Welcome, friend, to the Brewfest Grounds! There\'s much to enjoy here while we celebrate the spirit of friendly competition between rival breweries. If you have any questions, let me know! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啤酒节就是好好地在各大陆中享用美食及美酒，而且那一点都不夸大!只要看一眼手边这些令人精神振奋的手工啤酒及节日香肠，咸脆饼，以及起司。你将找不到更好的东西，而且只需要如此低廉的花费!' WHERE entry=12154; /* Text0_0: Brewfest is all about enjoying the very best food and drink in the lands, and that\'s no exaggeration! Just take a gander at the many invigorating hand-crafted beers and holiday sausages, pretzels, and cheeses available. You\'ll find nothing better, and for so little coin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='仅次於啤酒与香肠，啤酒节中最受欢迎的部分就是纪念品!从传统节日服装至美味啤酒的迷你桶，所有啤酒节的主题商品都可从贝尔碧·迅移那找到。只要确认手中拥有大量的啤酒节奖品章，因为这是唯一可以购买纪念品的方式!你可以在啤酒节场地附近帮忙来挣得啤酒节奖品章。' WHERE entry=12155; /* Text0_0: Next to the beer and sausage, the most popular part of Brewfest is the souvenirs! From traditional holiday garb to mini-kegs of tasty brew, all sorts of Brewfest-themed items are available from Belbi Quikswitch. Just be sure to have plenty of Brewfest Prize Tokens on hand, as it\'s the only way to buy them! You can earn prize tokens by helping out around the Brewfest Grounds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='山羊竞速是啤酒节伟大传统之一。如果你想要了解更多的话，去与后面山羊兽栏的保尔·安伯斯堤尔谈谈。那是个正确的，「并且」会是个获得啤酒节奖品章的绝佳方式!' WHERE entry=12156; /* Text0_0: Ram racing is one of the great traditions of Brewfest. Speak to Pol Amberstill down by the ram stable if you want to learn more. It\'s a right hoot AND can be a great way to earn Brewfest Prize Tokens! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨你好，欢迎光临啤酒节!在那里有一堆方式能让你尽兴，所以你要是有什麽问题呢，你就告诉我。除此之外，去买几瓶啤酒跟一包咸脆饼吧!' WHERE entry=12157; /* Text0_0: Hey there, welcome to Brewfest! There\'s a mess of ways to keep yourself entertained in there, so you got any questions, you let me know. Otherwise, go buy some beer and a pretzel! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啤酒节全都是啤酒及食物，且不会有其他比我们端上的菜色更好了。怀疑我在骗人吗?只要看看我们这些美味的啤酒、香肠、咸脆饼以及起司。你将会知道:这是附近最好的食物，而且找不到更便宜的了!' WHERE entry=12158; /* Text0_0: Brewfest is all about the beer and the eats, and it don\'t get any better than what we\'re serving up. Think I\'m lying? Just check out all the tasty brews, sausages, pretzels, and cheeses we got. You\'ll see: Best chow around, and it don\'t get any cheaper! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='每个人都爱死了那些疯狂的啤酒节竞速山羊了。想要了解更多吗?去跟后面山羊兽栏的德瑞兹·迅跌谈谈。祝你玩得开心，并赢取一些啤酒节奖品章!' WHERE entry=12159; /* Text0_0: Everyone loves those crazy Brewfest racing rams. Want to know more? Talk to Driz Tumblequick down by the ram stable. Have a blast and earn some Brewfest Prize Tokens while you\'re at it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨嗨，别忘了帮你自己抢一些啤酒节纪念品!我们有各式各样的东西，从传统节日服装到满载美味啤酒的迷你桶都有。只要去跟布力克斯·修械谈谈，不过得确认一下你手上有够多的啤酒节奖品章…这是购买纪念品的唯一方式!你可以在啤酒节场地附近帮忙来挣得啤酒节奖品章。' WHERE entry=12160; /* Text0_0: Hey hey, don\'t forget to grab yourself some Brewfest souvenirs! We got everything from traditional holiday garb to mini-kegs of tasty brew. Just talk to Blix Fixwidget, but make sure you got plenty of Brewfest Prize Tokens on hand... it\'s the only way to buy them! You can earn prize tokens by helping out around the Brewfest Grounds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，愿伊露恩之光保佑你。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，愿伊露恩之光保佑你。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12162; /* Text0_0: Greetings, Light of Elune be with you. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, Light of Elune be with you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我告诉你，正确的打猎方法就是先把自己灌醉!' WHERE entry=12165; /* Text0_0: I\'ll tell ya, the only proper way to hunt is when yer good an\' hammered! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<猎鹰发出饥饿的叫声，想要吃幼虫。>' WHERE entry=12168; /* Text0_0: <The falcon squawks hungrily for a grub.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='“朋友”，你最好埋下头！希望你懂我的意思！$B$B耶！' WHERE entry=12170; /* Text0_0: Best keep yer head down, "matey!"  If ye know what I mean!$B$BYarrrr! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我负责主持格斗比赛。你想不想赌一把啊？怎么样，有信心吗？但是——谁敢搞贿赂选手的猫腻，我就让他走跳板。$B$B我会亲自维持比赛的公平！' WHERE entry=12173; /* Text0_0: I run the fights around here.  You want to place a bet, gamble with confidence - anyone caught fixin\' fights gets to walk the plank.$B$BI\'ll make sure of that myself! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='“疯狗”约纳·斯特林要我整日整夜地打扫甲板。$B$B打扫甲板？！$B$B我是个法师，凭什么让我做这种杂事！就算要打扫，也该玩点新花样吧。',Text0_1_loc4='“疯狗”约纳·斯特林要我整日整夜地打扫甲板。$B$B打扫甲板？！$B$B我是个法师，凭什么让我做这种杂事！就算要打扫，也该玩点新花样吧。' WHERE entry=12176; /* Text0_0: Day in and day out all Mad Jonah Sterling wants me to do is swab the decks.$B$BSwab the decks?!$B$BI\'m a mage, I don\'t DO swabbin\'! At least not the mundane way. */ /* Text0_1: Day in and day out all Mad Jonah Sterling wants me to do is swab the decks.$B$BSwab the decks?!$B$BI\'m a mage, I don\'t DO swabbin\'! At least not the mundane way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='来点什么呢？朗姆酒？还是麦酒？$B$B或者你想尝尝别的？',Text0_1_loc4='来点什么呢？朗姆酒？还是麦酒？$B$B或者你想尝尝别的？' WHERE entry=12179; /* Text0_0: What\'s it going to be, then?  Rum?  Ale?$B$BOr perhaps something else? */ /* Text0_1: What\'s it going to be, then?  Rum?  Ale?$B$BOr perhaps something else? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想公然和杰克叫板是吗？$B$B嘿，我得说着这绝对是个……愚蠢的决定。这会让你损失惨重的。我可不想冒着丢掉小命的危险去干这种一分钱都挣不来的破事。嗯，你最好等我跑远了再动手。',Text0_1_loc4='你想公然和杰克叫板是吗？$B$B嘿，我得说着这绝对是个……愚蠢的决定。这会让你损失惨重的。我可不想冒着丢掉小命的危险去干这种一分钱都挣不来的破事。嗯，你最好等我跑远了再动手。' WHERE entry=12180; /* Text0_0: You\'re going to pull off a stunt on Jack in front of his boys?$B$BThat takes a good amount of... stupidity.  Well, it\'s going to cost you.  I\'m not going to risk my life for anything less than a gold.  And you best wait til I\'m out of the way before you make a move. */ /* Text0_1: You\'re going to pull off a stunt on Jack in front of his boys?$B$BThat takes a good amount of... stupidity.  Well, it\'s going to cost you.  I\'m not going to risk my life for anything less than a gold.  And you best wait til I\'m out of the way before you make a move. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喝酒的藉口是什麽都没有关系啦!' WHERE entry=12181; /* Text0_0: It never hurts to have a reason to drink! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='某件事激怒了那些黑铁矮人。他们几乎每半个小时就出现一次，把所有的桶子破坏后扬长而去!$B$B因此你一定会想问。「这干我什麽事?」$B$B我来告诉你…因为他们的破坏使我们无法提供免费的啤酒!你没听错，免费的啤酒!$B$B所以，如果那些矮人来袭时你在附近的话，花点时间帮忙保护这些桶子吧。' WHERE entry=12182; /* Text0_0: Something\'s got those Dark Iron Dwarves riled up.  They show up almost every half-hour, break all the kegs, and leave!$b$bSo you\'re probably asking, "Why should I care?"$b$bI\'ll tell you...  Because the kegs they break stop us from giving out free brew!  You heard me right, free brew!$b$bSo if you are around when those dwarves show up, take a minute and help protect the kegs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啤酒节是个无懈可击的节日!不过美中不足的是黑铁矮人的袭击。他们几乎每半个小时就来一次!$B$B攻击目标是那些发送「免费」啤酒的桶子!这些都是由啤酒大师所提供的美味啤酒!$B$B听着，如果你在那些黑铁矮人出现时刚好在附近的话，帮忙保护一下这些「免费」的啤酒。' WHERE entry=12183; /* Text0_0: Brewfest is the perfect holiday!  But it\'s got one catch, Dark Iron dwarf attacks.  They happen nearly every half-hour!$b$bThe attackers target the kegs that dispense the FREE brew!  And it\'s really good brew that the brewmasters are giving out!$b$bLook, if you\'re around when the Dark Iron dwarves show up, lend a hand and protect the FREE brew. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎回来，$n。' WHERE entry=12185; /* Text0_0: Welcome back, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='约纳·斯特林这个蠢货迟早要害死我们。如果他多花点时间观察局势的话，就会明白在战争期间攻击职业海军是件多么愚蠢的事。',Text0_1_loc4='约纳·斯特林这个蠢货迟早要害死我们。如果他多花点时间观察局势的话，就会明白在战争期间攻击职业海军是件多么愚蠢的事。' WHERE entry=12186; /* Text0_0: That cursed Jonah Sterling will lead us right into doom.  If he spent more time outside of his cave, he would realize the folly of attacking professional navies in a time of war. */ /* Text0_1: That cursed Jonah Sterling will lead us right into doom.  If he spent more time outside of his cave, he would realize the folly of attacking professional navies in a time of war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='瞧，那家伙正在为地毯的事烦恼呢。' WHERE entry=12190; /* Text0_0: The Dude, over yonder, is pretty upset about his rug. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='晚上好。',Text0_1_loc4='晚上好。' WHERE entry=12191; /* Text0_0: Evenin\', Gov\'na. */ /* Text0_1: Evenin\', Gov\'na. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呃……这么说……你打算启程返回前哨站，是吧？' WHERE entry=12193; /* Text0_0: I su... sur... surpose that yar wanna ride back to der outpost. Yarp? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一天两次，早上及晚上六点15分，大工匠梅卡托克本人为开桶仪式亲临啤酒节场地。千万别错过!' WHERE entry=12195; /* Text0_0: Twice a day, at six fifteen in the morning and six fifteen in the evening, High Tinker Mekkatorque himself comes out to the Brewfest grounds for the Tapping of the Keg ceremony. Don\'t miss it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一天两次，早上及晚上六点15分，暗影猎人沃金本人为开桶仪式亲临啤酒节场地。错过的是呆子!' WHERE entry=12196; /* Text0_0: Twice a day, at six fifteen in the morning and six fifteen in the evening, Shadow Hunter Vol\'jin himself comes out to the Brewfest grounds for the Tapping of the Keg ceremony. You\'d be a fool to miss it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这桶麦芽酒由加文·雷酒看管着。只要他在地窖里，谁都别想碰这些麦芽酒桶。$B' WHERE entry=12198; /* Text0_0: This barrel of ale is guarded by Jarven Thunderbrew.  As long as he\'s in the basement, no barrels may be disturbed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小胡子船长是最棒的!',Text1_0_loc4='小胡子船长是最棒的!' WHERE entry=12207; /* Text0_0: Cap\'n Stash is the BEST! */ /* Text1_0: I swab the decks! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='小胡子船长是最棒的!',Text3_0_loc4='小胡子船长是最棒的!' WHERE entry=12207; /* Text2_0: The Lady Mehley is the best ship EVER! */ /* Text3_0: Swabbin\' decks cured my rickets! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='时代改变了，$N。战争来临了。$B$B我的族人会在这个时机崛起并且协助我们的盟友…或是我们会继续在边缘苟延?' WHERE entry=12208; /* Text0_0: Times are changing, $N.  War has arrived.$B$BWill our people rise to the occasion and aid our allies... or will we linger in the sidelines? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有什麽时间可以聊天，抱歉。' WHERE entry=12209; /* Text0_0: I\'ve little time for talk, sorry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没看到我正在这里忙吗，$g小夥子:姑娘;?在被可沃斯基看到我在闲聊之前，快滚。',Text0_1_loc4='你没看到我正在这里忙吗，$g小夥子:姑娘;?在被可沃斯基看到我在闲聊之前，快滚。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12210; /* Text0_0: Can\'t ya see I\'m workin\' here, $glad:lass;? Off with ya, afore Kowalski sees me jawin.\' */ /* Text0_1: Can\'t ya see I\'m workin\' here, $glad:lass;? Off with ya, afore Kowalski sees me jawin.\' */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多苟利对我们很严格，不过他是个好船长，没错。' WHERE entry=12212; /* Text0_0: Torgoley works us hard, but he\'s a good captain, aye. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们已经没剩多少人了，$N。我们古老宿敌的回归令人非常担忧。' WHERE entry=12213; /* Text0_0: There aren\'t many of us left, $N.  The return of our old enemy is a cause for great concern. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我必须得盯牢这艘船及船员，好心的$g先生:女士;。你一定要原谅我无法停下来跟你进行交谈。' WHERE entry=12214; /* Text0_0: I must keep my eyes on ship and crew, good $gsir:madame;. You must forgive my not pausing to speak with you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='梅利女士号真的就在塞拉摩，我们已经被指派去守卫船上的乘客了。',Text0_1_loc4='梅利女士号真的就在塞拉摩，我们已经被指派去守卫船上的乘客了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12215; /* Text0_0: The Lady Mehley is in Theramore enough that we\'ve been assigned to guard her passengers. */ /* Text0_1: The Lady Mehley is in Theramore enough that we\'ve been assigned to guard her passengers. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是呀，梅蕾女士号，她是一艘很漂亮的船。$b$b你知道，呆在船上能学到很多知识的。有首诗说得好：苍茫黑夜中两只落寞行船，擦身而过时互相道安，风笛长鸣，堪堪见到模糊的形，片刻后却只余远去的影；人生亦如这广阔的洋，你我的船不期中徜徉而遇，彼此仅是浅烙下容与音，即又遁入黑暗与寂静。' WHERE entry=12217; /* Text0_0: Aye, that\'s her name, and a fine ship she is.$b$bThere\'s much to learn from such vessels, you know. A great poet once said: Ships that pass in the night, and speak each other in passing, only a signal shown, and a distant voice in the darkness; So on the ocean of life, we pass and speak one another, only a look and a voice, then darkness again and a silence. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='肚子饿的话，可以找厨师长格莱斯。' WHERE entry=12218; /* Text0_0: Should you desire sustenance, Galley Chief Grace can tend to your needs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='考布斯先生是随船的工程师和军需官，他出售各种你可能需要的物资。若是你想要修理装备的话，也可以找他哦，他技术不错的。' WHERE entry=12219; /* Text0_0: Mr. Combs, the ship\'s engineer and quartermaster, can furnish you with whatever supplies you might require. He is a fair tinker, too, if your gear is in need of repair. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，是啊……这个名字。嗯……人们常说，好名字就像美好的愿望，你需要用心经营，却很可能因一次失误前功尽弃。至于我的名字的由来嘛，不用说也知道为什么别人这么称呼我吧……' WHERE entry=12220; /* Text0_0: Ah, yes, that... the name. Well... as they say, a good name, like good will, is got by many actions and lost by one. No need to go into the hows or whys; suffice to say, that is how I am named by some. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果我们想要成功地建立一道传送门通往奎尔达纳斯之岛，联络整个太阳之井。我们一定会需要一个强大的能量来源好维持传送门。$B$B我们的目标已经完成了$3269w％。你愿意帮助我们吗，$c?' WHERE entry=12226; /* Text0_0: If we are to be successful in the creation of a portal to the Isle of Quel\'Danas, and the Sunwell which rests upon it, we must acquire an energy source powerful enough to ignite the portal.$B$BWe are $3269w percent completed with our efforts. Will you assist us, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座传送门不像其他通往艾泽拉斯的。要维持它，我们需要更多的法力电池。$B$B否则我们就会失去通往奎尔达纳斯之岛与太阳之井的通道。' WHERE entry=12227; /* Text0_0: This portal is not like the others that lead back to Azeroth. To maintain it, we must acquire more mana cells.$B$BIt is either that or risk losing our access to the Isle of Quel\'Danas and the Sunwell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，$r。$B$B我的店舖终於开了。希望你有看到喜欢的!',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎，$r。$B$B我的店舖终於开了。希望你有看到喜欢的!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12237; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $r.$b$bMy shop is finally open. I hope you like what you see! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $r.$b$bMy shop is finally open. I hope you like what you see! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='日安，$c。$B$B这里还有好多事情等着完成。可惜我目前帮不上你的忙，除非我能拿到我的补给品。$B$B我现在才取得$3223w％的刺棘根茎。你提供的任何协助都是有价值的，我向你保证。',Text0_1_loc4='日安，$c。$B$B这里还有好多事情等着完成。可惜我目前帮不上你的忙，除非我能拿到我的补给品。$B$B我现在才取得$3223w％的刺棘根茎。你提供的任何协助都是有价值的，我向你保证。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12238; /* Text0_0: Good day to you, $c.$b$bThere\'s much to be done to assist in the effort here. Sadly, there\'s very little I can do for you until I get all of my supplies.$b$bI\'ve now got $3223w percent of the razorthorn roots I need to get started. Any assistance you provide will be well worth the effort, I assure you. */ /* Text0_1: Good day to you, $c.$b$bThere\'s much to be done to assist in the effort here. Sadly, there\'s very little I can do for you until I get all of my supplies.$b$bI\'ve now got $3223w percent of the razorthorn roots I need to get started. Any assistance you provide will be well worth the effort, I assure you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是凯尔的军队用来逃往太阳之井的通道。一些只会奉承他的宠物狗被留了下来；燃烧军团以一些...不寻常的方法奖赏了他们。',Text0_1_loc4='这就是凯尔的军队用来逃往太阳之井的通道。一些只会奉承他的宠物狗被留了下来；燃烧军团以一些...不寻常的方法奖赏了他们。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12239; /* Text0_0: This is the gateway that Kael\'s armies used to retreat to the Sunwell.  Some of his lapdogs remain here; the Legion has rewarded them in a most... unusual way. */ /* Text0_1: This is the gateway that Kael\'s armies used to retreat to the Sunwell.  Some of his lapdogs remain here; the Legion has rewarded them in a most... unusual way. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你有看到岛上那些受损漫游的哨兵吗?只需要对控制水晶做些调整，就让我们控制这些哨兵，并且用他们来守卫我们的战略据点。$B$B日境圣所很快就是我们的。我们目前的目标达成率为$3233w％。',Text0_1_loc4='你有看到岛上那些受损漫游的哨兵吗?只需要对控制水晶做些调整，就让我们控制这些哨兵，并且用他们来守卫我们的战略据点。$B$B日境圣所很快就是我们的。我们目前的目标达成率为$3233w％。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12240; /* Text0_0: Have you seen the damaged sentries that wander the island?  A few modifications to the crystals that control their behavior will allow us to gain control of them and use them to secure tactical locations.$B$BThe Sun\'s Reach Sanctum will be ours in no time.  We are $3244w percent done with this goal. */ /* Text0_1: Have you seen the damaged sentries that wander the island?  A few modifications to the crystals that control their behavior will allow us to gain control of them and use them to secure tactical locations.$B$BThe Sun\'s Reach Sanctum will be ours in no time.  We are $3244w percent done with this goal. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们成功地拿下了圣所。我们可以继续转换那些哨兵，用他们来防卫其他战略位置。',Text0_1_loc4='我们成功地拿下了圣所。我们可以继续转换那些哨兵，用他们来防卫其他战略位置。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12241; /* Text0_0: We succeeded in taking the Sanctum.  We can continue to convert sentries and use them as guards at other tactical locations. */ /* Text0_1: We succeeded in taking the Sanctum.  We can continue to convert sentries and use them as guards at other tactical locations. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须确保不会再有谁葬身大海。',Text0_1_loc4='我们必须确保不会再有谁葬身大海。' WHERE entry=12243; /* Text0_0: We must make sure not to lose any more souls to the seas. */ /* Text0_1: We must make sure not to lose any more souls to the seas. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，请原谅，我必须专心工作。',Text0_1_loc4='$c，请原谅，我必须专心工作。' WHERE entry=12244; /* Text0_0: Forgive me $c, but I must concentrate on my job. */ /* Text0_1: Forgive me $c, but I must concentrate on my job. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='许多人在大海中失去了身影。我，以及这些幽光，则负责寻找那些灵魂。',Text0_1_loc4='许多人在大海中失去了身影。我，以及这些幽光，则负责寻找那些灵魂。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12245; /* Text0_0: Many have been lost to the seas.  I, and the wisps, are charged with looking for those souls. */ /* Text0_1: Many have been lost to the seas.  I, and the wisps, are charged with looking for those souls. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我和小精灵守护着那些迷失的灵魂。',Text0_1_loc4='我和小精灵守护着那些迷失的灵魂。' WHERE entry=12246; /* Text0_0: The wisps and I watch the seas for any lost souls. */ /* Text0_1: The wisps and I watch the seas for any lost souls. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='海洋是个危险的地方，$c。我们必须保持警惕。',Text0_1_loc4='海洋是个危险的地方，$c。我们必须保持警惕。' WHERE entry=12247; /* Text0_0: The seas are a dangerous place, $c.  We must be alert. */ /* Text0_1: The seas are a dangerous place, $c.  We must be alert. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在恐怕不能和你谈话。',Text0_1_loc4='我现在恐怕不能和你谈话。' WHERE entry=12248; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid I cannot speak with you at the moment. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m afraid I cannot speak with you at the moment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以看得出来我这里没有太多工作。在如此靠近前线的战斗区域服务是个不错的转换。' WHERE entry=12252; /* Text0_0: You don\'t get to see much action in my line of work.  Serving this close to the front lines in a combat zone is a nice change of pace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='占领日境圣所只是我们作战计画的第一步。下一个目标就是军械库。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3233w％。' WHERE entry=12255; /* Text0_0: Capturing the Sun\'s Reach Sanctum was the first step in our battle plan.  Our orders are to take control of the armory next.$B$BWe are $3233w percent done with our goal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们控制了军械库，但是我们在岛上的任务还没结束。' WHERE entry=12256; /* Text0_0: We have gained control of the armory, but our work on the island is not yet finished. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的任务就是在死亡之痕造成干扰，好让我们的部队可以占领日境军械库。这几乎和面对面杀死恶魔一样吸引人。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3233w％。',Text0_1_loc4='我的任务就是在死亡之痕造成干扰，好让我们的部队可以占领日境军械库。这几乎和面对面杀死恶魔一样吸引人。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3233w％。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12257; /* Text0_0: My orders are to create a distraction at the Dead Scar so our forces can take the Sun\'s Reach Armory.  It might not be as glamorous as killing demons face to face, but if it wins us this battle then I\'m all for it.$B$BWe are $3233w percent done with our goal. */ /* Text0_1: My orders are to create a distraction at the Dead Scar so our forces can take the Sun\'s Reach Armory.  It might not be as glamorous as killing demons face to face, but if it wins us this battle then I\'m all for it.$B$BWe are $3233w percent done with our goal. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们占领了军械库，$N。然而，我们却不能因为这点胜利而歇息。因为燃烧军团肯定不会停歇。',Text0_1_loc4='我们占领了军械库，$N。然而，我们却不能因为这点胜利而歇息。因为燃烧军团肯定不会停歇。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12258; /* Text0_0: We\'ve captured the armory, $N.  Let\'s not rest on our laurels, however.  The Legion sure will not. */ /* Text0_1: We\'ve captured the armory, $N.  Let\'s not rest on our laurels, however.  The Legion sure will not. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的努力获得了回报。我们占领了日境圣所，$N。去那边看看你能帮得上什麽忙。' WHERE entry=12259; /* Text0_0: Our efforts have paid off.  We\'ve captured the Sun\'s Reach Sanctum, $N.  Go there and see if there\'s anyone you can assist. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='强化圣所周围的结界可以帮助我们更快地巩固此地。我们可不希望有任何鄙恶者干扰我们对燃烧军团还有凯尔的全面进攻。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3244w％。' WHERE entry=12260; /* Text0_0: Arming the wards at the sanctum will help us secure it faster.  We don\'t want any Wretched getting in our way when we unleash a full scale attack on the Legion and Kael.$B$BWe are $3244w percent done with our goal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='勇者号上的水手将竭诚为你提供温馨舒适的服务。' WHERE entry=12262; /* Text0_0: The Bravery\'s crew will do its best to make your journey as swift and pleasant as possible. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不好意思，我们还是另找时间谈吧。再见。' WHERE entry=12263; /* Text0_0: Sorry, but we\'ll have to speak some other time. Farewell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎乘坐勇者号。不好意思，失陪……',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎乘坐勇者号。不好意思，失陪……' WHERE entry=12264; /* Text0_0: Welcome to The Bravery, $gsir:madame;. Now if you\'ll excuse me... */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to The Bravery, $gsir:madame;. Now if you\'ll excuse me... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对水手来说，这是个不幸的名字，是吗？',Text0_1_loc4='对水手来说，这是个不幸的名字，是吗？' WHERE entry=12267; /* Text0_0: Unlucky name fer a sailor, innit? */ /* Text0_1: Unlucky name fer a sailor, innit? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你的肚子饿得咕咕叫，就去找厨师长拜雷·钢胃谈谈，可别说是我告诉你的这家伙的名字可是有来历的……' WHERE entry=12273; /* Text0_0: If your stomach\'s rumbling, talk to Galley Chief Steelbelly, but just between you and me? You might want to wait. He\'s got that name for a reason. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎登上羽月渡口。我们往来於羽月要塞及被遗忘的海岸之间搜寻那些在海上失踪的人们。大海对那些没做好准备的人来说会是个危险的地方。$B$B如果你需要准备什麽的话，请与我们的物资供应者谈谈。他们会很乐意帮忙你的。' WHERE entry=12275; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Feathermoon Ferry.  We travel between Feathermoon Stronghold and the Forgotten Coast looking for those lost at sea.  The sea can be a dangerous place if you are not prepared.$b$bIf you need to get prepared, please speak to our provisioners.  They are more than happy to help you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='搭乘艾露恩的祝福号时请保持警惕，$r。虽然艾露恩保佑我们找到了新的盟友，但是深不可测的海洋依然危机四伏。$B$B但是，在月神的感召下，我们承担起搜寻失落灵魂的重任。' WHERE entry=12277; /* Text0_0: Watch your step aboard Elune\'s Blessing, $r.  Though Elune\'s blessed us with the discovery of our new friends, we\'ve also had our share of hardships at sea.$b$bHowever, recovering souls lost at sea or lost in a new world is truly a blessing from Elune. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在航海之旅中，艾露恩一直庇护着我们。但是我们仍然要保持警惕，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='在航海之旅中，艾露恩一直庇护着我们。但是我们仍然要保持警惕，$c。' WHERE entry=12278; /* Text0_0: Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不好意思，$r，我必须专心工作。',Text0_1_loc4='不好意思，$r，我必须专心工作。' WHERE entry=12279; /* Text0_0: Forgive me, $r, I must focus on my job. */ /* Text0_1: Forgive me, $r, I must focus on my job. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎登上少女之爱号。它将会一路顺风的抵达港口。' WHERE entry=12281; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Maiden\'s Fancy. It should be smooth sailing all the way to port. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你用力压榨地精的话，你可以从他身上学到很惊人的东西:逃脱捆绑的聪明小把戏，制造美味的饼乾，甚至连如何制造出一台飞行器都有。' WHERE entry=12282; /* Text0_0: It\'s amazing what you can learn from a gnome if you squeeze them hard enough: clever little tricks about getting out of a bind, making delicious cookies, and even how to make a flying machine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='常常。这是好活动，让我可以知道他们在忙些什麽--就我的经验来说，绝对不是好事。' WHERE entry=12283; /* Text0_0: As often as I can.  It\'s great exercise and it keeps me informed on what they\'re up to--which, from my experience, is always no good. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恶恶恶...要是那边那个肮脏的船舱长要你吃他的特别餐的话，帮你自己个忙，把它丢到海里吧。它可能可以杀死几个你想致之死地的龙虾人。' WHERE entry=12284; /* Text0_0: Urrrk... if that grubbing galley chief over there offers you his special, do yourself a favor and dump it in the ocean. It might kill a few makruras instead of your will to live. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$r。$B$B动手吧!别浪费时间等那些可能永远也不会到的补给。$B$B我需要我的铁砧来替部队打造装备。目前才完成了$3228w％。$B$B当铁砧完成后，我将可以为你做出更多强而有力的物品。',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，$r。$B$B动手吧!别浪费时间等那些可能永远也不会到的补给。$B$B我需要我的铁砧来替部队打造装备。目前才完成了$3228w％。$B$B当铁砧完成后，我将可以为你做出更多强而有力的物品。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12285; /* Text0_0: Hello, $r.$b$bLet\'s get busy! No sense waiting around for supplies that may never arrive.$b$bI need my anvil in order to outfit our troops properly. Right now It\'s $3228w percent complete.$b$bAnd when the anvil is completed, there will be many more powerful items that I will be able to smith for you. */ /* Text0_1: Hello, $r.$b$bLet\'s get busy! No sense waiting around for supplies that may never arrive.$b$bI need my anvil in order to outfit our troops properly. Right now It\'s $3228w percent complete.$b$bAnd when the anvil is completed, there will be many more powerful items that I will be able to smith for you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$n。$B$B现在我已经完成了铁砧，可以开始替部队提供装备了。这是很重要的一步，但还有许多事情得去做。$B$B更重要的是，我能制作新东西了，你可能会很感兴趣的东西。',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，$n。$B$B现在我已经完成了铁砧，可以开始替部队提供装备了。这是很重要的一步，但还有许多事情得去做。$B$B更重要的是，我能制作新东西了，你可能会很感兴趣的东西。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12286; /* Text0_0: Hello, $n.$b$bNow that I\'ve finished creating my anvil I can begin outfitting our troops. It\'s an important step, but there\'s still much to be done.$b$bMore importantly for you, there are new things that I can create, which you may be interested in. */ /* Text0_1: Hello, $n.$b$bNow that I\'ve finished creating my anvil I can begin outfitting our troops. It\'s an important step, but there\'s still much to be done.$b$bMore importantly for you, there are new things that I can create, which you may be interested in. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们拿下了港口，而这艘船更是额外的收获。可惜她已经不再适合航行了。$B$B不过我被指派要干扰绿鳃海岸的纳迦。$B$B你能给我一些帮助吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我们拿下了港口，而这艘船更是额外的收获。可惜她已经不再适合航行了。$B$B不过我被指派要干扰绿鳃海岸的纳迦。$B$B你能给我一些帮助吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12287; /* Text0_0: We\'ve taken the harbor, and this ship is a nice bonus. Too bad she\'s not yet sea-worthy.$B$BIn the meantime, I\'ve been instructed to oversee the disruption of the naga on the Greengill Coast.$B$BThink you can help me out? */ /* Text0_1: We\'ve taken the harbor, and this ship is a nice bonus. Too bad she\'s not yet sea-worthy.$B$BIn the meantime, I\'ve been instructed to oversee the disruption of the naga on the Greengill Coast.$B$BThink you can help me out? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎登上唤雷者号!$B$B别在意那些对爆炸或类似事情有所埋怨的人们。我是说真的，每个人都有犯错的时候。我们应该放过他们。$B$B瞧，我可以了解如果一位船长动不动就想把自己的船炸个22或23次的话...不过除此之外的事不值得一提。' WHERE entry=12288; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Thundercaller!$b$bDon\'t pay attention to the people that complain about explosions or the like.  I mean really, everyone makes mistakes.  We should cut people some slack.$b$bLook, I\'d understand if a captain managed to crash his ship 22 or 23 times... But anything less than that isn\'t worth mentioning. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<咕哝着>我猜那些山是凭空出现的…总共5次!',Text1_0_loc4='<咕哝着>我猜那些山是凭空出现的…总共5次!' WHERE entry=12289; /* Text0_0: <Grumbles>  I guess those mountains came out of nowhere...  All five times! */ /* Text1_0: <Grumbles>  You\'d think it would be hard to crash a zeppelin into the ocean.  You\'d think it\'d be even harder to do it four separate times! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='<咕哝着>我猜那些山是凭空出现的…总共5次!',Text3_0_loc4='<咕哝着>我猜那些山是凭空出现的…总共5次!' WHERE entry=12289; /* Text2_0: <Grumbles> I wish I could say we\'ve managed to avoid crash landing into lakes.  I wish I could say we\'ve only crashed into a lake once... but we\'ve managed to crash into four separate lakes, including Lordamere Lake! */ /* Text3_0: I am impressed that pine tree branches don\'t seem to damage our ship much.$b$bNot that it excuses the three times we\'ve crashed into some forest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我从来没想过我会亲眼见到泰达希尔…我当然从来没想到我们会坠落在泰达希尔。',Text5_0_loc4='我们现在得设法穿越雷霆崖两次！' WHERE entry=12289; /* Text4_0: I never thought I\'d get to see Teldrassil... I certainly never thought we\'d crash into Teldrassil. */ /* Text5_0: We\'ve managed to squeeze through Thunder Bluff twice now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='<咕哝着>我还是不知道我们是如何设法潜入通过千针石林还没被发现，却只是在闪光平原坠毁而已！' WHERE entry=12289; /* Text6_0: <Grumbles> I still don\'t know how we managed to snake through Thousand Needles without a scratch, only to crash and burn in the Shimmering Flats! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你喜欢刺激，那可是我们船长最擅长的事了！我爱这份工作！',Text0_1_loc4='如果你喜欢刺激，那可是我们船长最擅长的事了！我爱这份工作！',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12290; /* Text0_0: If you like excitement, our captain\'s the best!  I love this job! */ /* Text0_1: If you like excitement, our captain\'s the best!  I love this job! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要问...' WHERE entry=12291; /* Text0_0: Don\'t ask... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这件事故你不能怪我…我甚至连我要去哪都不知道!$B$B虽然也许那表示你可以责怪我…$B$B不!等等!我还可以将船停靠…这有可能是船长下的命令!也许他喜欢将我们逼到极限，然后测试我们生存及修理的能力。' WHERE entry=12292; /* Text0_0: You can\'t blame me for our mishaps... I can\'t even see where I\'m going!$b$bThough maybe that means you can blame me...$b$bNo!  Wait!  I can dock this ship just fine... It\'s gotta be the orders the captain issues!  Maybe he likes pushing us to our limits and testing our or survival and repair skills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我本来叫做洛罗，直到全镇秘密的投票将我的名字给改了。我只能接受他们替我取的新名字，不然就得叫做柯尔奇。如果换作是你也会和我的选择一样吧。你觉得我的新名字如何呢?好听多了，对吗?$B$B对了，假如你想找工作的话可以去看看布告栏。' WHERE entry=12294; /* Text0_0: I used to be known as Iolol until a secret vote was passed around town that resulted in me having to change my name. It was either change it or go the way of Corki. You would have done the same. What do you think of my new name? Huge improvement, right?$B$BBy the way, check the bulletin board if you\'re looking for work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很高兴你问了。我们完成了计画的$3233w％。$B$B我知道战斗法师艾里娜和先驱者因努罗需要你的帮忙。你可以在奎尔达纳斯之岛的日境圣所找到他们。' WHERE entry=12300; /* Text0_0: I am glad that you ask. Our efforts to take the armory are at $3233w percent of our projections.$B$BI know that Battlemage Arynna and Harbinger Inuuro need your help. Seek them inside the Sun\'s Reach Sanctum on the Isle of Quel\'Danas. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我从荷莎那边听来，她说我们才完成了目标的$3228w％。$B$B我无法说明完成这些对我们的计画来说有多重要。我们的男女战士都需要更好的铠甲与武器，而铁砧与熔炉是关键。$B$B你将会在日境军械库找到铁匠，$N。' WHERE entry=12301; /* Text0_0: Last I heard from Hauthaa, she indicated that we are $3228w percent of the way there.$B$BI cannot express how vital it is to our efforts that we get them created. Our men and women are going to need better armor and weapons, and the anvil and forge are the key to that.$B$BYou will find the smith behind the Sun\'s Reach Armory, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不，很不幸地我们还没拿下港口。然而，报告显示我们已经完成了$3238w％的目标。$B$B$N，如果你想要帮忙，可以去找奎尔达纳斯之岛上日境军械库的博学者伊拉斯塔和复仇者卡蓝。' WHERE entry=12302; /* Text0_0: No, unfortunately we have not yet taken the harbor. However, reports indicate that we are $3238w percent of the way towards doing so.$B$B$N, if you want to help out, look for Magister Ilastar and Vindicator Kaalan at the Sun\'s Reach Armory on the Isle of Quel\'Danas. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='链金实验室还没准备好，$N。玛纳说她才准备了$3223w％，然而。$B$B如果你愿意协助她的话，你可以在日境港的旅店中找到她。' WHERE entry=12303; /* Text0_0: The alchemy lab is not quite yet ready, $N. Mar\'nah says that she is $3223w percent done with its assembly, however.$B$BIf you would like to help her with that, you will find her inside the inn at the Sun\'s Reach Harbor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们还在努力终结第一道障壁。拜托，$c，前往奎尔达纳斯之岛并尽量帮忙我们!' WHERE entry=12304; /* Text0_0: We are trying to bring Agamath, the First Gate down. Please, $c, go to the Isle of Quel\'Danas and help in any way that you can! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='初始之门， 阿格玛司已经被破坏了，而基尔加丹的两大副官，莎珂蕾希女士和大术士艾黎瑟丝，一定得被消灭。$B$B召集你的朋友们，$c，解决它!洛罕铎，次之门是我们下一个目标。' WHERE entry=12305; /* Text0_0: Agamath, the First Gate is breached and two of Kil\'jaeden\'s lieutenants, Lady Sacrolash and Grand Warlock Alythess, must be destroyed.$B$BGather your friends, $c, and see to it! Rohendor, the Second Gate is our next target. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='万一基尔加丹觉醒，通过太阳之井进入我们的世界，他将会掀起一场大战，就像在10,000年前那样。' WHERE entry=12309; /* Text0_0: Should Kil\'jaeden rise up through the Sunwell our world will be thrown into a war the likes of which has not been seen for 10,000 years!$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='「铁鹰。」嗯。它是艘客船，而非战禽!不过嘿，工作就是工作，而我将迎合船长「浮夸」，既然好人都付钱了。$B$B无论如何，欢迎登船。',Text0_1_loc4='「铁鹰。」嗯。它是艘客船，而非战禽!不过嘿，工作就是工作，而我将迎合船长「浮夸」，既然好人都付钱了。$B$B无论如何，欢迎登船。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12314; /* Text0_0: "Iron Eagle." Hmph. It\'s a passenger ship, not a warbird! But hey, a job\'s a job, and I\'ll humor Captain "Bombast" so long as the prince is paying.$b$bIn any case, welcome aboard. */ /* Text0_1: "Iron Eagle." Hmph. It\'s a passenger ship, not a warbird! But hey, a job\'s a job, and I\'ll humor Captain "Bombast" so long as the prince is paying.$b$bIn any case, welcome aboard. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
