UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们保护这艘从奥格玛航行至荆棘谷格罗姆高营地的飞船。',Text0_1_loc4='我们保护这艘从奥格玛航行至荆棘谷格罗姆高营地的飞船。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12316; /* Text0_0: We protect this airship on its way from Orgrimmar to Grom\'gol base camp in Stranglethorn Vale. */ /* Text0_1: We protect this airship on its way from Orgrimmar to Grom\'gol base camp in Stranglethorn Vale. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不是现在，$g夥伴:甜心;...我有事情要忙。再见。' WHERE entry=12317; /* Text0_0: Not right now, $gpal:sugar;... I got things to do. See ya around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我驾驶艾泽拉斯里最坚固的飞船。她曾经装备着双轻型火炮和足以夷平一座城市的炸药，你知道的...光是她的影子就足够击退敌人了。$B$B什麽?这当然是真的!' WHERE entry=12318; /* Text0_0: I run the tightest airship in Azeroth. She used to be fitted with twin light cannons and enough bombs to flatten a city, you know... her mere shadow was enough rout armies.$b$bWhat? Of course it\'s true! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们快可以巩固对日境地区的控制权了。假如我们设法让那个港口无法获得援军支援的话，我们就可以办到了。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3238w％。' WHERE entry=12319; /* Text0_0: We\'ve almost consolidated our control over Sun\'s Reach.  If we manage to keep the harbor from getting any reinforcements we will certainly succeed.$B$BWe are $3238w percent done with our goal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们成功了，$N。现在日境已经在我们的控制之下，没多久我们就可以达到完全的胜利。' WHERE entry=12320; /* Text0_0: We\'ve done it, $N.  With Sun\'s Reach under our control we are but mere moments away from absolute victory. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我正在募集资金来盖一座纪念碑，以纪念那在战争中死去的英雄。我们不能忘记那些为了获得胜利而牺牲的人们。$B$B我们目前的目标达成度为$3275w％。',Text0_1_loc4='我正在募集资金来盖一座纪念碑，以纪念那在战争中死去的英雄。我们不能忘记那些为了获得胜利而牺牲的人们。$B$B我们目前的目标达成度为$3275w％。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12322; /* Text0_0: I\'m gathering funds to build a monument in honor of those who\'ve died in the war.  It is important to not forget the sacrifices we\'ve made to achieve victory.$B$BWe are $3275w percent done with this goal. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m gathering funds to build a monument in honor of those who\'ve died in the war.  It is important to not forget the sacrifices we\'ve made to achieve victory.$B$BWe are $3275w percent done with this goal. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个纪念碑很美吧?牢记那些历史上的重大牺牲是很重要的，免得我们忘记那些战争的代价 - 既使是那些胜利的战争。',Text0_1_loc4='这个纪念碑很美吧?牢记那些历史上的重大牺牲是很重要的，免得我们忘记那些战争的代价 - 既使是那些胜利的战争。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12323; /* Text0_0: Isn\'t the memorial beautiful?  It is important to remember moments in our history when great sacrifices are made, lest we forget the price of all wars - even ones that are won. */ /* Text0_1: Isn\'t the memorial beautiful?  It is important to remember moments in our history when great sacrifices are made, lest we forget the price of all wars - even ones that are won. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎登舰$c。卸下重担好好享受这趟旅途。在「紫色公主号」上我们希望你能够觉得放松。假如你登船后有任何需要的话，我们楼下备有贩卖机。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎登舰$c。卸下重担好好享受这趟旅途。在「紫色公主号」上我们希望你能够觉得放松。假如你登船后有任何需要的话，我们楼下备有贩卖机。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12327; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard $c.  Take a load off and enjoy the trip.  Aboard "The Purple Princess" we want you to relax.  We have vending machines down below if there\'s anything you might need while aboard. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome aboard $c.  Take a load off and enjoy the trip.  Aboard "The Purple Princess" we want you to relax.  We have vending machines down below if there\'s anything you might need while aboard. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='休息与消遣是成为一个有效率的船员的关键。让船员好好休息，他们才能表现得更好。' WHERE entry=12328; /* Text0_0: Relaxation is the key to being an efficient crew.  Let the crew relax, and they\'ll perform better. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请容许我休息一下。' WHERE entry=12330; /* Text0_0: Please allow me a few seconds of rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='妈，再让我多睡五分钟……' WHERE entry=12331; /* Text0_0: Let me sleep just five more minutes, mon... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在很忙。',Text0_1_loc4='我现在很忙。',Text1_0_loc4='有点忙。',Text1_1_loc4='我现在很忙。' WHERE entry=12332; /* Text0_0: I\'m busy right now. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m busy right now. */ /* Text1_0: You need something fixed? Use the Vend-O-Matic. */ /* Text1_1: You need something fixed? Use the Vend-O-Tron. */
