UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从葛罗姆高到幽暗城的飞行是多麽的美丽而平静。当然这不是在工作中睡着的藉口。',Text0_1_loc4='从葛罗姆高到幽暗城的飞行是多麽的美丽而平静。当然这不是在工作中睡着的藉口。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12333; /* Text0_0: The flight from Grom\'gol to Undercity is beautiful, though uneventful.  Though that is no excuse to fall asleep on the job. */ /* Text0_1: The flight from Grom\'gol to Undercity is beautiful, though uneventful.  Though that is no excuse to fall asleep on the job. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='经过了灰烬与污泥。让你自己风乾一阵子吧。' WHERE entry=12334; /* Text0_0: Come in out of the ash and muck. Dry yourself a spell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='牛头大佬在我替他们安排下一场巡回演出时都会待在银月城里。他们没排练的时候通常会在我上方的楼台里消磨时间。放心挥手吧...他们喜欢接受注目。$B$B我们目前没有接受表演或是工作人员，不过你以后可以常来连系看看。谁知道会发生什麽事呢?' WHERE entry=12335; /* Text0_0: The Tauren Chieftains are staying in Silvermoon while I arrange their next tour. They often lounge on the balcony above me when they\'re not practicing. Feel free to wave... they love the attention.$B$BWe\'re not currently hiring for the show or the crew, but you can always check back later. Who knows what will arise? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要毫无准备地和敌人交战，$N。我可以提供你非常强大的物品...因为你已经向我们证明了自己。',Text0_1_loc4='不要毫无准备地和敌人交战，$N。我可以提供你非常强大的物品...因为你已经向我们证明了自己。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12338; /* Text0_0: Do not fight the enemy unprepared, $N.  I can provide you with very powerful items... provided you have proven yourself to us. */ /* Text0_1: Do not fight the enemy unprepared, $N.  I can provide you with very powerful items... provided you have proven yourself to us. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='凯尔的宠物是该在羞辱中学上一课。我们将会击溃曦刃军团并且从他们手中夺下日境港。$B$B我们目前的目标达成率为$3238w％。' WHERE entry=12339; /* Text0_0: Kael\'s lackeys are about to be taught a lesson in humility.  We will crush the Dawnblade army and take Sun\'s Reach Harbor from them.$B$BWe are $3238w percent done with our goal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='日境属於我们了。凯尔的走狗四散奔逃...是时候来终结他们的苦难了!' WHERE entry=12340; /* Text0_0: Sun\'s Reach is ours.  Kael\'s dogs are on the run... it is time to put them out of their misery! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我负责管理支援牛头大佬的工作人员。$B$B你知道的:打包，开车，还有乐器拆卸，舞台搭盖及拆掉，设置烟火，所有这种类的事。' WHERE entry=12341; /* Text0_0: I\'m in charge of the workers that support the Tauren Chieftains.$B$BYou know: packing, driving, and unpacking the wagons, building and taking down the stage, setting up the pyrotechnics, all that sort of thing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的史怀哲是我的老朋友...那，是一件贵重的东西。我是说，友情。我想我会忘掉这种感觉，直到我们再度在撒塔斯城遇见。$B$B这些日子他没有常常待在提瑞斯法，所以我想我会使用这里的传送之门去传达我的问候。' WHERE entry=12342; /* Text0_0: Schweitzer here is an old friend of mine... a valuable thing, that. Friendship, I mean. I thought I\'d forgotten the feeling until we met again in Shattrath City.$B$BHe\'s not in Tirisfal so much these days, so I thought I\'d take the Orb of Translocation here to give my hellos. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Mmrrglglglg？Glbmr brmmrggl glmrrbmrgl。$B$BGrglgrlbrr mrgl！！！' WHERE entry=12343; /* Text0_0: Mmrrglglglg? Glbmr brmmrggl glmrrbmrgl.$B$BGrglgrlbrr mrgl!!! */
