UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿尔萨斯曾是万民敬仰的人类王子。他所率领的诺森德远征军遭遇了可怕的命运。$B$B我的哥哥萨萨里安就是军中的一员。',Text0_1_loc4='阿尔萨斯曾是万民敬仰的人类王子。他所率领的诺森德远征军遭遇了可怕的命运。$B$B我的哥哥萨萨里安就是军中的一员。' WHERE entry=12534; /* Text0_0: Arthas was once a human prince.  The army he led into Northrend suffered a horrible fate.$B$BMy brother, Thassarian, was a part of that army. */ /* Text0_1: Arthas was once a human prince.  The army he led into Northrend suffered a horrible fate.$B$BMy brother, Thassarian, was a part of that army. */
