UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='缝合场是天灾军团制造食尸鬼、憎恶和血肉巨人的中心。如果我们能摧毁这座工厂，巫妖王的力量就会被大大削弱。',Text0_1_loc4='缝合场是天灾军团制造食尸鬼、憎恶和血肉巨人的中心。如果我们能摧毁这座工厂，巫妖王的力量就会被大大削弱。' WHERE entry=13838; /* Text0_0: The Fleshwerks is the heart of the Scourge\'s ghoul, abomination, and flesh giant production. If we can take it out, the Lich King will be greatly weakened. */ /* Text0_1: The Fleshwerks is the heart of the Scourge\'s ghoul, abomination, and flesh giant production. If we can take it out, the Lich King will be greatly weakened. */
