UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在东瘟疫之地的圣光之愿礼拜堂，银色黎明指挥着对抗天灾军团的战斗。去那里接受命令吧。',Text0_1_loc4='在东瘟疫之地的圣光之愿礼拜堂，银色黎明指挥着对抗天灾军团的战斗。去那里接受命令吧。' WHERE entry=13915; /* Text0_0: The Argent Dawn coordinates the Scourge\'s opposition at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.  Go there for instructions. */ /* Text0_1: The Argent Dawn coordinates the Scourge\'s opposition at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.  Go there for instructions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='许多人都死在了瓦哈拉斯，他们的尸体见证了比武场的残酷。$B$B$n，你的骸骨是否也会留在荣耀与血腥的战场呢？',Text0_1_loc4='许多人都死在了瓦哈拉斯，他们的尸体见证了比武场的残酷。$B$B$n，你的骸骨是否也会留在荣耀与血腥的战场呢？' WHERE entry=13918; /* Text0_0: Many have fallen within Valhalas and their corpses are a testament to the strength of our ways.$B$BWill your bones litter this place of honor and battle as well, $N? */ /* Text0_1: Many have fallen within Valhalas and their corpses are a testament to the strength of our ways.$B$BWill your bones litter this place of honor and battle as well, $N? */
