UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素之灵与我们同在，$n。在它们的帮助下，我们可以竭尽全力阻止瓦里玛萨斯和普特雷斯的阴谋得逞！LOK\'TAR OGAR！' WHERE entry=14051; /* Text0_0: The elements are with us in force, $N. With their help, we will do all that is in our power to stop Varimathras and Putress! LOK\'TAR OGAR! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀！小声点，$n！怎么？你想把我们害死吗？！$B$B我当然知道你是谁！你的大名早就在联盟中传遍了！$B$B你觉得我的跳跃机器人怎么样啊？她是根据机械侏儒的原理设计的，运行起来非常流畅，是以空气为动力的！',Text0_1_loc4='哎呀！小声点，$n！怎么？你想把我们害死吗？！$B$B我当然知道你是谁！你的大名早就在联盟中传遍了！$B$B你觉得我的跳跃机器人怎么样啊？她是根据机械侏儒的原理设计的，运行起来非常流畅，是以空气为动力的！' WHERE entry=14052; /* Text0_0: Oh my gosh! Keep your voice down, $N! What? Are you trying to get us killed?!$B$BOf course I know who you are! Who in the Alliance doesn\'t know the name, $N?!$B$BSay, what do you think of my jumpbot? She\'s based off of the mechagnome design. Sleek and aerodynamic! */ /* Text0_1: Oh my gosh! Keep your voice down, $N! What? Are you trying to get us killed?!$B$BOf course I know who you are! Who in the Alliance doesn\'t know the name, $N?!$B$BSay, what do you think of my jumpbot? She\'s based off of the mechagnome design. Sleek and aerodynamic! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='形势严峻，没有捷径可走。如果你的战斗力够强，请掩护我的小队，直到他们做好爬上伊米海姆的准备。他们需要一切可利用的帮助。' WHERE entry=14055; /* Text0_0: We don\'t have any easy path before us. If you\'ve got a strong arm on you, stick around until one of my squads is ready to ascend to Ymirheim. They could use all the help they can get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀，你长得真难看！不过这并不表示你不会战斗。$B$B我麾下的一支小队很快就要出发啦——加入他们的行列，一起爬上伊米海姆吧！' WHERE entry=14061; /* Text0_0: Well you\'re an ugly one! Don\'t mean you don\'t know how to fight though.$B$BOne of my squads should be geared and ready to march soon - get your sorry butt in line and make the climb with them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='竞技场排名赛将在$6318d后再次拉开帷幕。$B$B未来的竞技场冠军正在忙于练习作战技巧以及搜寻最好的装备。你准备好了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='竞技场排名赛将在$6318d后再次拉开帷幕。$B$B未来的竞技场冠军正在忙于练习作战技巧以及搜寻最好的装备。你准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=14062; /* Text0_0: Ranked arena matches start again in $6318d.$B$BWould-be champions are already busy honing their skills and acquiring the best gear they can. Are you going to be ready? */ /* Text0_1: Ranked arena matches start again in $6318d.$B$BWould-be champions are already busy honing their skills and acquiring the best gear they can. Are you going to be ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该传送门通往时光之穴，它位于遥远的塔纳利斯沙漠地底。$B$B但是你的力量还不够强大，我建议你不要去那里。',Text0_1_loc4='该传送门通往时光之穴，它位于遥远的塔纳利斯沙漠地底。$B$B但是你的力量还不够强大，我建议你不要去那里。' WHERE entry=14066; /* Text0_0: This portal leads to the Caverns of Time, deep beneath the earth in far-off Tanaris.$B$BUntil you have grown stronger, though, I must ask you not to travel there. */ /* Text0_1: This portal leads to the Caverns of Time, deep beneath the earth in far-off Tanaris.$B$BUntil you have grown stronger, though, I must ask you not to travel there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能闻到炸弹和火箭里的火药味儿！你也要出去找些乐子吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能闻到炸弹和火箭里的火药味儿！你也要出去找些乐子吗？' WHERE entry=14067; /* Text0_0: I can smell the gunpowder from all the bombs and rockets!  You want to get out there and join the fun? */ /* Text0_1: I can smell the gunpowder from all the bombs and rockets!  You want to get out there and join the fun? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有很多声音在对我讲话。',Text1_0_loc4='我必须服从。' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text0_0: The voices are talking to me. */ /* Text1_0: I must obey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你最好赶紧离开，不然你也会被它影响！',Text3_0_loc4='它就在我们身边。就在我的脑海里！' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text2_0: You have to get out of here before it gets to you, too! */ /* Text3_0: It\'s all around us. It\'s in my head! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='萨隆邪铁……里面藏有什么东西！',Text5_0_loc4='邪铁里藏有东西！就在岩石和泥土里！' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text4_0: The saronite... there\'s something in it! */ /* Text5_0: There\'s something here.  It\'s in the rocks and the earth! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我要离开这里！你能放我出去吗？',Text7_0_loc4='你听见了吗？它正在你的脑海中低语。' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text6_0: I have to get out of here! Can you get me free? */ /* Text7_0: Can you hear it speaking in your mind? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='准备工作尚未完成。我们暂时还不会离开。' WHERE entry=14069; /* Text0_0: We\'re still making preparations. We won\'t be ready to go for a while. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们就快准备好啦。再给我们一点时间，很快就能出发了。' WHERE entry=14070; /* Text0_0: We\'re almost ready to depart. Just give us a little bit longer to finish our preparations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我在旅途中学会了精魂披风的图样。$B$B图样可交易，是史诗级的施法者披风，装备后可获得耐力、法术强度、智力以及法力回复速度的加成。我一直在寻找有资格学习这张图样的人。$B$B打通诺森德所有的普通难度地下城，并获得“诺森德地下城大师”成就的人才有资格学习精魂披风的图纸。' WHERE entry=14072; /* Text0_0: In my travels I have learned the recipe for the Wispcloak.$B$BThis cloak is a tradeable Epic spellcasting cloak that grants Stamina, Spellpower, Intellect and Mana Recovery.   I am looking for someone worthy to teach this recipe to.$B$BSomeone who had completed all the normal dungeons of Northrend and had the "Northrend Dungeonmaster" achievement would be worthy of learning the recipe for the Wispcloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾去过许多黑暗的地方，学会了死寒披风的图样。$B$B图样可交易，是史诗级的施法者披风，装备后可获得法术强度、急速以及爆击的加成。我一直在寻找有资格学习这张图样的人。$B$B完成诺森德的大部分任务，并获得“诺森德的博学者”成就的人才有资格学习死寒披风的图纸。' WHERE entry=14074; /* Text0_0: I have ventured to dark places and learned the tailoring recipe for the Deathchill Cloak.$B$BThis cloak is a tradeable Epic cloak for spellcasters that grants Spellpower, Haste and Critical Strike.   I am looking for someone worthy to teach this recipe to.$B$BSomeone who had completed most of the quests across Northrend and had the "Loremaster of Northrend" achievement would be worthy of learning the recipe for the Deathchill Cloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是一位颇为出色的裁缝，因此我可以教你一些特别的图样，比如精魂披风和死寒披风。' WHERE entry=14076; /* Text0_0: Since you are a tailor of some skill, I can tell you that I know some special recipes.   I know recipes for both the Wispcloak and the Deathchill Cloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友。我能为你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14087; /* Text0_0: Greetings, friend.  Something I can do for ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，等一等。你没有属于自己的飞行坐骑诶。$B$B如果出行不便的话，恐怕你没有办法帮助其他的地精了。他们付钱给我，让我将旧坐骑借给你这样的人使用——免费使用哦。$B$B怎么样？' WHERE entry=14088; /* Text0_0: Hey there, hold on just one second.  I see you\'re not riding a flying mount of your own.$B$BYou probably won\'t be of much use to the other goblins here if you can\'t get around.  They\'ve paid me to loan my used mounts to people such as yourself -- at no cost to you.$B$BInterested? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经找到了诺甘农钥石的线索，有了它就能进入奥杜尔的档案室；但是泰坦将钥石分成了两块并分别藏了起来。$B$B钥石的外壳藏在北部海滩的创世者图书馆里，就在奥杜尔以南。首先，你要从图书馆守护者那里获得访问磁盘的碎片。' WHERE entry=14089; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got a lead on Norgannon\'s keystone, which guards access to Ulduar\'s archives, but the Titans divided it into two pieces and secreted them away.$B$BOne of the pieces, the keystone\'s shell, is held within the Inventor\'s Library on the northern coast, south of Ulduar itself. The first thing you\'ll need to do is retrieve the fragments of an access disk from the library\'s guardians. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='说到财宝，永远不要轻视翻捡别人的垃圾的行为。偷来的财宝更加珍贵，是吗？但是免费的东西就是好的，无论你采用什么方式！',Text0_1_loc4='说到财宝，永远不要轻视翻捡别人的垃圾的行为。偷来的财宝更加珍贵，是吗？但是免费的东西就是好的，无论你采用什么方式！',Text1_0_loc4='人们经常置疑我身为三指大盗的本事。其实我靠的是手腕的灵活性……一旦失手，你应该立即制服他们，这同样要依赖手腕的力量。$B$B灵巧的双手比稳定的收入更加宝贵，你明白吗？' WHERE entry=14090; /* Text0_0: When it comes to treasure, never be lookin\' sideways at lootin\' someone else\'s junk. Stolen goods be much sweeter, ya? But free is free, no matta how it got that way! */ /* Text0_1: When it comes to treasure, never be lookin\' sideways at lootin\' someone else\'s junk. Stolen goods be much sweeter, ya? But free is free, no matta how it got that way! */ /* Text1_0: I always be up for a nice three-finger discount. Stealin\' be all in the wrist... and when that fails ya, then ya stick somethin\' sharp in between the ribs, and that\'s all in the wrist too.$B$BSkilled hands be worth more than a steady paycheck, ya heard? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我一点都不担心巫妖王。我见过无数的大人物沉沉浮浮，他们喜欢把事情搞得一团糟。但是每当人民站起来反抗时，他们很快就会偃旗息鼓，沦为历史课本上的教程。巫妖王也不会例外。' WHERE entry=14090; /* Text2_0: I don\'t be worryin\' \'bout no Lich Kings. Seen a lotta big-shots come and go, dey always messin\' somethin\' up. It ain\'t long aftah that when a posse rolls on through and sends dem quick on dey way to da history books. Dis one ain\'t no different. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来帮忙的吗？' WHERE entry=14115; /* Text0_0: Come to make yourself useful? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='地精工程学的奥秘是，教你学会如何让爆炸物在指定的地点按时引爆，而不是确保产品不会爆炸。' WHERE entry=14118; /* Text0_0: The secret to goblin engineering has nothing to do with keeping things from exploding. It has everything to do with directing the explosions exactly where you want them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是见证者夏拉托尔。',Text1_0_loc4='你愿意听我讲个故事吗？' WHERE entry=14119; /* Text0_0: I am Xarantaur, the Witness. */ /* Text1_0: Would you like to hear a story? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='故事？',Text3_0_loc4='嗯，我读到过你的故事，$n。' WHERE entry=14119; /* Text2_0: Do you have a story for me? */ /* Text3_0: Ah yes, I have read of you, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是最早一批，也是最后一代接受过塞纳留斯教诲的牛头人德鲁伊之一。那时候世界还很年轻，没有燃烧军团，大灾变也还没有发生。一切都是那么宁静。$B$B当我的同胞学习猎杀巨兽时，我却在搜寻历史故事。对知识的渴求令我沉湎于德鲁伊的魔法。有段时间，我满足于与树木、岩石和野兽交谈，倾听它们的故事。$B$B后来，塞纳留斯不再露面，我的同胞渐渐遗忘了他的教诲，但是我忘不了，我还想了解更多关于这个世界的知识。$B$B于是我告别族人，离开家乡去远方流浪。' WHERE entry=14120; /* Text0_0: I was one of the first tauren druids, of the last generation taught by Shan\'do Cenarius, before the Legion, before the Sundering, when the world was still young. Before everything changed.$B$BWhile my brethren hunted great beasts, I hunted stories. I had been drawn to the druidic arts by this hunger, this lust for knowledge. For a time, that hunger was sated as I learned to talk to the trees, rocks, and beasts, and heard their stories.$B$BBut then, the time came when Cenarius walked among us no more and my brethren began to forget what he had taught us. I could not forget, though, and I still needed to learn more about our world.$B$BSo I said my farewells and travelled beyond the lands of my people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14126; /* Text0_0: How may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text1_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text1_1_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14128; /* Text0_0: How may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: How may I help you? */ /* Text1_0: How may I help you? */ /* Text1_1: How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text2_1_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14128; /* Text2_0: How may I help you? */ /* Text2_1: How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有什么要修理的吗，$r？' WHERE entry=14134; /* Text0_0: Got somethin\' that needs tightening, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们已经损失了好几名优秀的同胞。我开始怀疑，这里是否值得我们如此关注。',Text0_1_loc4='我们已经损失了好几名优秀的同胞。我开始怀疑，这里是否值得我们如此关注。' WHERE entry=14137; /* Text0_0: We\'ve lost a few good people up here already. I\'m beginning to doubt that this place is worth our attention. */ /* Text0_1: We\'ve lost a few good people up here already. I\'m beginning to doubt that this place is worth our attention. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='最后的决战即将开始，$n。保持警惕！' WHERE entry=14142; /* Text0_0: The final battle will begin soon, $N. Stand at attention! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你，龙族的朋友和盟友。请在大厅好好休息吧。' WHERE entry=14149; /* Text0_0: You are welcome here, friend and ally of the Dragonflights. Take your rest here in our halls. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，是你，$n！欢迎来到我们的圣殿。在这里好好休息一下，这是你应得的权利。' WHERE entry=14150; /* Text0_0: Ah, it\'s you, $N! Welcome into our sanctuary. Rest and refresh yourself; you have more than earned it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，繁忙的航程是吧？在返回战场之前，你最好先喘口气。',Text0_1_loc4='$n，繁忙的航程是吧？在返回战场之前，你最好先喘口气。' WHERE entry=14155; /* Text0_0: It\'s been a busy day in the air, eh $N?  Maybe you should take a moment to catch your breath before going back out. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s been a busy day in the air, eh $N?  Maybe you should take a moment to catch your breath before going back out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当心，$n。你的教徒长袍呢？' WHERE entry=14159; /* Text0_0: Careful, $N.  Where are your cultist robes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='给。准备好了吗？一旦我们开始行动，就不能回头了。' WHERE entry=14160; /* Text0_0: There you are.  Are you ready then?  Once we start, there is no turning back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你敢于进入玛里苟斯的王国，面对他手下的精英侍卫吗，$r？',Text0_1_loc4='你敢于进入玛里苟斯的王国，面对他手下的精英侍卫吗，$r？' WHERE entry=14169; /* Text0_0: Do you possess the courage to face Malygos\' elite drakes in their own realm, $r? */ /* Text0_1: Do you possess the courage to face Malygos\' elite drakes in their own realm, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对不起，朋友。只有联盟的军官才有权购买载具。',Text0_1_loc4='对不起，朋友。只有联盟的军官才有权购买载具。' WHERE entry=14172; /* Text0_0: Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Alliance can authorize the purchase of a vehicle. */ /* Text0_1: Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Alliance can authorize the purchase of a vehicle. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的风景是不是很漂亮啊？你能看到潜在的利益吗？',Text1_0_loc4='黑暗主宰西塔利克斯从东南方冲进了瓦哈拉斯！' WHERE entry=14177; /* Text0_0: Isn\'t it just beautiful? Can you see the potential profit? */ /* Text1_0: Khit\'rix the Dark Master skitters into Valhalas from the southeast! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，小$r。' WHERE entry=14179; /* Text0_0: Hello, little $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='即使东西没有损坏，也不代表你不能鼓捣它。你想要什么，亲爱的？',Text0_1_loc4='即使东西没有损坏，也不代表你不能鼓捣它。你想要什么，亲爱的？' WHERE entry=14180; /* Text0_0: Just because something isn\'t broke doesn\'t mean you can\'t fix it.  You lookin\' for something, sweety? */ /* Text0_1: Just because something isn\'t broke doesn\'t mean you can\'t fix it.  You lookin\' for something, sweety? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='D16限时炸弹分配器发出轰鸣声。' WHERE entry=14182; /* Text0_0: The U.D.E.D. dispenser rumbles at you expectantly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='翡翠梦境已然危机四伏。许多勇士放弃了艾泽拉斯的生活，试图拯救翡翠梦境。我越来越担心他们的安危了。' WHERE entry=14198; /* Text0_0: The Emerald Dream has become a dangerous place. I grow increasingly concerned for those who have sacrificed their waking life in Azeroth in hopes of saving it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='快点，$c。' WHERE entry=14204; /* Text0_0: Make it quick, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有事吗，小家伙？' WHERE entry=14209; /* Text0_0: Yes, little one? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='炼金房的铭文训练师身旁有一本巨大的，闪闪发光的魔法书，能够帮助你制作强化法术和技能的铭文。',Text0_1_loc4='炼金房的铭文训练师身旁有一本巨大的，闪闪发光的魔法书，能够帮助你制作强化法术和技能的铭文。' WHERE entry=14213; /* Text0_0: Big, sparkly, magic book help make Glyphs for spells and abilities. Always find near inscription trainer, in The Apothecarium. */ /* Text0_1: Big, sparkly, magic book help make Glyphs for spells and abilities. Always find near inscription trainer, in The Apothecarium. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='快一点，$r。我很疲倦，没功夫开玩笑……',Text0_1_loc4='快一点，$r。我很疲倦，没功夫开玩笑……' WHERE entry=14215; /* Text0_0: Make it quick, $r. I am weary and have no time for pleasantries.. */ /* Text0_1: Make it quick, $r. I am weary and have no time for pleasantries.. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来了！' WHERE entry=14218; /* Text0_0: There you are! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，复活节。看到人们放下尊严，四处搜寻彩蛋，真是有趣啊。显然，这些彩蛋拥有某种特殊的魔力……',Text0_1_loc4='啊，复活节。看到人们放下尊严，四处搜寻彩蛋，真是有趣啊。显然，这些彩蛋拥有某种特殊的魔力……' WHERE entry=14227; /* Text0_0: Ah, Noblegarden. So amusing to watch others throw away their dignity in favor of hunting colored eggs. Still, they do have a curious magical aura to them... */ /* Text0_1: Ah, Noblegarden. So amusing to watch others throw away their dignity in favor of hunting colored eggs. Still, they do have a curious magical aura to them... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='糖果！这正是我想要的；希望我不用为了找糖果而东奔西跑！',Text0_1_loc4='糖果！这正是我想要的；希望我不用为了找糖果而东奔西跑！' WHERE entry=14229; /* Text0_0: Candy! That\'s what I\'m talking about; I just wish I didn\'t have to run around finding it! */ /* Text0_1: Candy! That\'s what I\'m talking about; I just wish I didn\'t have to run around finding it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，如果人们乐意四处奔走，在土堆里寻找彩蛋，我有什么好说的呀？反正我能从绘制彩蛋上赚到一笔，而且今年我还投资了养鸡场。',Text0_1_loc4='嘿，如果人们乐意四处奔走，在土堆里寻找彩蛋，我有什么好说的呀？反正我能从绘制彩蛋上赚到一笔，而且今年我还投资了养鸡场。' WHERE entry=14231; /* Text0_0: Hey, if people want to run around rooting in the dirt for colored eggs, who am I to judge? I still get a cut of the profits on paint, and I invested in chickens this year. */ /* Text0_1: Hey, if people want to run around rooting in the dirt for colored eggs, who am I to judge? I still get a cut of the profits on paint, and I invested in chickens this year. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们会在复活节期间庆祝春天的到来。赞美生命和一切美好的事物。',Text0_1_loc4='我们会在复活节期间庆祝春天的到来。赞美生命和一切美好的事物。' WHERE entry=14234; /* Text0_0: We\'re celebrating spring during Noblegarden. Affirmation of life and all that. */ /* Text0_1: We\'re celebrating spring during Noblegarden. Affirmation of life and all that. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，朋友，眼下正是为生命和春天欢呼的日子。你已经收集到了不少彩蛋吧？',Text0_1_loc4='嘿，朋友，眼下正是为生命和春天欢呼的日子。你已经收集到了不少彩蛋吧？' WHERE entry=14236; /* Text0_0: Yah, mon, this be the time to be glad of life and spring. Ya collect lots of eggs yet? */ /* Text0_1: Yah, mon, this be the time to be glad of life and spring. Ya collect lots of eggs yet? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个节日根本毫无意义。彩蛋和所谓“生命的礼赞”，我呸。',Text0_1_loc4='这个节日根本毫无意义。彩蛋和所谓“生命的礼赞”，我呸。' WHERE entry=14237; /* Text0_0: This entire holiday is nonsensical. Colored eggs and "life affirmation," bah. */ /* Text0_1: This entire holiday is nonsensical. Colored eggs and "life affirmation," bah. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B一旦联盟取得冬拥堡垒的控制权，我就将为想要前往那里的旅行者开启一道传送门。$B$B战斗正在进行中，赶快前往冬拥湖，支援我们的部队吧！',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B一旦联盟取得冬拥堡垒的控制权，我就将为想要前往那里的旅行者开启一道传送门。$B$B战斗正在进行中，赶快前往冬拥湖，支援我们的部队吧！' WHERE entry=14240; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BWhen the Alliance controls Wintergrasp Fortress, I will open a portal for those who wish to travel there.$B$BThe battle currently enues. Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BWhen the Alliance controls Wintergrasp Fortress, I will open a portal for those who wish to travel there.$B$BThe battle currently enues. Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B一旦部落取得冬拥堡垒的控制权，我就将为想要前往那里的旅行者开启一道传送门。$B$B战斗正在进行中，赶快前往冬拥湖，支援我们的部队吧。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B一旦部落取得冬拥堡垒的控制权，我就将为想要前往那里的旅行者开启一道传送门。$B$B战斗正在进行中，赶快前往冬拥湖，支援我们的部队吧。' WHERE entry=14241; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BWhen the Horde controls Wintergrasp Fortress, I will open a portal for those who wish to travel there.$B$BThe battle currently ensues. Hurry to Wintergrasp to support our forces. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BWhen the Horde controls Wintergrasp Fortress, I will open a portal for those who wish to travel there.$B$BThe battle currently ensues. Hurry to Wintergrasp to support our forces. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们的新盟友牦牛人的帮助下，部落一定会取得诺森德的统治权。' WHERE entry=14245; /* Text0_0: With the help of our new taunka allies, the Northrend will belong to the Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊，$c！欢迎乘坐吻云号。诺森德的环境非常恶劣，希望你已经做好了准备。',Text0_1_loc4='你好啊，$c！欢迎乘坐吻云号。诺森德的环境非常恶劣，希望你已经做好了准备。' WHERE entry=14248; /* Text0_0: Greetings $c!  Welcome aboard the Cloudkisser.  Northrend can be a very harsh place.  I hope you have prepared yourself. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings $c!  Welcome aboard the Cloudkisser.  Northrend can be a very harsh place.  I hope you have prepared yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，那么你应该去找本尼克·螺剪。他就在矮人区中心的铁匠铺。',Text0_1_loc4='哦，那么你应该去找本尼克·螺剪。他就在矮人区中心的铁匠铺。' WHERE entry=14249; /* Text0_0: You\'ll be after Benik Boltshear, then. He\'s located in the heart of the Dwarven District by the blacksmiths. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll be after Benik Boltshear, then. He\'s located in the heart of the Dwarven District by the blacksmiths. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='维斯派塔斯的角鹰兽会带你迅速抵达目的地。',Text0_1_loc4='维斯派塔斯的角鹰兽会带你迅速抵达目的地。',Text1_0_loc4='维斯派塔斯的角鹰兽会带你迅速抵达目的地。',Text1_1_loc4='维斯派塔斯的角鹰兽会带你迅速抵达目的地。' WHERE entry=14254; /* Text0_0: Vesprystus\' hippogryphs will bear you swiftly to your destination. */ /* Text0_1: Vesprystus\' hippogryphs will bear you swiftly to your destination. */ /* Text1_0: It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil. */ /* Text1_1: It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在目睹了瘟疫之地的凄惨和圣光之愿礼拜堂的血战之后，我以为再也看不到比那些更加恐怖的东西了。$B$B但是我错了。',Text0_1_loc4='在目睹了瘟疫之地的凄惨和圣光之愿礼拜堂的血战之后，我以为再也看不到比那些更加恐怖的东西了。$B$B但是我错了。' WHERE entry=14286; /* Text0_0: After the Plaguelands and the Battle for Light\'s Hope Chapel, I didn\'t think that we would witness anything more horrible.$B$BI was wrong. */ /* Text0_1: After the Plaguelands and the Battle for Light\'s Hope Chapel, I didn\'t think that we would witness anything more horrible.$B$BI was wrong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='掘地鼠炖肉美味极了。' WHERE entry=14313; /* Text0_0: Dig rats make some surprisingly tasty stew. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你，$g先生:女士;。这片营地比我待过的上一个营地要好多了。$B$B很荣幸，我能够和一群出色的战友共事，他们教会了我不少战斗技巧。现在我已经能独立与部落作战了。' WHERE entry=14315; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $g sir : my lady;. This is a much better camp than the one that I used to have.$B$BIt\'s good to have company. They\'ve been nice enough to teach me some of their fighting techniques so that I can hold my own against the Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还以为我永远都没有办法摆脱那个可怕的诅咒了。陌生人，谢谢你。',Text0_1_loc4='我还以为我永远都没有办法摆脱那个可怕的诅咒了。陌生人，谢谢你。' WHERE entry=14319; /* Text0_0: I thought I\'d never be free from that terrible curse. You have my gratitude, stranger. */ /* Text0_1: I thought I\'d never be free from that terrible curse. You have my gratitude, stranger. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='收下它吧。再次感谢你，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='收下它吧。再次感谢你，$c。' WHERE entry=14320; /* Text0_0: Take it with my gratitude, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Take it with my gratitude, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$G先生:女士;，我能为您做什么？' WHERE entry=14324; /* Text0_0: What may I do for you, $GSir:Dame;? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你们确定要借助我的力量去跟尤格-萨隆作战吗？' WHERE entry=14325; /* Text0_0: Are you certain you want my help in the battle against Yogg-Saron? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些该死的害虫!',Text0_1_loc4='这些该死的害虫!' WHERE entry=14330; /* Text0_0: Missing US text */ /* Text0_1: Missing US text */
