UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是什么，$c？' WHERE entry=14344; /* Text0_0: What is it, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天哪，我从来没有想过能亲眼目睹泰坦之城奥杜尔。当布莱恩恳求我资助这支探险队时，我怎么能忍心拒绝呢？！' WHERE entry=14362; /* Text0_0: My, my, I never thought I would have the chance to see Ulduar myself. Why, when Brann asked me to help fund this expedition, how could I refuse?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还以为我们没法逃出那片雾蒙蒙的丛林呢！现在，我是这支探险队的首席工程师啦。' WHERE entry=14363; /* Text0_0: I never thought we\'d escape from that steamy jungle! Now I\'m the lead engineer of this expedition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些宝贝儿看上去跟废铁似的，但是它们可以高速前进，猛烈地撞击敌人。器械前端的撞锤加载了可以施放电能震击的高压电容器。$B$B就连炮塔也升级成了防空火箭，使它比那些破烂攻城车更具优势。',Text0_1_loc4='这些宝贝儿看上去跟废铁似的，但是它们可以高速前进，猛烈地撞击敌人。器械前端的撞锤加载了可以施放电能震击的高压电容器。$B$B就连炮塔也升级成了防空火箭，使它比那些破烂攻城车更具优势。' WHERE entry=14364; /* Text0_0: These babies may look like scrap, but they can rush ahead, knocking enemies aside. The front ram has been overloaded with a electroscopic hyper capacitor, letting it discharge electrical blasts. $B$BEven the turret has been upgraded with anti-air rockets, providing it with a definitive edge over those blasted demolishers. */ /* Text0_1: These babies may look like scrap, but they can rush ahead, knocking enemies aside. The front ram has been overloaded with a electroscopic hyper capacitor, letting it discharge electrical blasts. $B$BEven the turret has been upgraded with anti-air rockets, providing it with a definitive edge over those blasted demolishers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老大，我能为你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14372; /* Text0_0: Something I can do for you, Boss? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。' WHERE entry=14375; /* Text0_0: Greetings. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='控制台显得非常陈旧，却没有一丝破损或是荒废的迹象。上面刻有一道插槽，似乎可以放入大型的圆盘。' WHERE entry=14383; /* Text0_0: The console appears ancient though there is no sign of dilapidation or decay.  A single slot appears to fit large circular discs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等我们以银月城的名义赢下这场锦标赛时，荣耀将属于我们。',Text0_1_loc4='等我们以银月城的名义赢下这场锦标赛时，荣耀将属于我们。' WHERE entry=14392; /* Text0_0: Glory will be ours when we win this tournament in the name of Silvermoon. */ /* Text0_1: Glory will be ours when we win this tournament in the name of Silvermoon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='麦格尼国王希望我们赢得锦标赛的胜利。我们绝不能失败。',Text0_1_loc4='麦格尼国王希望我们赢得锦标赛的胜利。我们绝不能失败。' WHERE entry=14396; /* Text0_0: King Magni expects us to win the tournament and make him proud. We will not fail. */ /* Text0_1: King Magni expects us to win the tournament and make him proud. We will not fail. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='锦标赛开始后，所有人都将见证被遗忘者的胜利。' WHERE entry=14402; /* Text0_0: When the tournament starts, all will see the Forsaken emerge triumphant. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='竞争会非常激烈，但是奥格瑞玛的勇士是所向披靡的。' WHERE entry=14403; /* Text0_0: The competition will be fierce, but Orgrimmar\'s champions will decimate all who stand in our way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们不仅为荣耀而战，还要为我们的先祖和人民赢得光荣。' WHERE entry=14404; /* Text0_0: We compete not only for glory, but to bring honor to our ancestors and to our people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗矛氏族已经做好了竞争的准备。' WHERE entry=14405; /* Text0_0: The Darkspears stand ready to face the competition and the enemy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你准备好参加勇士的晋级测试后，我会召来一位银色北伐军的成员。',Text0_1_loc4='当你准备好参加勇士的晋级测试后，我会召来一位银色北伐军的成员。' WHERE entry=14408; /* Text0_0: When you are ready to test for the rank of valiant, I will call forth a member of the Argent Crusade. */ /* Text0_1: When you are ready to test for the rank of valiant, I will call forth a member of the Argent Crusade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高墙内的秘密远远超越了我们的想象。' WHERE entry=14420; /* Text0_0: There are secrets contained within these halls that are beyond our wildest dreams. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能协助布莱恩探索泰坦古城奥杜尔的秘密真是莫大的荣幸。' WHERE entry=14428; /* Text0_0: It\'s a real honor to be able to aid Brann in exploring ancient Ulduar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我所知道的关于探险的知识，都是布莱恩教给我的。',Text0_1_loc4='我所知道的关于探险的知识，都是布莱恩教给我的。' WHERE entry=14429; /* Text0_0: Brann taught me everything I know about exploring. */ /* Text0_1: Brann taught me everything I know about exploring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，很高兴见到你。$B$B我负责向候选者传授骑乘近身战的诀窍。' WHERE entry=14431; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.$B$BI train Aspirants in the art of mounted close combat. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='近战目标可以帮助候选者训练骑乘攻击与防御的技巧。$B$B你需要靠近并刺击近战目标。刺击的力量通常会令目标旋转起来，对你或你的坐骑造成伤害。因此，你需要巧妙地利用防御技能。$B$B在攻击目标之前，最好确保自己至少有一层防御效果。在接下来的战斗中，你还需要尽可能地堆叠并刷新防御效果。否则，你很快就会被打下坐骑。$B$B在骑乘实战中遵循着同样的原则：在攻击与防御之间寻求平衡，一有机会就发动刺击，并尽可能保持多层防御效果。' WHERE entry=14434; /* Text0_0: The Melee Target trains Aspirants in both mounted attack and defense.$B$BApproach the Melee Target and strike it with a Thrust attack. The force of the blow often spins the target hard enough to injure you or your mount. This is where defense comes into play.$B$BBe certain to have at least one layer of Defend before attacking the target, and continue to stack and refresh Defend throughout the training exercise. Otherwise, you may well find yourself dismounted.$B$BThe same holds true in actual mounted combat: Balance attack and defense, Thrusting at every opportunity and maintaining your layers of Defend as best you can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，你好！$B$B你是来学习冲锋技巧的吗，$c？' WHERE entry=14436; /* Text0_0: Hey there, how are ye?$B$BCome ta learn the art o\' the Charge, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧！骑乘冲锋可不仅仅是让你的坐骑高速冲刺，体验那种心飙到嗓子眼的快感……当然这的确是最有趣的部分，嘿嘿！但是冲锋目标可以帮助你掌握更多诀窍。$B$B冲锋的关键在于距离与时机。不能靠得太近，否则无法全力提速。也不能离得太远，否则坐骑就会进入疲惫状态！至于冲锋的时机……$B$B在冲锋之前，你最好确认一下冲锋目标身上是否有防御效果。如果有，你应该先使用碎盾然后再冲锋！$B$B实战中遵循着同样的原则：在冲锋前要尽可能地削弱对手的防御效果！' WHERE entry=14437; /* Text0_0: Well then! A mounted Charge is about more than just kickin\' yer mount ta full speed an\' hollerin\' yer lungs out... though that IS the fun part, heh! But the Charge Target will teach ye the finer points.$B$BA good Charge is all about distance and timing. Ye can\'t be TOO close, or ye won\'t get enough speed. But ye can\'t be too far away either or yer mount will tire! As for timin\'...$B$BYe\'ll want ta make sure the Charge Target doesn\'t have a layer o\' Defend up before ye rush in. If it does, use yer Shield Breaker ta make it vulnerable, and THEN Charge in!$B$BSame goes for the real thing: Try ta drop yer opponent defenses before ye Charge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀。又一位$c，你是来学习碎盾的技巧的吗……？' WHERE entry=14438; /* Text0_0: Well. Another $c, come to learn the ways of the Shield-Breaker...? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='远程碎盾攻击上手容易精通难。碎盾攻击所能造成的伤害不高，但是配合刺击和冲锋使用就能发挥出完美的效果，令你在骑乘作战中所向披靡。$B$B选定一个远程目标，估算一下碎盾攻击的射程……你需要多远的距离以及你能将长枪掷多远。$B$B接下来，就开始投掷长枪吧，直到你破坏目标身上的所有防御效果。$B$B骑乘实战中遵循着同样的原则：彻底粉碎对手的防御……然后狠狠地揍他们！' WHERE entry=14439; /* Text0_0: The ranged Shield-Breaker attack is simple to learn, but difficult to master. Alone it may seem weak, but in conjunction with Thrusts and Charges the Shield-Breaker makes a successful jouster.$B$BFind a Ranged Target. Take a moment to understand the Shield-Breaker\'s range... how much space you need, and how far you can hurl the lance.$B$BAfter that? Well. Start throwing, and do not stop until you\'ve broken every last layer of Defend and pierced the vulnerable target.$B$BThis tactic will serve you well in actual mounted combat: Break down your opponents\' defenses... and then crush them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，你来得正是时候。很快我就会给你安排更多的任务了……' WHERE entry=14441; /* Text0_0: All in good time, mon. I be havin\' more work for you to do soon.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看出来了。荒芜水晶的储量大增，很快就能满足需求了。' WHERE entry=14442; /* Text0_0: Indeed you have, mon. Our stores of blight crystals be nearly sufficient! */
