UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节。嗯，我明白这些牛头人都渴望着向部落酋长表达他们的感激和情谊。但亡灵呢？$B$B我还以为他们早就丢弃了这种多愁善感的传统。',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节。嗯，我明白这些牛头人都渴望着向部落酋长表达他们的感激和情谊。但亡灵呢？$B$B我还以为他们早就丢弃了这种多愁善感的传统。' WHERE entry=14635; /* Text0_0: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty." Hrm. I can understand the tauren\'s eagerness to express their sense of gratitude and comraderie to the Horde\'s warchief, but the Forsaken?$B$BI imagined they would have dropped such sentimental traditions long ago. */ /* Text0_1: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty." Hrm. I can understand the tauren\'s eagerness to express their sense of gratitude and comraderie to the Horde\'s warchief, but the Forsaken?$B$BI imagined they would have dropped such sentimental traditions long ago. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有高贵的朋友们都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有高贵的朋友们都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。' WHERE entry=14640; /* Text0_0: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe hope that all of our noble allies will join us in feasting and celebration. */ /* Text0_1: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe hope that all of our noble allies will join us in feasting and celebration. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这样的节日和人类的风格实在是有着巨大的反差。有谁会想到，贪婪无情的人类竟然会举办一个表达赠与和分享的节日？$B$B我很高兴看到这样欢乐的景象。达纳苏斯会不遗余力地支持这一活动。',Text0_1_loc4='这样的节日和人类的风格实在是有着巨大的反差。有谁会想到，贪婪无情的人类竟然会举办一个表达赠与和分享的节日？$B$B我很高兴看到这样欢乐的景象。达纳苏斯会不遗余力地支持这一活动。' WHERE entry=14641; /* Text0_0: Such a stark contrast, this holiday, to typical human behavior. Who\'d have thought such a relentlessly voracious people would make a celebration of giving and sharing?$B$BIt\'s pleasant to see. Darnassus should do its utmost to support and encourage it. */ /* Text0_1: Such a stark contrast, this holiday, to typical human behavior. Who\'d have thought such a relentlessly voracious people would make a celebration of giving and sharing?$B$BIt\'s pleasant to see. Darnassus should do its utmost to support and encourage it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一张盛宴餐桌上放着五种感恩节美食。每一份都放在一把座椅前面。$B$B坐进这些椅子里，你就能随心所欲地大吃面前的美食，并将这些美食传递给其它椅子中的朋友。能够和朋友共享的快乐才是真正的快乐！$B$B如果你吃足任何一种食物，你就能从这种食物中获得独特的好处。$B$B另外，如果你将每种食物都吃得足够多，你就能得到分享之魂！',Text0_1_loc4='一张盛宴餐桌上放着五种感恩节美食。每一份都放在一把座椅前面。$B$B坐进这些椅子里，你就能随心所欲地大吃面前的美食，并将这些美食传递给其它椅子中的朋友。能够和朋友共享的快乐才是真正的快乐！$B$B如果你吃足任何一种食物，你就能从这种食物中获得独特的好处。$B$B另外，如果你将每种食物都吃得足够多，你就能得到分享之魂！' WHERE entry=14647; /* Text0_0: A Bountiful Table is laid out with five Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, one in front of each chair.$B$BWhile in a chair, you may eat as much of that food as you like, as well as pass servings of that food to the other chairs. Feast and share with friends!$B$BIf you eat enough of any one food, you\'ll gain benefits unique to that food.$B$BIn addition, if you eat enough of every food, you\'ll gain the Spirit of Sharing! */ /* Text0_1: A Bountiful Table is laid out with five Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, one in front of each chair.$B$BWhile in a chair, you may eat as much of that food as you like, as well as pass servings of that food to the other chairs. Feast and share with friends!$B$BIf you eat enough of any one food, you\'ll gain benefits unique to that food.$B$BIn addition, if you eat enough of every food, you\'ll gain the Spirit of Sharing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一张盛宴餐桌上放着五种感恩节美食。每一份都放在一把座椅前面。$B$B坐进这些椅子里，你就能随心所欲地大吃面前的美食，并将这些美食传递给其它椅子中的朋友。能够和朋友共享的快乐才是真正的快乐！$B$B如果你吃足任何一种食物，你就能从这种食物中获得独特的好处。$B$B另外，如果你将每种食物都吃得足够多，你就能得到分享之魂！',Text0_1_loc4='一张盛宴餐桌上放着五种感恩节美食。每一份都放在一把座椅前面。$B$B坐进这些椅子里，你就能随心所欲地大吃面前的美食，并将这些美食传递给其它椅子中的朋友。能够和朋友共享的快乐才是真正的快乐！$B$B如果你吃足任何一种食物，你就能从这种食物中获得独特的好处。$B$B另外，如果你将每种食物都吃得足够多，你就能得到分享之魂！' WHERE entry=14648; /* Text0_0: A Bountiful Table is laid out with five Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, one in front of each chair.$B$BWhile in a chair, you may eat as much of that food as you like, as well as pass servings of that food to the other chairs. Feast and share with friends!$B$BIf you eat enough of any one food, you\'ll gain benefits unique to that food.$B$BIn addition, if you eat enough of every food, you\'ll gain the Spirit of Sharing! */ /* Text0_1: A Bountiful Table is laid out with five Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, one in front of each chair.$B$BWhile in a chair, you may eat as much of that food as you like, as well as pass servings of that food to the other chairs. Feast and share with friends!$B$BIf you eat enough of any one food, you\'ll gain benefits unique to that food.$B$BIn addition, if you eat enough of every food, you\'ll gain the Spirit of Sharing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有些奖励只会赠予那些赢得了银色北伐军及其盟友的崇拜，获得了十字军头衔的战士。$B$B提里奥亲自授命令我寻找这样的英雄，并赐予他们应得的奖章。',Text0_1_loc4='有些奖励只会赠予那些赢得了银色北伐军及其盟友的崇拜，获得了十字军头衔的战士。$B$B提里奥亲自授命令我寻找这样的英雄，并赐予他们应得的奖章。' WHERE entry=14661; /* Text0_0: There are some rewards fit only for those who have attained the title of Crusader, exalted in the eyes of the Argent Crusade as well as all their allied peoples.$B$BTirion himself has charged me with the finding of such heroes and bestowing upon them the proper decorations. */ /* Text0_1: There are some rewards fit only for those who have attained the title of Crusader, exalted in the eyes of the Argent Crusade as well as all their allied peoples.$B$BTirion himself has charged me with the finding of such heroes and bestowing upon them the proper decorations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些猛兽实在是令人惊愕。被他们打败绝不是什么羞耻的事情。' WHERE entry=14667; /* Text0_0: Those beasts are amazing specimens. You should feel no shame at being bested by them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你干得真漂亮！等你再次准备好以后，就立刻通知我。' WHERE entry=14668; /* Text0_0: Excellent! Let me know when you are ready for the next attempt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='征服之岛上有许多非常重要的物资，我们绝不能让它落入部落的手中。你愿意加入我们的战斗吗？',Text0_1_loc4='征服之岛上有许多非常重要的物资，我们绝不能让它落入部落的手中。你愿意加入我们的战斗吗？' WHERE entry=14670; /* Text0_0: The Isle of Conquest is laden with valuable resources we cannot allow to fall into Horde hands. Will you join the fight? */ /* Text0_1: The Isle of Conquest is laden with valuable resources we cannot allow to fall into Horde hands. Will you join the fight? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='征服之岛上有许多非常重要的物资，我们绝不能让它落入联盟的手中。你愿意加入我们的战斗吗？',Text0_1_loc4='征服之岛上有许多非常重要的物资，我们绝不能让它落入联盟的手中。你愿意加入我们的战斗吗？' WHERE entry=14671; /* Text0_0: The Isle of Conquest is laden with valuable resources we cannot allow to fall into Alliance hands. Will you join the fight? */ /* Text0_1: The Isle of Conquest is laden with valuable resources we cannot allow to fall into Alliance hands. Will you join the fight? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是否已经准备好了为部落而战，$c？',Text0_1_loc4='你是否已经准备好了为部落而战，$c？' WHERE entry=14674; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to fight for the Horde, $c? */ /* Text0_1: Are you ready to fight for the Horde, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是否已经准备好了为联盟而战，$c？',Text0_1_loc4='你是否已经准备好了为联盟而战，$c？' WHERE entry=14675; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to fight for the Alliance, $c? */ /* Text0_1: Are you ready to fight for the Alliance, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好！你竟然打败了所有这些猛兽，这简直太神奇了！不过，我听说下一个挑战将更加艰难！' WHERE entry=14678; /* Text0_0: Well done! Your fighting against all those beasts was splendid! I hear the next challenge should be even tougher! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在我们暂时压制住了加拉克苏斯大王，但我们不可能压制住他太长时间。' WHERE entry=14679; /* Text0_0: We\'re holding Lord Jaraxxus back for now, but we can\'t keep him bound for much longer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='敌人将有多么强大，你很快就会知道了。现在，你是否已经准备好了迎接下一场挑战？' WHERE entry=14680; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find out soon enough. Are you ready for the next challenge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这太好了，一定及时给我信号，让我知道该在什么时候放下那些法术。' WHERE entry=14682; /* Text0_0: That\'s great, just give me the signal for when to drop the binding spells. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多年以来，我一直在这个被世界遗忘的角落里工作着，查看这里的地形，在无聊中打发时间。但我的时代终会到来的。奥格瑞玛正将全部力量转向艾萨拉，我们打开了通往灰谷的通道，并终将统治这片大陆。欢迎来到前线，$c。' WHERE entry=14690; /* Text0_0: For years I served in this backwater corner of the world, learning the terrain and biding my time. At last our time has come. The full might of Orgrimmar is now turned to Azshara, our gateway to Ashenvale and dominance over this continent. Welcome to the front lines, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到我的店铺。我们这里有你所需要的一切……如果你所需要的是炼金术材料……',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到我的店铺。我们这里有你所需要的一切……如果你所需要的是炼金术材料……' WHERE entry=14712; /* Text0_0: Welcome to our shop.  We have everything you need... if you need alchemy supplies. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to our shop.  We have everything you need... if you need alchemy supplies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不，我的脑子很不错，最好不要小看我。我能够用洗碗水和蒲公英配制出治疗药剂。不过这不是我要给你的东西！$b$b不管怎样，如果你想要买东西，就请和Patricia谈谈吧。',Text0_1_loc4='不，我的脑子很不错，最好不要小看我。我能够用洗碗水和蒲公英配制出治疗药剂。不过这不是我要给你的东西！$b$b不管怎样，如果你想要买东西，就请和Patricia谈谈吧。' WHERE entry=14713; /* Text0_0: No, I\'m the intellectual one, and I am not to be taken lightly.  I could brew a healing potion from dishwater and dandelions, although that\'s not something I\'ll show you!$b$bAnyhow, if you\'d like to make a purchase, please speak with Patricia. */ /* Text0_1: No, I\'m the intellectual one, and I am not to be taken lightly.  I could brew a healing potion from dishwater and dandelions, although that\'s not something I\'ll show you!$b$bAnyhow, if you\'d like to make a purchase, please speak with Patricia. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='今天，你在竞技场上的表现给所有人都留下了深刻的印象。现在，你将在万众瞩目下成为这次比武的冠军。' WHERE entry=14738; /* Text0_0: You\'ve impressed everyone here today with your skills in the arena.  It is now time to be recognized before all as a champion of the tournament. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一场挑战需要你骑上一匹银色战马。' WHERE entry=14757; /* Text0_0: The first challenge requires you to be mounted on an Argent Warhorses.  You will find these mounts along the walls of this coliseum.$b$bPlease, mount the warhorse, speak to me, and then we can proceed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='猛犸人并不像看上去那样愚蠢。看管戈莫克就是一个非常困难的任务。但现在他已经被紧紧地捆住，应该不会有任何危险了。' WHERE entry=14759; /* Text0_0: The magnataur are not as stupid as they appear. Keeping Gormok until his time is a difficult task, but he is bound tightly enough that there is no danger. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我帮助戈莫克照顾这些怪物。我并不完全赞同这种屠杀。但至少，他有机会进行战斗了。' WHERE entry=14760; /* Text0_0: I tend these creatures of Gormok as he cannot. I do not fully agree with this slaughter, but at the least he will have his chance to fight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='雪人是一种凶猛而狡诈的怪物，而这头雪人又是雪人之中最强壮的一头。我们在他的食物里掺了药，让他睡着了。$b$b但你可千万别以为他在斗兽场里还会这样昏昏沉沉地酣睡。' WHERE entry=14761; /* Text0_0: The yeti is a fierce, cunning creature, and this one is one of the strongest of his kind. We keep him asleep through herbs in his food.$b$bDo not think he will be lethargic in the ring, however. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当进攻冰冠堡垒的战斗开始时，我一定会加入。' WHERE entry=14771; /* Text0_0: I will join in the assault upon Icecrown Citadel when the time to strike is upon us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！' WHERE entry=14777; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun.  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun.  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们照顾这些虫子已经有一段时间了。我希望它们能在斗兽活动中充分发挥作用。要知道，你要打败的不是一条冰虫，而是两条。' WHERE entry=14779; /* Text0_0: We have been tending these worms for some time. I hope they will be fit in time for the ring event of this organization. You must face not one, but two jormungar, after all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！' WHERE entry=14781; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun!  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun!  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。当战斗就要开始的时候，你和我交谈，就能加入这场战斗。$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。当战斗就要开始的时候，你和我交谈，就能加入这场战斗。$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。' WHERE entry=14782; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress.  When the battle is about to begin, talk to me to enter the battle.$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress.  When the battle is about to begin, talk to me to enter the battle.$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你！好啊，就是你！$b$b好好看着我。对你来说，遇到我是你不可多得的幸运。过不了多久，全世界的人都会知道并畏惧威尔弗雷德·菲兹班的名字和我威严的面容！一旦我宏大的召唤最终完成，将没有任何人敢怀疑我的能力！' WHERE entry=14787; /* Text0_0: You! Yes, you!$b$bGaze upon me and treasure this moment of meeting, for soon the world will come to know and fear the name and stern visage of Wilfred Fizzlebang! Once my magnificent summoning is complete, no one will doubt my ability! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但下一场争夺这座堡垒的战斗就要开始了。赶快做好准备，前往冬拥湖帮助我们作战吧！$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但下一场争夺这座堡垒的战斗就要开始了。赶快做好准备，前往冬拥湖帮助我们作战吧！$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。' WHERE entry=14790; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the next battle starts soon.   Get ready to head to Wintergrasp and support our forces!$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the next battle starts soon.   Get ready to head to Wintergrasp and support our forces!$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在冬拥堡垒由联盟控制，但下一次战斗就要开始了！加入冬拥湖的战斗，帮助我们赢取胜利吧！$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在冬拥堡垒由联盟控制，但下一次战斗就要开始了！加入冬拥湖的战斗，帮助我们赢取胜利吧！$B$B这场战斗将在$4354k内开始。' WHERE entry=14791; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the next battle starts soon.   Get ready to head to Wintergrasp and support our forces!$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the next battle starts soon.   Get ready to head to Wintergrasp and support our forces!$B$BThe next battle begins in $4354k. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='裁决者玛蕾尔·图哈特请求我们负责锦标赛所需的各项工作。而我们只会邀请那些曾经在我们面前证明过自身实力的真正勇士帮助我们完成这些工作。',Text0_1_loc4='裁决者玛蕾尔·图哈特请求我们负责锦标赛所需的各项工作。而我们只会邀请那些曾经在我们面前证明过自身实力的真正勇士帮助我们完成这些工作。' WHERE entry=14793; /* Text0_0: Justicar Mariel Trueheart has asked us to see to the needs of the tournament. Those who have earned the right to stand as champions and who have proven themselves in our eyes are asked to assist with these duties. */ /* Text0_1: Justicar Mariel Trueheart has asked us to see to the needs of the tournament. Those who have earned the right to stand as champions and who have proven themselves in our eyes are asked to assist with these duties. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，竞技场已经竣工。裁决者玛蕾尔·图哈特请求我们帮助管理锦标赛和保护赛事安全。她想让我们和那些无能的银色盟约混蛋们一同工作。但他们只会碍事。',Text0_1_loc4='现在，竞技场已经竣工。裁决者玛蕾尔·图哈特请求我们帮助管理锦标赛和保护赛事安全。她想让我们和那些无能的银色盟约混蛋们一同工作。但他们只会碍事。' WHERE entry=14794; /* Text0_0: Justicar Mariel Trueheart has asked us to help administer and defend the tournament now that the coliseum is complete. She wants us to work with those worthless Silver Covenant curs, but they\'re just getting in the way. */ /* Text0_1: Justicar Mariel Trueheart has asked us to help administer and defend the tournament now that the coliseum is complete. She wants us to work with those worthless Silver Covenant curs, but they\'re just getting in the way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们也许只能在上流社会的阴影中做着默默无闻的事情。只有离开这里，在战争的最前线，我们的力量才能得到应有的尊重。',Text0_1_loc4='我们也许只能在上流社会的阴影中做着默默无闻的事情。只有离开这里，在战争的最前线，我们的力量才能得到应有的尊重。' WHERE entry=14804; /* Text0_0: We may operate in the shadows of polite society, but out here on the battlefront our powers are properly respected at last. */ /* Text0_1: We may operate in the shadows of polite society, but out here on the battlefront our powers are properly respected at last. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那名术士肯定没有召唤末日守卫。你在下一场挑战中将和银色十字军作战。做好接受挑战的准备了吗？' WHERE entry=14813; /* Text0_0: That warlock certainly didn\'t summon a Doomguard! Your next challenge will find you fighting knights of the Argent Crusade. Think you\'re up for the challenge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧，你做好准备之后，我就会向提里奥发出信号。' WHERE entry=14814; /* Text0_0: Well then, I\'ll give the signal to Tirion when you are ready to go. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这场战斗真是野蛮残忍至极。我已经有许多年没见到过如此大规模的战斗了！实在是令人震惊！' WHERE entry=14815; /* Text0_0: That fight was savage and brutal. I haven\'t seen a grand melee like that in many years! Amazing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经等不及要看到下一场战斗了！他们似乎已经做好了准备。所以，你们也赶快进行准备吧！' WHERE entry=14816; /* Text0_0: I can\'t wait to see it! They seem ready for another round now, so prepare yourselves! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='瓦格里的团队协作能力真是令人震惊。现在我终于明白，为什么只是抓住两只瓦格里就会如此困难。' WHERE entry=14820; /* Text0_0: The Val\'kyrs\'  teamwork is rather astounding. I now see why we had such problems capturing the two of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你最好记住！你要面对的是阿尔萨斯最强大的两个瓦格里侍从！' WHERE entry=14821; /* Text0_0: You better believe it! You\'re going to face two of Arthas\' most powerful Val\'kyr lieutenants! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你能够迅速提高！' WHERE entry=14822; /* Text0_0: Well I hope you improve quickly! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，竞技场终于落成了。而锦标赛的管理者也请求我们负责管理在那里面举行的竞技活动。而我们只会邀请那些曾经在我们面前证明过自身实力的真正勇士帮助我们完成这些工作。',Text0_1_loc4='现在，竞技场终于落成了。而锦标赛的管理者也请求我们负责管理在那里面举行的竞技活动。而我们只会邀请那些曾经在我们面前证明过自身实力的真正勇士帮助我们完成这些工作。' WHERE entry=14824; /* Text0_0: The tournament\'s seneschal has asked us to shoulder some of the burden of running the competition now that the coliseum is finished. Those who have earned the right to stand as champions and who have proven themselves in our eyes are asked to assist with these duties. */ /* Text0_1: The tournament\'s seneschal has asked us to shoulder some of the burden of running the competition now that the coliseum is finished. Those who have earned the right to stand as champions and who have proven themselves in our eyes are asked to assist with these duties. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太好了，今天你们证明了自己是强大的勇士。只要你们和银色十字军并肩作战，我们必将战胜天灾军团！' WHERE entry=14828; /* Text0_0: Splendid, you\'ve proven yourselves as great champions here today. With you fighting alongside the Argent Crusade, victory against the Scourge is inevitable! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论给予你怎样的赞扬都不会过份。提里奥肯定想亲自表彰你的功绩。嗨，你有没有突然觉得有些冷？' WHERE entry=14829; /* Text0_0: The praise is well deserved. Tirion will want to praise you himself, shortly. Hey, have you noticed it getting a bit cold all of a sudden? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，勇士！你是否已经聚集起力量，做好准备，打算迎接大十字军的试炼的挑战了？只有最强大，最聪明的冒险者才能进行这样的试炼。为了参与这次试炼，你们必须首先完成普通的十字军的试炼。' WHERE entry=14850; /* Text0_0: Welcome, champion! Have you gathered your forces in preparation for the challenges of the Trial of the Grand Crusader? Only the most powerful and accomplished of combatants are able to participate in these trials. To participate in these trials, you must have completed the normal Trial of the Crusader. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大十字军的试炼比十字军的试炼更加困难。这里的每一个敌人都会变得更强大。而且你无法为自己挑选敌人，除非你们曾经战胜过他们。如果在这周之内，你们进行了50次不成功的尝试，就只能等到下周再继续大十字军的试炼了。在成功地完成大十字军的试炼之后，你们将获得另一个宝物匣。现在，是否已经为这一试炼做好了准备？' WHERE entry=14853; /* Text0_0: The Trial of the Grand Crusader is a more difficult version of the Trial of the Crusader. Each encounter is more difficult, and you will not be able to freely attempt the encounters until you win. After 50 unsuccessful attempts, the Trial of the Grand Crusader will end for the week. After successfully completing the Trial of the Grand Crusader, you will receive an additional tribute chest of rewards as compensation. Are you prepared for this trial? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，很高兴再见到你。',Text0_1_loc4='$n，很高兴再见到你。' WHERE entry=14882; /* Text0_0: Nice to see you again, $N. */ /* Text0_1: Nice to see you again, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这看到兽人感到意外吧？用不着这样。$b$b需要有人看着那些被遗忘者。如果从一开始我们就好好盯着，或许天谴之门的事根本就不会发生。',Text0_1_loc4='在这看到兽人感到意外吧？用不着这样。$b$b需要有人看着那些被遗忘者。如果从一开始我们就好好盯着，或许天谴之门的事根本就不会发生。',Text1_0_loc4='希望你要找的不是那些憎恶。炼金师没有一个靠得住，他们造出来的那些在大厅里巡逻的东西也一样。真正保卫这里安全的是我们。',Text1_1_loc4='希望你要找的不是那些憎恶。炼金师没有一个靠得住，他们造出来的那些在大厅里巡逻的东西也一样。真正保卫这里安全的是我们。' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text0_0: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text0_1: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text1_0: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */ /* Text1_1: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='Lok\'tar。不要在这里做出任何可疑的行为。如果那些亡灵打算加入部落，他们就得接受我们的监视。',Text2_1_loc4='Lok\'tar。不要在这里做出任何可疑的行为。如果那些亡灵打算加入部落，他们就得接受我们的监视。' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text2_0: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */ /* Text2_1: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='速度要快，$r。' WHERE entry=14932; /* Text0_0: Make it quick, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='怎么了？骨头堆。在找人吗？这里只有我，要买东西就快点儿。',Text0_1_loc4='怎么了？骨头堆。在找人吗？这里只有我，要买东西就快点儿。',Text1_0_loc4='我敢说你们这些无赖一定觉得自己在天谴之门干得很漂亮，对吧？游戏结束了。我们来就是要阻止你们的一切行为。',Text1_1_loc4='我敢说你们这些无赖一定觉得自己在天谴之门干得很漂亮，对吧？游戏结束了。我们来就是要阻止你们的一切行为。' WHERE entry=14933; /* Text0_0: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text0_1: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text1_0: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */ /* Text1_1: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我会告诉你都该知道些什么，但这并不表示我有多么愿意。我们一直在监视着你和你的同类。',Text2_1_loc4='我会告诉你都该知道些什么，但这并不表示我有多么愿意。我们一直在监视着你和你的同类。' WHERE entry=14933; /* Text2_0: I\'ll tell you what you need to know, but I don\'t have to like it. We\'re watching you and your kind. */ /* Text2_1: I\'ll tell you what you need to know, but I don\'t have to like it. We\'re watching you and your kind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还记得和我的兄弟一起在艾萨拉荒野上露营的时候。看看它现在的样子。' WHERE entry=15021; /* Text0_0: I remember when my brother and I would camp alone in the Azshara wilderness. Look at it now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='幸会，莫霍克的好$G兄弟:姐妹;。' WHERE entry=15038; /* Text0_0: Well met, fellow Mohawk $GBrother:Sister;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来这要干什么，$c？' WHERE entry=15074; /* Text0_0: What is your business here, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='找到你了！我几乎以为你已经被逐日者劫走了。你准备好把宝典递送给冰冠冰川的使者了吗？' WHERE entry=15077; /* Text0_0: There you are! I was beginning to think that the Sunreavers had intercepted you. Are you ready to deliver the tome to our representatives in Icecrown? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没办法阻挡他太久，我们必须马上离开！',Text0_1_loc4='我没办法阻挡他太久，我们必须马上离开！' WHERE entry=15081; /* Text0_0: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */ /* Text0_1: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有当你潜入雪层时，你的冰虫才能够移动，但潜入后你的冰虫无法攻击。浮出雪层的冰虫可以使用它强大的酸性攻击穿透钢铁巨像的护甲。要做好随时下潜的准备以躲避钢铁巨像最具毁灭性的攻击。' WHERE entry=15119; /* Text0_0: Your jormungar can only move if you\'ve submerged beneath the snow, but it cannot attack while submerged. Once your jormungar emerges, it can use its powerful acid attack to wear through the armor of the Iron Colossus. Be ready to submerge to escape from the Iron Colossus\'s most devastating attacks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好吗，$c？' WHERE entry=15145; /* Text0_0: How do you do, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这看上去像是萨洛瑞安·寻晨者的遗体，奎尔德拉最后的使用者。' WHERE entry=15155; /* Text0_0: These appear to be the remains of Thalorien Dawnseeker, the last wielder of Quel\'Delar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没办法阻挡他太久，我们必须马上离开！',Text0_1_loc4='我没办法阻挡他太久，我们必须马上离开！' WHERE entry=15157; /* Text0_0: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */ /* Text0_1: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灰烬审判军是由黑锋骑士团和银色北伐军中的精英工匠组成的一支队伍。他们的创造标志了一种团结，各支力量齐心协力同巫妖王及其爪牙展开最终的战斗。  $b$b正是通过灰烬审判军的努力，我们掌握了如何将源生萨隆邪铁为我们所用的方法。' WHERE entry=15159; /* Text0_0: The Ashen Verdict is a select group of the most talented craftsmen in the Ebon Blade and Argent Crusade. Its creation symbolizes the unity of our forces as we mount this final assault on the Lich King and his minions.$b$bIt is through the Ashen Verdict\'s efforts that we have discovered how to bend primordial saronite to our will. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，和炼金师菲肯斯坦谈谈。他会为你指明道路。$b$b表明你的忠诚，你就会知道他们的办法。' WHERE entry=15160; /* Text0_0: Speak with Alchemist Finklestein, $c. He can set you on the path.$b$bDemonstrate your loyalty and their methods shall be made known to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫妖王已经离我们很近了，$n。我感觉到了他声音中的嘲弄…$b$b去让他安静下来吧！' WHERE entry=15166; /* Text0_0: The Lich King is near, $n. His voice taunts me...$b$bLet us silence him at last! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会集结其它的奴隶，被让他们做好战斗的准备。在你同天灾领主泰兰努斯开始交战前我们会赶上你的。' WHERE entry=15172; /* Text0_0: I\'ll gather up the rest of slaves and get them ready to fight. We\'ll catch up with you before you engage Scourgelord Tyrannus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='原谅我，英雄们。我应该听乌瑟尔的。我……我只是希望能够，能够看他最后一眼。对不起。',Text0_1_loc4='原谅我，英雄们。我应该听乌瑟尔的。我……我只是希望能够，能够看他最后一眼。对不起。' WHERE entry=15189; /* Text0_0: Forgive me, heroes. I should have listened to Uther. I... I just had to see for myself. To look into his eyes one last time. I am sorry. */ /* Text0_1: Forgive me, heroes. I should have listened to Uther. I... I just had to see for myself. To look into his eyes one last time. I am sorry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们暂时……安全了。他的力量已经十倍于往昔。只有一支大军才能战胜巫妖王。单凭部落的力量毫无胜算。',Text0_1_loc4='我们暂时……安全了。他的力量已经十倍于往昔。只有一支大军才能战胜巫妖王。单凭部落的力量毫无胜算。' WHERE entry=15190; /* Text0_0: We are safe... for now. His strength has increased tenfold since our last battle. It will take a mighty army to destroy the Lich King. An army greater than even the Horde can rouse. */ /* Text0_1: We are safe... for now. His strength has increased tenfold since our last battle. It will take a mighty army to destroy the Lich King. An army greater than even the Horde can rouse. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在援兵赶到前我会尽量拖延时间，但你必须继续前进。阿尔萨斯很快会发现我们在这里。',Text0_1_loc4='在援兵赶到前我会尽量拖延时间，但你必须继续前进。阿尔萨斯很快会发现我们在这里。' WHERE entry=15191; /* Text0_0: I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you must keep moving. Arthas will soon realize that we\'re here. */ /* Text0_1: I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you must keep moving. Arthas will soon realize that we\'re here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能肯定吗，$g 伙计:小姑娘;？再给你一两分钟？' WHERE entry=15195; /* Text0_0: Are ye sure, $g lad:lass;? Ye don\'t need another minute or two? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们没有时间可以浪费了，$c。为什么你在这停了下来？',Text0_1_loc4='我们没有时间可以浪费了，$c。为什么你在这停了下来？' WHERE entry=15206; /* Text0_0: We have no time to waste, $c. Why do you delay here? */ /* Text0_1: We have no time to waste, $c. Why do you delay here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们时间不多了，英雄。你需要些什么？',Text0_1_loc4='我们时间不多了，英雄。你需要些什么？' WHERE entry=15207; /* Text0_0: We do not have much time, hero. What do you need? */ /* Text0_1: We do not have much time, hero. What do you need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要我想起所有那些让我精神失常的事？听着。他们并没有付钱让我跟进这件事，我们之间的协议也不允许我透露这些。我可以把我的账本扔在地上，你自己捡起来然后别来烦我了。$b$b听明白了？' WHERE entry=15211; /* Text0_0: You expect me to remember all that off the top of my head? Look. They didn\'t pay me enough to put up with this, and the contract only asked for my silence. So I\'m just gonna drop my ledger on the floor here, and you\'re going to take it and leave me alone.$b$bGot it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论你要什么，布雷泽·盖茨！明白吗？$B$B而且我指的不光是那些“合法”的东西。我是说——无论——你要什么，朋友！任何东西……' WHERE entry=15214; /* Text0_0: Whatever you need, Brazie Getz! Get it?$B$BAnd I\'m not just talkin\' about the "legal" stuff, either. WHATEVER YOU NEED, PAL! Anything... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就是这把剑终结了我的生命……那种痛苦……挥之不去。',Text0_1_loc4='就是这把剑终结了我的生命……那种痛苦……挥之不去。' WHERE entry=15215; /* Text0_0: Standing this close to the blade that ended my life... The pain... It is renewed. */ /* Text0_1: Standing this close to the blade that ended my life... The pain... It is renewed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='部落勇敢的战士，我向你致敬！如果没有你和你盟友的帮助，我们一定会死在联盟炮艇的火力下。$B$B请稍事休息，随后我们会展开针对敌人堡垒上游的袭击。' WHERE entry=15217; /* Text0_0: Brave soldier of the Horde, I salute you! We would have surely been destroyed by the Alliance gunship had it not been for you and your allies.$B$BTake a moment to rest before we begin our assault upon the upper reaches of the citadel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能肯定吗，$n？要想战胜天灾军团，我们必须全力以赴。如果你休息得差不多了，我们就开始吧。' WHERE entry=15218; /* Text0_0: Are you sure, $N? We must face the Scourge at full strength if we are to succeed. If you do not require more rest, we will begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾听过我的孩子在那里发生的故事。现在，他已经成了巫妖王手下一名强大的死亡骑士。如果这是真的，我必须大义灭亲。$B$B我现在的责任就是指挥奥格瑞姆之锤号抵达冰冠堡垒之顶，并消灭所有阻拦我们的天灾军团。你和你的盟友准备好以后我们就出发。' WHERE entry=15219; /* Text0_0: I have heard tale of my boy being here. That he\'s now a powerful death knight in service of the Lich King. If this is true, then it must be me that ends the bloodline.$B$BMy charge now is to command Orgrim\'s Hammer to the top of Icecrown Citadel and destroy all Scourge that get in our way. We leave when you and your allies are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等你准备好了，我就护送你去太阳井。',Text0_1_loc4='等你准备好了，我就护送你去太阳井。' WHERE entry=15240; /* Text0_0: I will escort you into the Sunwell when you\'re ready. */ /* Text0_1: I will escort you into the Sunwell when you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠我近点，朋友。我在上一次袭击中被一颗子弹射中了。$B$B<甘恩努力想挪动一下身体，却只是痛苦地呻吟了一声。他的左手按在一处伤口上。血不断地从他的指缝间涌出。>$B$B当矮人们最初入侵贫瘠之地的时候，我只是满足于骚扰他们的挖掘工，破坏他们的设备。我真应该趁有机会的时候对他们发动致命的打击。' WHERE entry=15246; /* Text0_0: Kneel beside me, friend. I caught a bullet during that last raid.$B$B<Gann grunts in pain as he tries to shift position. His left hand clutches a wound, blood welling between his quivering fingers.>$B$BWhen the dwarves first invaded the Barrens, I contented myself with harassing their diggers and sabotaging their equipment. I should\'ve struck a killing blow when I had the chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没什么东西要搬吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你没什么东西要搬吗？' WHERE entry=15282; /* Text0_0: Don\'t you have some packages to move? */ /* Text0_1: Don\'t you have some packages to move? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有东西在发出臭味，这次可不是我的袜子。',Text0_1_loc4='有东西在发出臭味，这次可不是我的袜子。' WHERE entry=15284; /* Text0_0: Something stinks, and for once it\'s not my socks. */ /* Text0_1: Something stinks, and for once it\'s not my socks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是一把神器的剑，你觉得呢？这绝不会是出自矮人之手，不，还要古老的多。$B$B这些夺日者和银色盟约的使者似乎打算对这一秘密一探究竟。我已经开始准备给布莱恩的报告了。' WHERE entry=15287; /* Text0_0: Truly an amazing sword, don\'t you think? That\'s no weapon of dwarven make, no, it\'s far more ancient than that.$B$BThese Sunreaver and Silver Covenant representatives seem intent on getting to the bottom of the mystery. I\'m already working on a report for Brann. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我等待这一天的到来已经太久了，英雄。你和你的同袍们是否已经准备好对巫妖王进行正义的审判？我们将在你的命令下向敌人发起冲锋！' WHERE entry=15290; /* Text0_0: Long have I waited for this day, hero. Are you and your allies prepared to bring the Lich King to justice? We charge on your command! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text0_1_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text1_0_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text1_1_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!' WHERE entry=15296; /* Text0_0: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text1_0: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text1_1: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */
