UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，这是自己造成的创伤。我实在无法面对这样一个在巫妖王的蹂躏下充满恐慌的世界。$B$B这是我救赎之旅的第一站，如果我的罪孽无法得到原谅，我会设法用我的余生加以偿还。' WHERE entry=15297; /* Text0_0: A self-inflicted wound, friend.  I could not bear to look upon a world where I\'d committed so many horrors under the Lich King\'s grasp.$B$BIt was my first step towards redemption, and if my sins are unforgivable, then I will attempt to atone for them for the rest of my life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，东方吹来了一阵污秽的风。' WHERE entry=15302; /* Text0_0: A foul wind blows from the East, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='霜之哀伤：正是它摧毁了我们的王国。',Text0_1_loc4='霜之哀伤：正是它摧毁了我们的王国。' WHERE entry=15339; /* Text0_0: Frostmourne: the blade that destroyed our kingdom... */ /* Text0_1: Frostmourne: the blade that destroyed our kingdom... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的密探在搜集可用的天灾军团枯萎样本时经历了很多次失败，现在我亲自到前线来视察工作进度。就像他们说的，如果你希望工作能够干好…',Text0_1_loc4='我们的密探在搜集可用的天灾军团枯萎样本时经历了很多次失败，现在我亲自到前线来视察工作进度。就像他们说的，如果你希望工作能够干好…' WHERE entry=15340; /* Text0_0: After countless failures of our agents to secure workable samples of Scourge blight for analysis, I\'ve come up to the front lines myself to oversee the efforts. Like they say, if you want a job done right.... */ /* Text0_1: After countless failures of our agents to secure workable samples of Scourge blight for analysis, I\'ve come up to the front lines myself to oversee the efforts. Like they say, if you want a job done right.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='凡人们，你们将我从那比死亡更可怕的厄运中拯救了出来。如果继续困在那些设备中，我的意志迟早会被巫妖王的巫师们摧毁，我的身体也将遭受永恒的折磨。在你们面前的便是荣耀一时的辛达苟萨——玛里苟斯的配偶。$B$B奈萨里奥的背叛使她受到了致命的创伤，躺在冰冠冰川的积雪中孤独的等待死亡，现在的她完全被仇恨所充斥。然而，恶意之下仍存留着龙之女王的高尚灵魂。我相信辛达苟萨的灵魂还有机会回归安宁。',Text0_1_loc4='凡人们，你们将我从那比死亡更可怕的厄运中拯救了出来。如果继续困在那些设备中，我的意志迟早会被巫妖王的巫师们摧毁，我的身体也将遭受永恒的折磨。在你们面前的便是荣耀一时的辛达苟萨——玛里苟斯的配偶。$B$B奈萨里奥的背叛使她受到了致命的创伤，躺在冰冠冰川的积雪中孤独的等待死亡，现在的她完全被仇恨所充斥。然而，恶意之下仍存留着龙之女王的高尚灵魂。我相信辛达苟萨的灵魂还有机会回归安宁。' WHERE entry=15379; /* Text0_0: Mortals, you have saved me from a fate worse than death. Left to their devices, the sorcerers of the Lich King would have broken my will eventually, and condemned me to a tortured eternity of unlife. Ahead of you lies one who was not so fortunate: the once-proud consort of Malygos, Sindragosa.$B$BMortally wounded after Neltharion\'s betrayal and left to die alone in the snows of Icecrown, she exists now as a being of pure hatred. And yet, beneath those layers of malevolence still remains the noble spirit of a dragon queen. I believe there is yet hope that Sindragosa\'s soul may find peaceful respite. */ /* Text0_1: Mortals, you have saved me from a fate worse than death. Left to their devices, the sorcerers of the Lich King would have broken my will eventually, and condemned me to a tortured eternity of unlife. Ahead of you lies one who was not so fortunate: the once-proud consort of Malygos, Sindragosa.$B$BMortally wounded after Neltharion\'s betrayal and left to die alone in the snows of Icecrown, she exists now as a being of pure hatred. And yet, beneath those layers of malevolence still remains the noble spirit of a dragon queen. I believe there is yet hope that Sindragosa\'s soul may find peaceful respite. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的提问相当机敏，年轻的$c。铭文师能够制作蕴藏强大力量的塔罗牌，当然即使是铭文师自己也无法完全驾驭他们所创造出来的东西。决定一切的还是命运。$b$b如果你有办法集齐完整的套牌，请把它带给我，你会得到不错的回报。' WHERE entry=15400; /* Text0_0: You are astute to ask, young $c.  Scribes are capable of inscribing tarot cards of great power, although even they do not have full control of what they make.  The fates decide for them.$b$bIf you manage to obtain a completed deck, please bring it to me for a magnificent reward. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='霜翼大厅前的最后一道屏障已经被我们击破了，$g小伙子:姑娘;。只有辛达苟萨还挡在正义之师和巫妖王之间！还等什么？！' WHERE entry=15412; /* Text0_0: We got the final barrier blockin\' entry to Frostwing Halls down, $g lad:lass;. Only Sindragosa stands between the Lich King and divine retribution! What are ye waitin\' for?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有的屏障都被击破了，$n！只有辛达苟萨还挡在我们和巫妖王之间。审判即将开始…' WHERE entry=15415; /* Text0_0: All barriers are now down, $N! Only Sindragosa stands between the Lich King and us. Justice comes soon... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去哪里都行，只要离开这里……' WHERE entry=15432; /* Text0_0: Anywhere but here... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售德鲁伊需要的树纹套装。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售德鲁伊需要的树纹套装。' WHERE entry=15445; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Freya\'s Lasherweave armor for druids. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Freya\'s Lasherweave armor for druids. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售猎人需要的安卡哈猎血套装。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售猎人需要的安卡哈猎血套装。' WHERE entry=15449; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ahn\'kahar Blood Hunter armor for hunters. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ahn\'kahar Blood Hunter armor for hunters. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售战士需要的伊米亚之王套装。' WHERE entry=15450; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ymirjar Lord\'s armor for warriors. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<亡灵卫兵希米尔专注地看着你。>' WHERE entry=15512; /* Text0_0: <Deathguard Simmer looks at you expectantly.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这里通风很不错。',Text3_0_loc4='乔汉说，葛尔多需要个裁缝来修整一下葛尔多的肚子。' WHERE entry=15531; /* Text2_0: It drafty out here. */ /* Text3_0: Johaan say Gordo need a tailor to fix Gordo tummy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我代表杰出的，并依旧保持中立的热砂集团向你表示问候，并衷心希望你能在这里渡过一段愉快的时光。$B$B请记住，加基森欢迎所有人！只有海盗除外。' WHERE entry=15532; /* Text0_0: On behalf of the illustrious and still neutral Steamwheedle Cartel, I hope you enjoy your stay.$B$BRemember, everyone is welcome in Gadgetzan! Everyone except pirates. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='需要什麽吗?' WHERE entry=15572; /* Text0_0: Need something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灰烬审判军和像你一样的英雄们以惨重的牺牲为代价，终于接近了最终的胜利。现在，我来到冰冠堡垒，帮助所有对抗天灾军团的勇士们。我们将并肩作战，结束巫妖王的暴行！' WHERE entry=15602; /* Text0_0: The continued sacrifice of the Ashen Verdict and heroes such as yourself bring us all closer to final victory. Now I have come to Icecrown Citadel to lend aid to those who fight against the Scourge. Together we will end the tyranny of the Lich King! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要击败巫妖王，你需要的将不止是勇气。祝你好运。' WHERE entry=15604; /* Text0_0: You will need more than bravery to defeat the Lich King. Good luck. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经做出了选择。至于是生是死，就只能靠你自己了。' WHERE entry=15605; /* Text0_0: Your choice has been made. Whether you live or die by that choice is now up to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战歌远征军已经到达冰冠堡垒。胜利就在眼前！巫妖王的惨败将成为部落新的荣耀！' WHERE entry=15606; /* Text0_0: With the Warsong Offensive here in Icecrown Citadel, victory is within our grasp! The death of the Lich King will bring glory to the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的选择很勇敢！而你对荣耀和功业的欲望也值得尊敬！光荣地去死吧，$n！' WHERE entry=15607; /* Text0_0: Your choice was bold! I respect your desire for glory and honor! Die well, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别被鹰身人那长满羽毛的翘臀迷惑……她们的杀伤力可是致命的！' WHERE entry=15664; /* Text0_0: Try to ignore the firm, feathery behinds of the harpies... the creatures are really quite deadly! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些该死的害虫!',Text0_1_loc4='哨兵部队在卡利姆多各地阻挡部落的攻势。当灰谷与石爪山相继被战火席卷之时，这里也需要我们的帮助——我们要保护那些仅存的野生动植物，并阻止我们的敌人攻占更为纵深的据点。' WHERE entry=15719; /* Text0_0: Missing US text */ /* Text0_1: The forces of the Sentinel Army hold back the Horde across all of Kalimdor. While the war continues in Ashenvale and Stonetalon, our forces are also needed here, to protect these remaining wilds and prevent our enemies from gaining further footholds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是第一批响应沃金的号召，投身军队的人之一。你愿意加入我们吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我是第一批响应沃金的号召，投身军队的人之一。你愿意加入我们吗？' WHERE entry=15796; /* Text0_0: I be one of da first to answer Vol\'jin\'s call to arms. Will you be joinin\' us? */ /* Text0_1: I be one of da first to answer Vol\'jin\'s call to arms. Will you be joinin\' us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想要蝙蝠，那么你可是来对地方了。我掌管着全部哨兵的蝙蝠。' WHERE entry=15806; /* Text0_0: If ya need a bat, ya come to da right place. I be handlin\' all de bats for de scouts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿英灵指引你，$c。' WHERE entry=15846; /* Text0_0: May de spirits guide ya, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到侏儒区！' WHERE entry=15863; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Tinker Town! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这块碎冰中回荡着冰川切割地壳时深沉的碎裂声。它能够将你的思维变成没有生命，没有尽头的寒冬。' WHERE entry=15864; /* Text0_0: This shard of ice echoes the deep, cracking rumble of invading glaciers.  Its cold turns your thoughts to a lifeless, endless winter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='扎拉赞恩就要完蛋了。回音群岛将再次属于暗矛部族！' WHERE entry=15865; /* Text0_0: Zalazane\'s time be runnin\' out. De Echo Isles will belong to de Darkspear Tribe again! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗矛部族回到了家园！$n，如果没有你的帮助，我们无法实现这个梦想。现在，让我们庆祝吧！' WHERE entry=15866; /* Text0_0: De Darkspears have a home again! An\' we couldn\'t have done it wit\'out ya helpin\', $N. Now, we celebrate! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的任务就是确保整个进攻行动像时钟一样准确地进行。$B$B大工匠梅卡托克已经到战场去了，但他正计划返回这里，再将更多的部队带上战场。$B$B他从不会迟到，所以你应该在这里等他。',Text0_1_loc4='我的任务就是确保整个进攻行动像时钟一样准确地进行。$B$B大工匠梅卡托克已经到战场去了，但他正计划返回这里，再将更多的部队带上战场。$B$B他从不会迟到，所以你应该在这里等他。' WHERE entry=15868; /* Text0_0: It\'s my job to ensure that this whole assault runs like clockwork.$B$BHigh Tinker Mekkatorque is out in the field now, but he\'s scheduled to come back to get some more troops any time now.  $B$BHe\'s never late, so just stick around and he\'ll be here. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s my job to ensure that this whole assault runs like clockwork.$B$BHigh Tinker Mekkatorque is out in the field now, but he\'s scheduled to come back to get some more troops any time now.  $B$BHe\'s never late, so just stick around and he\'ll be here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='快点！你现在应该去找梅卡托克！如果我们不尽快开始进攻，我们就要耽误行动了。$B$B如果我们耽误的话，我们的首领可是要发火的！',Text0_1_loc4='快点！你现在应该去找梅卡托克！如果我们不尽快开始进攻，我们就要耽误行动了。$B$B如果我们耽误的话，我们的首领可是要发火的！' WHERE entry=15870; /* Text0_0: Hurry! You should talk to Mekkatorque! If we don\'t start the assault soon, we\'re going to be late.$B$BAnd my boss HATES it when we\'re late! */ /* Text0_1: Hurry! You should talk to Mekkatorque! If we don\'t start the assault soon, we\'re going to be late.$B$BAnd my boss HATES it when we\'re late! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='沃金要我在他回来之前一直敲这面鼓。如果你在等他，那么我可以告诉你，他很快就会回来夺回这些岛屿了。$B$B暂时先在这里等一等他，欣赏一下这音乐吧！' WHERE entry=15873; /* Text0_0: Vol\'jin told me ta keep hittin\' da drum till he gets back.  If ya be waitin\' for him, he\'d be back soon to take back da Isles.$B$BJust wait here and enjoy da music! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们正在为夺回回音群岛做准备。扎拉赞恩一直在施展他的黑暗魔法，操纵傀儡，进行古老的黑暗仪式。$B$B他知道我们的行动，所以我们必须做好万全的准备。' WHERE entry=15876; /* Text0_0: We\'d be gettin\' ready to take back da Echo Isles. Zalazane has been workin\' his voodoo magic for some time, convincing folks dat he be dead and performing ancient dark rituals.$B$BHe knows we\'d be coming, so we have ta make sure we be prepared. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果要成功地夺回这些岛屿，我们就需要有援军的帮助。$B$B岑塔布拉一直在照看这片群岛上的动物们。我们需要她和那些动物的帮助。$B$B邦桑迪是一位强大的神灵。他控制着这片群岛上死者们的灵魂。他的祝福对我们是至关重要的。$B$B当我们取得他们的援助之后，扎拉赞恩和被他控制的巨魔将必败无疑！那时，回音群岛就会回到暗矛部族的怀抱！' WHERE entry=15877; /* Text0_0: We require da help of allies on da islands.$B$BZen\'tabra has been watching over da animals of de Islands for some time now.  We\'d need her help and da help of da animal creatures.$B$BBwonsamdi is a powerful loa dat controls de spirits of de dead on da islands.  His blessing is crucial for our attack.$B$BOnce our allies have joined us, Zalazane and his army of mind-controlled trolls will have no chance!  Then, da Echo Isles will be de Darkspears! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，就算没有这些新麻烦不断的冒出来，维持这儿的秩序就已经够让人头痛的了！希望你有好消息，$n……',Text0_1_loc4='啊，就算没有这些新麻烦不断的冒出来，维持这儿的秩序就已经够让人头痛的了！希望你有好消息，$n……' WHERE entry=16211; /* Text0_0: Ach, it\'s hard enough keeping order around here without all these new troubles popping up!  I hope you have good news, $n... */ /* Text0_1: Ach, it\'s hard enough keeping order around here without all these new troubles popping up!  I hope you have good news, $n... */
